#### <a name="officecompliancefileformatballotoption"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-549">Office.Compliance.FileFormatBallotOption</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-549">Office.Compliance.FileFormatBallotOption</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-550">Stebi, ar rodomas dialogo langas „FileFormat Ballot“ – įvykis siunčiamas pirmą arba antrą kartą paleidžiant „Word“, „Excel“ arba PPT sąsajoje „Win32“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-550">Tracks whether the FileFormat Ballot dialog box is displayed - event is sent at the first/second boot of Word, Excel or PPT Win32.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-551">Nurodo, ar „Office“ failų formato pasirinkimo dialogo langas buvo rodomas pirmą arba antrą kartą paleidžiant „Word“, „Excel“, „PowerPoint“ sąsajoje „Win32“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-551">Indicates whether the Office File Format choice dialog box is displayed on first or second boot of Word, Excel, or PowerPoint on Win32.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-553">**FileFormatBallotSelectedOption** – identifikuoja failo formato parinktį (OOXML/ODF), kurią vartotojas pasirinko per failo formato balsavimo dialogo langą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-553">**FileFormatBallotSelectedOption** – Identifies the file format option (OOXML/ODF) that was selected by the user through the file format ballot dialog box.</span></span>


#### <a name="officecorrelationmetadatautccorrelationmetadata"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-554">Office.CorrelationMetadata.UTCCorrelationMetadata</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-554">Office.CorrelationMetadata.UTCCorrelationMetadata</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-555">Renka „Office“ metaduomenis per UTC, kad palyginti atitinkamus duomenis, surinktus naudojant „Office“ telemetrijos srautą, bei patikrinti duomenų tikslumą ir užbaigtumą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-555">Collects Office metadata through UTC to compare with equivalent data collected through the Office telemetry pipeline to check correctness and completeness of data.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-557">**abConfigs** – funkcijų ID sąrašas, skirtas identifikuoti pas klientą įjungtas funkcijas arba jis gali būti tuščias, kai duomenys nėra renkami.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-557">**abConfigs** - A list of feature IDs to identify which features are enabled on the client or empty when this data is not being collected.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-560">**AppSessionGuid** – konkrečios taikomosios programos seanso pradžios identifikatorius, naudojamas nuo proceso kūrimo pradžios ir iki proceso pabaigos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-560">**AppSessionGuid** - An identifier of a particular application session starting at process creation time and persisting until process end.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-561">Jis yra suformuotas kaip standartinis 128 bitų GUID, tik sudarytas iš 4 dalių.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-561">It is formatted as a standard 128-bit GUID but constructed of 4 parts.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-562">Šios keturios dalys eilės tvarka yra (1) 32 bitų proceso ID (2) 16 bitų seanso ID (3) 16 bitų įkrovos ID (4) 64 bitų proceso sukūrimo laikas, išreikštas UTC 100 nsek.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-562">Those four parts in order are (1) 32 bit Process ID (2) 16 bit Session ID (3) 16 bit Boot ID (4) 64 bit Process creation time in UTC 100ns</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-563">**appVersionBuild** – taikomosios programos komponavimo versijos numeris.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-563">**appVersionBuild** - The app build version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-564">**appVersionMajor** – taikomosios programos pagrindinės versijos numeris.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-564">**appVersionMajor** - The app major version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-565">**appVersionMajor** – taikomosios programos papildomos versijos numeris.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-565">**appVersionMinor** - The app minor version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-566">**appVersionRevision** – taikomosios programos peržiūros versijos numeris.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-566">**appVersionRevision** - The app revision version number.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-567">**audienceGroup** – leidimo auditorijos grupės pavadinimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-567">**audienceGroup** - The release audience group name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-568">**audienceId** – leidimo auditorijos pavadinimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-568">**audienceId** - The release audience name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-569">**channel** – kanalas, kuriuo platintas „Office“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-569">**channel** - The channel by which Office was distributed</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-570">**deviceClass** – įrenginio formos koeficientas iš OS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-570">**deviceClass** - Device form factor from the OS</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-571">**ecsETag** – proceso eksperimento identifikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-571">**ecsETag** - An experiment identifier for the process</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-572">**impressionId** – GUID rodo dabartinį funkcijų rinkinį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-572">**impressionId** - A guid indicating the current set of features.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-573">**languageTag** - dabartinė „Office“ UI IETF kalbos žymė</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-573">**languageTag** - The current Office UI IETF language tag</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-574">**officeUserID** – atsitiktinai sugeneruotas GUID, skirtas šiam „Office“ diegimui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-574">**officeUserID** - Randomly generated guid for this Office install</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-575">**osArchitecture** – operacinės sistemos architektūra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-575">**osArchitecture** - Operating system architecture</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-576">**osEnvironment** – sveikasis skaičius, nurodantis operacinę sistemą („Windows“, „Android“, „iOS“, „Mac“ ir kt).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-576">**osEnvironment** - An integer indicating the operating system (Windows, Android, iOS, Mac, etc).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-577">**osVersionString –** operacinės sistemos versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-577">**osVersionString** - Operating system version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-578">**sessionID** – atsitiktinai sugeneruotas GUID, skirtas nustatyti taikomosios programos seansą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-578">**sessionID** - Randomly generated guid to identify the app session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-579">**UTCReplace_AppSessionGuid** – nuolatinė Bulio logikos vertė.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-579">**UTCReplace_AppSessionGuid** - Constant boolean value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-580">Visuomet „True“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-580">Always true.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeonenotefirstrunfirstrun"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-581">Office.OneNote.FirstRun.FirstRun</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-581">Office.OneNote.FirstRun.FirstRun</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-582">Kritinis signalas, naudojamas siekiant užtikrinti, kad nauji vartotojai galėtų sėkmingai paleisti ir paleisti „OneNote“ pirmą kartą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-582">The critical signal used to ensure new users can successfully launch and run OneNote for the first time.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-583">Telemetrija renkama siekiant užtikrinti regresijos aptikimą, kuris ypač svarbus programai „OneNote“ ir tarnybos sveikatai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-583">The telemetry is collected to ensure critical regression detection for OneNote app and service health.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-584">Jei vartotojai negali paleisti pirmą kartą, tai gali lemti didelės svarbos incidentą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-584">If users can’t launch the app for the first time, this would trigger a high severity incident.</span></span>

#### <a name="officetargetedmessagingensurecached"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-616">Office.TargetedMessaging.EnsureCached</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-616">Office.TargetedMessaging.EnsureCached</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-617">Seka, ar buvo atsisiųstas paketas dinaminei matomosios tinklalapio srities daliai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-617">Tracks if a package for Dynamic Canvas was downloaded.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-618">Laikoma taikomosios programinės įrangos konfigūracija, nes paketas turi būti sėkmingai atsisiųstas, kad įgalinti klientą generuoti tinkamą patirtį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-618">Considered a software configuration because the package must be successfully downloaded to enable the client to render the right experience.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-619">Yra ypač kritinės vartotojo prenumeratoms, kur matomąją tinklalapio sritį naudojame informuoti vartotoją, kad licencija nebegalioja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-619">Is especially critical in consumer subscriptions where we use canvas to communicate to the user that the license has expired.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-620">Naudojamas sekti metaduomenis dinaminio turinio paketo, kurį atsisiuntė ir į talpyklą įkėlė produktas, taip pat operacijų, atliktų su paketu, rezultatus: nesėkmingus atsisiuntimus, negalimą išsipakavimą, nuolatines patikros triktis, sėkmingą kreipimąsi į talpyklą, paketo naudojimus ir atsisiuntimo šaltinius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-620">Used to track metadata of a dynamic content package downloaded and cached by the product as well as results of operations performed on the package: download failures, unpacking failures, consistency checks failures, cache hits, package usages, download sources.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-621">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-621">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-622">**Data\_CacheFolderNotCreated –** Bulio logikos žyma nurodo, ar pavyko sukurti talpyklos aplanką</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-622">**Data\_CacheFolderNotCreated -** Boolean flag indicating if cache folder creation succeed</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-623">**Data\_CdnPath – paketo šaltinio adresas –**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-623">**Data\_CdnPath – source address of the package-**</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-624">**Data\_EnsureCached –** Bulio logikos žyma, nurodanti, ar turinio paketas buvo įtrauktas į talpyklą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-624">**Data\_EnsureCached -** Boolean flag indicating if content package was cached</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-625">**Data\_ExistsAlready –** Bulio logikos žyma, nurodanti, kad paketas jau buvo atsisiųstas anksčiau ir buvo dar vienas bandymas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-625">**Data\_ExistsAlready -** Boolean flag indicating that the package was already downloaded before and there was another attempt</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-626">**Data\_GetFileStreamFailed –** šaltinio paketo nėra šaltinyje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-626">**Data\_GetFileStreamFailed -** source package not available in source</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-627">**Data\_GetFileStreamFailedToCreateLocalFolder –** vietinio disko problemos, dėl kurių nepavyksta sukurti katalogo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-627">**Data\_GetFileStreamFailedToCreateLocalFolder -** local disk issues causing failure in directory creation</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-628">**Data\_GetFileStreamFromPackageFailed –** žyma, nurodanti, ar paketas buvo atsisiųstas, bet klientas negali jo perskaityti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-628">**Data\_GetFileStreamFromPackageFailed -** flag indicating if package was downloaded, but the client can’t read it</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-629">**Data\_GetFileStreamFromPackageSuccess –** sėkmingi paketo perskaitymo bandymai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-629">**Data\_GetFileStreamFromPackageSuccess -** successful attempts to read the package</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-630">**Data\_GetFileStreamSuccess -** nėra disko arba konfigūravimo problemų, neleidžiančių skaityti failų srautą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-630">**Data\_GetFileStreamSuccess -** no disk issues nor configuration issues which doesn’t let the file stream to be read</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-631">**Data\_GetRelativePathsFailed –** santykinis kelias nenurodo pasiekiamos vietos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-631">**Data\_GetRelativePathsFailed -** relative path doesn’t point to accessible location</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-632">**Data\_HashActualValue –** maišos vertė paimta iš failo pavadinimo paketo naudojimo metu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-632">**Data\_HashActualValue -** hash value extracted from file name when the package was used</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-633">**Data\_HashCalculationFailed –** maišos skaičiavimo klaida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-633">**Data\_HashCalculationFailed -** error with calculation of a hash</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-634">**Data\_HashMatchFailed –** maišos neatitikimas tarp paketo pavadinimo ir registro vertės, įtrauktos į talpyklą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-634">**Data\_HashMatchFailed -** hash mismatch between the package name and registry values cached</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-635">**Data\_HashMatchSuccess –** sėkminga maišos nuoseklumo patikra</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-635">**Data\_HashMatchSuccess -** hash consistency check success</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-636">**Data\_PackageDownloadRequestFailed –** negalima atsisiųsti paketo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-636">**Data\_PackageDownloadRequestFailed -** can’t download the package</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-637">**Data\_PackageDownloadRequestNoData –** atsisiųstame pakete nėra duomenų</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-637">**Data\_PackageDownloadRequestNoData -** downloaded package contains no data</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-638">**Data\_PackageDownloadRequestSuccess –** sėkmingas paketo atsisiuntimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-638">**Data\_PackageDownloadRequestSuccess -** successful download of a package</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-639">**Data\_PackageExplodedSuccess –** bandymo išpakuoti būsenos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-639">**Data\_PackageExplodedSuccess -** unpacking attempts statuses</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-640">**Data\_PackageOpenFailed –** nepavykę bandymai atidaryti paketo failą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-640">**Data\_PackageOpenFailed -** failed attempts to open the package file</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-641">**Data\_PackageOpenSuccess –** pavykę bandymai atidaryti paketo failą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-641">**Data\_PackageOpenSuccess -** successful attempts to open the package file</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-642">**Data\_SuccessHashValue –** maišos vertė paimta iš failo pavadinimo, kai buvo atsisiųstas paketas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-642">**Data\_SuccessHashValue -** hash value extracted from file name when the package was downloaded</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-643">**Data\_SuccessSource –** paviršius, kuriam buvo atsisiųstas paketas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-643">**Data\_SuccessSource -** surface for which the package was downloaded</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-656">**AsyncBegin** – asinchroninių funkcijų skaičius, kurios prasideda</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-656">**AsyncBegin** - number of async functions that begin</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1178">**RMS.DurationWithoutExternalOps** – bendrasis laikas atėmus išorinių operacijų laiką, pvz., tinklo delsą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1178">**RMS.DurationWithoutExternalOps** - Total time minus external operations consumed, such as network latency.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1185">**RMS.StatusCode** – API apibrėžtas scenarijaus ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1185">**RMS.StatusCode** - Scenario Id defined by the API</span></span>


#### <a name="officeappcompatappcompatagentupload"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1186">Office.AppCompat.AppCompat.AgentUpload</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1186">Office.AppCompat.AppCompat.AgentUpload</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1187">Generuojama paleidžiant klientą, kai galutinis vartotojas įgalina „Office“ telemetrijos ataskaitų sritį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1187">Generated on client startup when end user has enabled Office Telemetry Dashboard.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1188">Tenka informaciją, kai „Office“ telemetrijos agentas įkelia duomenis į bendrinimo aplanką.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1188">It collects information on when the Office Telemetry Agent has uploaded data to the share folder.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1189">Šis įvykis visų pirma naudojamas norint stebėti „Office“ telemetrijos agento sveikatą. Antrinė paskirtis yra įvertinti „Office“ telemetrijos ataskaitų srities naudojimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1189">The primary use of this event is to monitor the health of the Office Telemetry agent and the secondary use of the event is to estimate usage of the Office Telemetry Dashboard.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1190">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1190">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1193">Renkama tik kai galutinis vartotojas įgalina „Office“ telemetrijos ataskaitų sritį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1193">Only collected when end user has enabled Office Telemetry Dashboard.</span></span><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1194">Ji renka informaciją, kai „Office“ telemetrijos agentas yra įvykdytas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1194"> It collects information on when the Office Telemetry Agent is executed.</span></span><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1195">Informacija renkama tik tuo atveju, kai „Office“ telemetrijos ataskaitų sritis yra įjungta ir naudojama nustatyti „Office“ telemetrijos agento sveikatą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1195">  This is only collected when Office Telemetry Dashboard is enabled and is used to determine the health of Office Telemetry agent.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1197">**Data.AgentExit** – telemetrijos agento sėkmingo uždarymo laiko žyma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1197">**Data.AgentExit** - Timestamp of when the Telemetry agent exits successfully</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1198">**Data.AgentExit** – telemetrijos agento sėkmingo nuskaitymo atlikimo laiko žyma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1198">**Data.AgentScan** - Timestamp of when the Telemetry agent completed a scan successfully</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1199">**Data.AgentUpload** – telemetrijos agento sėkmingo įkėlimo atlikimo laiko žyma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1199">**Data.AgentUpload** - Timestamp of when the Telemetry agent completes the upload successfully</span></span>

#### <a name="officeappcompatappcompattelemetrydashboardresiliencycrashlog"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1200">Office.AppCompat.AppCompat.TelemetryDashboardResiliencyCrashLog</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1200">Office.AppCompat.AppCompat.TelemetryDashboardResiliencyCrashLog</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1204">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1204">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1205">**Data.CollectionTime** – laiko žyma, kai buvo užregistruotas gedimo įvykis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1205">**Data.CollectionTime** - Timestamp of when a crash event was logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1216">**Data_ActivatingPrimaryIdentity** – teisinga/klaidinga reikšmė, jei buvo naudojamas pagrindinį tapatybė.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1216">**Data_ActivatingPrimaryIdentity** - A true/false value denoting if the primary identity was used.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1219">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1219">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1220">Įvykis naudojamas fiksuoti autorizavimo žymos generavimo klaidas atliekant InAppPurchase „Mac“ (įvykių žurnalai, gautas klaidos kodas).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1220">The event is used for capturing auth token generation failures during InAppPurchase on the Mac (the event logs the error code received).</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1221">Šis įvykis naudojamas nustatant ir sprendžiant autorizavimo žymos generavimo klaidas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1221">This event is used for detecting and helping troubleshoot auth token generation failures</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1227">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1227">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1228">Mes renkame informaciją, susijusią su produkto sąsaja pirkimo programėlėje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1228">We collect information related to product association after an in-app purchase.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1229">Užregistruojame, kurį prenumeratos SKU susiejame.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1229">We log which subscription SKU we are associating.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1230">Tai naudojama pirkimo programėlėje produktų susiejimų sveikatai stebėti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1230">This is used to monitor the health of the in-app purchase product associations.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1234">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1234">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1235">Renkame informaciją, susijusią su produktų pirkimu „AppStore“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1235">We collect information related to product purchases on the AppStore.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1236">Stebime pirkimo rezultatą (nepavyko, pavyko, mokėjimo problema ir t. t.), pirkimo užklausos tipą (atkūrimas, įsigijimas) ir įsigytą SKU/produktą („Office 365 Home“ ir t. t.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1236">We track the result of the purchase (Failure, success, payment issue, etc.), the type of the purchase request (restore, purchase) and the SKU/product being purchased (Office 365 Home, etc.).</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1237">Šie duomenys naudojami pirkimo programėlėje srautų sveikatai stebėti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1237">This data is used for monitoring the health of the in-app purchase flows.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_apple_intune"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1242">Office_Apple_InTune</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1242">Office_Apple_InTune</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1243">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1243">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1244">Renkame, ar dabartinis seansas yra "Intune" valdomas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1244">We collect whether the current session is Intune-managed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1245">Tai naudojama „Intune“ valdomuose seansuose greitai rikiuoti / filtruoti, bei suteikia mums galimybę ištirti galimas programos „Office, kuri vykdoma kaip „Intune“ valdoma taikomoji programa, triktis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1245">This is used to pivot/filter on Intune managed sessions and allows us to investigate potential issues related to Office being run as an Intune-managed application.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docs_apple_docsuxiossaveasthroughfilemenu"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1279">Office_Docs_Apple_DocsUXiOSSaveAsThroughFileMenu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1279">Office_Docs_Apple_DocsUXiOSSaveAsThroughFileMenu</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1280">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1280">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1281">Įvykių įrašai, kai vykdoma operacija Įrašyti kaip, naudojami suprasti ir nustatyti prioritetus vartotojo patirčiai pagal failo operacijos informaciją, pvz., vietų kategorijas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1281">The event records when a “Save as” operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file operation information such as location categories.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1282">Operacija Įrašyti kaip vykdoma, kai vartotojas sukuria naują failą ir įrašo jį pirmą kartą arba išsaugo esamo failo kopiją naujoje vietoje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1282">A “Save as” operation occurs whenever a user creates a new file and saves it for the first time or saves a copy of an existing file to a new location.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1283">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1283">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1284">**Data_OriginServiceType** – pradinės failo vietos, pvz., „SharePoint“, „OneDrive“, „Local“, „WOPI“ ir t. t., abstraktus kategorizavimas, ir aiškus nurodymas, kad tai nėra faktinė failo vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1284">**Data_OriginServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the original location of a file like “SharePoint”, “OneDrive”, “Local”, “WOPI”, etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1285">**Data_ServiceType** – naujos failo vietos, pvz., „SharePoint“, „OneDrive“, „Local“, „WOPI“ ir t. t., abstraktus kategorizavimas kai įrašymas yra baigtas ir aiškus nurodymas, kad tai nėra faktinė failo vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1285">**Data_ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the new location of a file after the save is completed like “SharePoint”, “OneDrive”, “Local”, “WOPI”, etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1287">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1287">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1288">Šis įvykis įrašo, kai vartotojas „@“ pamini kitą vartotoją ir yra naudojamas norint suprasti ir nustatyti vartotojo patirčių prioritetus, atsižvelgiant į tai, kaip vartotojai bendradarbiauja su kitais vartotojais.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1288">This event records when a user “@” mentions another user and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on how users collaborate with other users.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1289">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1289">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1290">**Data_CharactersTyped** – skaitinė reikšmė, nurodanti bendrą simbolių skaičių, įvestą tekste, kuriame minimas vartotojas „@“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1290">**Data_CharactersTyped** - A numerical value that indicates the total number of characters typed in the “@” mention text.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docs_apple_docsuxmacodspsharingwebviewsharingcompleted"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1291">Office_Docs_Apple_DocsUXMacODSPSharingWebViewSharingCompleted</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1291">Office_Docs_Apple_DocsUXMacODSPSharingWebViewSharingCompleted</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1292">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1292">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1293">Šis įvykis fiksuoja, kada vartotojas pasirenka bendrinti debesies dokumentą naudodamas „OneDrive“ bendrinimo patirtį ir yra naudojamas norint geriau suprasti ir nustatyti vartotojo patirties prioritetus, atsižvelgiant į dokumentų bendrinimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1293">This event records when a user chooses to share a cloud document using the OneDrive sharing experience and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on sharing documents.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1294">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1294">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1295">**Data_ShareType** – užprogramuota eilutė, kurioje nurodoma, kokio tipo operacija buvo baigta, įskaitant, bet neapsiribojant operacijomis „kopijuoti saitą“, „daugiau taikomųjų programų“, „Teams“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1295">**Data_ShareType** - A hardcoded string that indicates what kind of share operation was completed including but not limited to “Copy Link”, “More apps”, “Teams”.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1296">**Data_ShareWebViewMode** – užprogramuota eilutė, nurodanti, kokio tipo bendrinimo režimas buvo aktyvus, kai bendrinamas buvo baigtas, įskaitant, bet neapsiribojant „ManageAccess“, „AtMentions“, Bendrinti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1296">**Data_ShareWebViewMode** - A hardcoded string that indicates what kind of share mode was active when the share was completed including but not limited to “ManageAccess”, “AtMentions”, “Share”.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_collaboration_coauthorgalleryrowtapped"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1297">Office_DocsUI_Collaboration_CoauthorGalleryRowTapped</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1297">Office_DocsUI_Collaboration_CoauthorGalleryRowTapped</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1298">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1298">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1299">Šis įvykis fiksuoja, kada vartotojas pasirenka dabartinio bendraautorių sąrašo peržiūrą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1299">This event records when a user selects to look at the list of current co-authors.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1300">Šie duomenys naudojami siekiant geriau suprasti ir nustatyti vartotojo patirčių prioritetus, susijusius su dokumento redagavimu vienu metu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1300">This data is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences relating to co-authoring a document at the same time.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1301">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1301">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1302">**Data_CoauthorCount** – skaitinė reikšmė, nurodanti bendrą skaičių žmonių, kurie vienu metu redaguoja tą patį dokumentą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1302">**Data_CoauthorCount** - A numerical value that represents the total number of people who are currently editing the same document as the user.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1304">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1304">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1305">Įvykių įrašai, kai pasikeičia aktyvių bendraautorių skaičius debesies dokumente.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1305">The event records when the number of active co-authors in a cloud document changes.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1306">Šie duomenys naudojami siekiant geriau suprasti ir nustatyti vartotojo patirčių prioritetus, susijusius su dokumento redagavimu vienu metu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1306">This data is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences relating to co-authoring a document at the same time.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1307">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1307">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1308">**Data_CoauthorsJoined** – bendraautorių, prisijungusių prie dokumento, skaičius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1308">**Data_CoauthorsJoined** - The number of co-authors that joined the document.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1309">**Data_CoauthorsLeft** – bendraautorių, kurie atsijungė nuo dokumento, skaičius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1309">**Data_CoauthorsLeft** - The number of co-authors that left the document.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1312">**Data_ServiceType** – failo vietos, pvz., „SharePoint“, „OneDrive“, „Local“, „WOPI“ ir t. t., abstraktus kategorizavimas, ir aiškus nurodymas, kad tai nėra faktinė failo vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1312">**Data_ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like “SharePoint”, “OneDrive”, “Local”, “WOPI”, etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_docstage_docstagecreatenewfromtemplate"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1313">Office_DocsUI_DocStage_DocStageCreateNewFromTemplate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1313">Office_DocsUI_DocStage_DocStageCreateNewFromTemplate</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1314">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1314">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1315">Įvykio įrašai, nurodantys patirtį naują failą sukuriant naudojant funkciją Naujas iš šablono, ir naudojami siekiant geriau suprasti ir nustatyti vartotojo patirties prioritetus, atsižvelgiant į dokumentų kūrimo informaciją.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1315">The event records when a new file is created from the “New from template” experience and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on document creation information.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1316">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1316">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1317">**Data_InHomeTab** – Bulio logikos reikšmė, nurodanti, ar naujas failas iš šablono buvo sukurtas failo naujų funkcijų skirtuke Pagrindinis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1317">**Data_InHomeTab** - A Boolean value that indicate whether the new file from template was created from the Home tab of the file new experience.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1318">**Data_InSearch** – Bulio logika, nurodanti, ar failas buvo sukurtas, kai vartotojas ieškojo šablono.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1318">**Data_InSearch** - A Boolean that indicates whether the file was created when the user was searching for a template.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1319">**Data_IsHomeTabEnabled** – Bulio logikos reikšmė, nurodanti, ar skirtukas Pagrindinis šiuo metu pasiekiamas vartotojui.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1319">**Data_IsHomeTabEnabled** - A Boolean value that indicates if the Home tab is currently available to the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1320">**Data_IsRecommendedEnabled** – Bulio logikos reikšmė, nurodanti, ar patirtis Rekomenduojama šiuo metu pasiekiamas vartotojui.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1320">**Data_IsRecommendedEnabled** - A Boolean value that indicates if the “Recommended” experience is currently available to the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1321">**Data_TemplateIndex** – vartotojui vizualiai rodomas šablono failo skaitinis indeksas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1321">**Data_TemplateIndex** - The numerical index of the template file as it is displayed visually to the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1322">**Data_TemplateType** – klasifikacija, padedanti atskirti šablono tipą, bet neapsiribojant šablonais „Online“, „Online search" ar „Local“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1322">**Data_TemplateType** - A classification to help distinguish the type of template like, but not limited to, “Online” templates, “Online search” templates, “Local” templates.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_docstage_recommendedopen"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1323">Office_DocsUI_DocStage_RecommendedOpen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1323">Office_DocsUI_DocStage_RecommendedOpen</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1324">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1324">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1325">Įvykių įrašai, kai vykdoma failo atidarymo operacija iš rekomenduojamo dokumentų galerijos failų skyriaus, naudojama nustatyti prioritetus vartotojo patirčiai pagal failo atidarymo operacijos informaciją.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1325">The event records when a file-open operation takes place from the recommended files section of the document gallery and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file open operation information.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1326">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1326">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1327">**Data_Success** – Bulio logikos reikšmė, nurodanti, ar pavyko atlikti operaciją.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1327">**Data_Success** - A Boolean value to indicate whether the operation succeeded.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_fileoperations_docsuifileopenmacrequired"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1328">Office_DocsUI_FileOperations_DocsUIFileOpenMacRequired</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1328">Office_DocsUI_FileOperations_DocsUIFileOpenMacRequired</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1329">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1329">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1330">Įvykių įrašai, kai vykdoma failo atidarymo operacija, naudojama suprasti ir nustatyti prioritetus vartotojo patirčiai remiantis failo atidarymo operacijos informacija, pvz., vietinėmis kategorijomis „ServiceType“ ir pirmaisiais keturiais plėtinio simboliais.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1330">The event records when a file open operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file open operation information such as location categories “ServiceType” and the first four characters of the extension.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1331">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1331">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1332">**Data_Ext** – failo plėtinys, apribotas iki pirmų keturių ar mažiau plėtinio simbolių.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1332">**Data_Ext** - The file extension limited to the first four characters of the extension or less.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1333">**Data_ServiceType** – failo vietos, pvz., „SharePoint“, „OneDrive“, „Local“, „WOPI“ ir t. t., abstraktus kategorizavimas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1333">**Data_ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like “SharePoint”, “OneDrive”, “Local”, “WOPI”, etc.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_fileoperations_openfilewithreason"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1334">Office_DocsUI_FileOperations_OpenFileWithReason</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1334">Office_DocsUI_FileOperations_OpenFileWithReason</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1335">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1335">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1336">Įvykių įrašai, kai vykdoma failo atidarymo operacija, naudojama suprasti ir nustatyti prioritetus vartotojo patirčiai remiantis failo atidarymo operacijos informacija, pvz., vietinėmis kategorijomis „ServiceType“ ir kurioje taikomosios programos vietoje naudotojas pateikė prašymą atidaryti failą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1336">The event records when a file open operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file open operation information such as location categories “ServiceType” and from where within Application the user requested to open a file.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1337">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1337">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1338">**Data_IsCandidateDropboxFile** – tai yra Bulio logikos reikšmė, kuri registruojama, jei tikrinant failo kelią, manome, kad jis gali būti iš aplanko, kuris sinchronizuotas saugyklos „DropBox“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1338">**Data_IsCandidateDropboxFile** - This is a Boolean value that is logged if by inspecting the path of the file we think it might be from a folder that is sync’d by Drop Box.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1339">**Data_IsSignedIn** – ar failo įrašymo metu vartotojas yra prisijungęs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1339">**Data_IsSignedIn** - Whether or not a user is signed in when the file is saved.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1340">**Data_OpenReason** – atviroji priežastis yra skaitinė reikšmė, nurodanti vietą, iš kurios taikomojoje programoje vartotojas atidarė failą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1340">**Data_OpenReason** - The open reason is a numerical value that indicates from where within the application a user opened a file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1341">**Data_ServiceType** – failo vietos, pvz., „SharePoint“, „OneDrive“, „Local“, „WOPI“ ir t. t., abstraktus skaitinis kategorizavimas, ir aiškus nurodymas, kad tai nėra faktinė failo vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1341">**Data_ServiceType** - An abstract numerical categorization of the location of a file like “SharePoint”, “OneDrive”, “Local”, “WOPI”, etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_fileoperations_savetourl"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1342">Office_DocsUI_FileOperations_SaveToURL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1342">Office_DocsUI_FileOperations_SaveToURL</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1343">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1343">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1344">Įvykių įrašai, kai vykdoma operacija „įrašyti kaip“, naudojama suprasti ir nustatyti prioritetus vartotojo patirčiai remiantis failo operacijos informacija, pvz., vietinėmis kategorijomis ir pirmaisiais keturiais plėtinio simboliais.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1344">The event records when a “save as” operation takes place and is used to understand and prioritize user-experiences based on file operation information such as location categories and the first four characters of the extension.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1345">Operacija „įrašyti kaip“ vykdoma, kai vartotojas sukuria naują failą ir įrašo jį pirmą kartą arba išsaugo esamo failo kopiją naujoje vietoje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1345">A “save as” operation occurs whenever a user creates a new file and saves it for the first time or saves a copy of an existing file to a new location.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1346">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1346">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1347">**Data_FileExtension** – pirmi keturi naujo failo plėtinio simboliai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1347">**Data_FileExtension** - The first four characters of the new file’s extension.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1348">**Data_IsNewFileCreation** – nurodo, ar įrašymo operacija skirta naujam failui, ar esamo failo kopijai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1348">**Data_IsNewFileCreation** - Indicates if the save operation is for a new file or a copy of an existing file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1349">**Data_IsSignedIn** – ar failo įrašymo metu vartotojas yra prisijungęs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1349">**Data_IsSignedIn** - Whether or not a user is signed in when the file is saved.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1350">**Data_SaveErrorCode** – skaitinė reikšmė, nustatoma įvykus klaidai, kad padėtų nustatyti klaidos tipą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1350">**Data_SaveErrorCode** - A numerical value that is set if there is an error to help identify the kind of error.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1351">**Data_SaveErrorDomain** – nurodo SaveErrorCode domeną, kaip apibrėžta „Apple“ SaveErrorDomains – „yra pasirenkamos eilutės, skirtos kodų grupėms atskirti".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1351">**Data_SaveErrorDomain** - Specifies the domain of the SaveErrorCode as defined by Apple SaveErrorDomains “are arbitrary strings used to differentiate groups of codes”.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1352">**Data_SaveLocation** – failo vietos, pvz., „SharePoint“, „OneDrive“, „Local“, „WOPI“ ir t. t., abstraktus kategorizavimas, ir aiškus nurodymas, kad tai nėra faktinė failo vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1352">**Data_SaveLocation** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like “SharePoint”, “OneDrive”, “Local”, “WOPI”, etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1353">**Data_SaveOperationType** – skaitinė reikšmė, apibrėžta „Apple“ NSSaveOperationType reikšmių grupėje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1353">**Data_SaveOperationType** - A numerical value defined by Apple’s NSSaveOperationType group of values.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_sharingui_cloudupsellshown"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1354">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_CloudUpsellShown</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1354">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_CloudUpsellShown</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1355">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1355">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1356">Šis įvykis įrašo, kada vartotojas peržvelgia papildomo debesies srauto pardavimo dokumentą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1356">This event records when a user goes through the document upsell to cloud flow.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1357">Šie duomenys naudojami siekiant geriau suprasti ir nustatyti vartotojo patirčių prioritetus, susijusius su dokumentų perkėlimu į debesį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1357">This data is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences relating to moving documents to cloud locations.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1358">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1358">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1359">**Data_FileStyle** – skaitinė reikšmė, nurodanti, koks scenarijus buvo naudojamas papildomo pardavimo patirties rodymui, pvz., automatinio įrašymo jungiklio ar bendrinimo mygtuko.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1359">**Data_FileStyle** - A numerical value that indicates from what scenario the upsell experience was shown like from an autosave toggle or a share button.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1360">**Data_FileType** – pirmi keturi esamo failo plėtinio simboliai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1360">**Data_FileType** - The first four characters of the current file’s extension.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1361">**Data_InDocStage** – Bulio logika, nurodanti, ar papildomo pardavimo patirtis rodoma iš dokumentų galerijos ar dokumento lango.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1361">**Data_InDocStage** - A Boolean that indicates if the upsell experience is shown from the Document Gallery or from within a document window.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1362">**Data_IsDocumentOpened** – Bulio logika, nurodanti, ar taip pat atidarytas esamas dokumentas, kuriame rodoma papildomo pardavimo patirtis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1362">**Data_IsDocumentOpened** - A Boolean that indicates if the current document for which the upsell experience is being shown is also open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1363">**Data_IsDraft** – Bulio logika, nurodanti, ar esamas failas kada nors buvo įrašytas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1363">**Data_IsDraft** - A Boolean that indicates if the current file has ever been saved.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1364">**Data_IsSheetModal** – Bulio logika, nurodanti, ar papildomo pardavimo patirtis buvo pateikta modališkai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1364">**Data_IsSheetModal** - A Boolean that indicates if the upsell experience was presented modally or not.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_sharingui_cloudupsellupload"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1365">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_CloudUpsellUpload</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1365">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_CloudUpsellUpload</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1366">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1366">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1367">Šis įvykis fiksuoja kada vartotojas pasirenka nusiųsti naują ar vietinį failą į debesį ir šios operacijos rezultatą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1367">This event records when a user chooses to upload a new or local file to the cloud and the result of that operation.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1368">Šie duomenys naudojami siekiant geriau suprasti ir nustatyti vartotojo patirčių prioritetus, susijusius su dokumentų perkėlimu į debesį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1368">This data is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences relating to moving documents to cloud locations.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1369">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1369">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1370">**Data_FileStyle** – skaitinė reikšmė, nurodanti, koks scenarijus buvo naudojamas papildomo pardavimo patirties rodymui, pavyzdžiui, automatinio įrašymo jungiklio ar bendrinimo mygtuko.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1370">**Data_FileStyle** - A numerical value that indicates from what scenario the upsell experience was shown like an autosave toggle or a share button.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1371">**Data_FileType** – pirmi keturi esamo failo plėtinio simboliai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1371">**Data_FileType** - The first four characters of the current file’s extension.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1372">**Data_InDocStage** – Bulio logika, nurodanti, ar papildomo pardavimo patirtis rodoma iš dokumentų galerijos ar dokumento lango.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1372">**Data_InDocStage** - A Boolean that indicates if the upsell experience is shown from the Document Gallery or from within a document window.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1373">**Data_IsDefaultServiceLocation** – Bulio logikos reikšmė, nurodanti, ar pasirinkta dokumento įkėlimo vieta yra numatytoji vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1373">**Data_IsDefaultServiceLocation** - A Boolean value that indicates if the selected location to upload the document to is the default location.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1374">**Data_IsDocumentOpened** – Bulio logika, nurodanti, ar taip pat atidarytas esamas dokumentas, kuriame rodoma papildomo pardavimo patirtis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1374">**Data_IsDocumentOpened** - A Boolean that indicates if the current document for which the upsell experience is being shown is also open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1375">**Data_IsDraft** – Bulio logika, nurodanti, ar esamas failas kada nors buvo įrašytas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1375">**Data_IsDraft** - A Boolean that indicates if the current file has ever been saved.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1376">**Data_IsSheetModal** – Bulio logika, nurodanti, ar papildomo pardavimo patirtis buvo pateikta modališkai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1376">**Data_IsSheetModal** - A Boolean that indicates if the upsell experience was presented modally or not.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1377">**Data_LocationServiceType** – failo vietos, pvz., „SharePoint“, „OneDrive“, „Local“, „WOPI“ ir t. t., abstraktus kategorizavimas, ir aiškus nurodymas, kad tai nėra faktinė failo vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1377">**Data_LocationServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like “SharePoint”, “OneDrive”, “Local”, “WOPI”, etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1378">**Data_UploadAction** – užprogramuota eilutė, nurodanti, ar nusiuntimas buvo perkėlimo, ar kopijavimo operacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1378">**Data_UploadAction** - A hard coded string that indicates whether the upload was a move or a copy operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1379">**Data_UploadResult** – užprogramuota eilutė, nurodanti mėginimo nusiųsti rezultatą, įskaitant, bet neapsiribojant parametrais „Success", „UserCancelledUpload“ ir „PreAuthFailed“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1379">**Data_UploadResult** - A hard coded string that indicates the result of the attempt to upload including but not limited to ‘’Success”, “UserCancelledUpload”, and “PreAuthFailed”.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_sharingui_copylinkoperation"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1380">Office.Security.SecureReaderHost.OpenInOSR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1380">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_CopyLinkOperation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1381">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1381">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1382">Šis įvykis fiksuoja, kada vartotojas pasirenka dokumento bendrinimą sugeneruodamas nuorodą į debesies dokumentą ir yra naudojamas norint geriau suprasti ir nustatyti vartotojo patirties prioritetus, atsižvelgiant į dokumentų bendrinimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1382">This event records when a user chooses to share a document by generating a link to a cloud document and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on sharing documents.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1383">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1383">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1384">**Data_ ServiceType** – failo vietos, pvz., „SharePoint“, „OneDrive“, „Local“, „WOPI“ ir t. t., abstraktus kategorizavimas, ir aiškus nurodymas, kad tai nėra faktinė failo vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1384">**Data_ ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like “SharePoint”, “OneDrive”, “Local”, “WOPI”, etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1385">**Data_LinkType** – užprogramuota eilutė, aprašanti kvietimo operacijos rūšį, pvz., „ViewOnly“ ir „ViewAndEdit“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1385">**Data_LinkType** - A hard coded string that describes the kind of invite operation performed like “ViewOnly” and “ViewAndEdit”.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1386">**Data_ShareScenario** – užprogramuota eilutė, aprašanti, ar failas buvo bendrintas iš taikomosios programos vartotojo sąsajos, įskaitant, bet neapsiribojant „FileMenu“, „OpenTabShareActionMenu“ ar „RecentTabShareActionMenu“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1386">**Data_ShareScenario** - A hard-coded string description of where within the application’s user interface the file is being shared from including but not limited to, “FileMenu”, “OpenTabShareActionMenu”, “RecentTabShareActionMenu”.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_sharingui_docsuionedriveshare"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1387">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_DocsUIOneDriveShare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1387">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_DocsUIOneDriveShare</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1388">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1388">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1389">Šis įvykis fiksuoja, kada vartotojas pasirenka bendrinti debesies dokumentą naudodamas „OneDrive“ bendrinimo patirtį ir yra naudojamas norint geriau suprasti ir nustatyti vartotojo patirties prioritetus, atsižvelgiant į dokumentų bendrinimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1389">This event records when a user chooses to share a cloud document using the OneDrive sharing experience and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on sharing documents.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1390">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1390">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1391">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareError** – jei bendrinimo patirties metu įvyksta klaida, tai yra skaitinė reikšmė, padedanti nustatyti trikties priežastį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1391">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareError** - If the sharing experience experiences an error this is a numerical value to help identify the reason for the failure.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1392">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareGrantAccessResult** – Bulio logikos reikšmė. Kai yra teisinga, nurodo, kad sėkmingai įvykdyta paprasta bendrinimo operacija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1392">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareGrantAccessResult** - A Boolean value that when true indicates that a lightweight sharing operation successfully completed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1393">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareSuccessType** – sėkmingai užbaigus bendrinimo operaciją, tai yra skaitinė reikšmė, naudojama nustatyti atliktos bendrinimo operacijos tipą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1393">**Data_ODSPShareWebviewShareSuccessType** - When a share operation successfully completes this is a numerical value used to determine what kind of sharing operation was completed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1394">**Data_WebViewInfoResult** – jei nepavyko įkelti vartotojo sąsajos, tai yra skaitinė reikšmė, padedanti nustatyti trikties priežastį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1394">**Data_WebViewInfoResult** - If the user interface fails to load this is a numerical value to help identify the reason for the failure.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1395">**Data_WebViewLoadTimeInMs** – skaitinė reikšmė, kuri registruoja laiką, reikalingą įkelti žiniatinklio vartotojo sąsają.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1395">**Data_WebViewLoadTimeInMs** - A numerical value that records the amount of time it took for the web user interface to load.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_sharingui_invitepeople"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1396">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_InvitePeople</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1396">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_InvitePeople</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1397">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1397">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1398">Šis įvykis fiksuoja, kada vartotojas pasirenka žmonių kvietimą prisijungti prie debesies dokumento ir yra naudojamas norint geriau suprasti ir nustatyti vartotojo patirties prioritetus, atsižvelgiant į dokumentų bendrinimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1398">This event records when a user chooses to invite people to a cloud document and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on sharing documents.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1399">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1399">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1400">**Data_ ServiceType** – failo vietos, pvz., „SharePoint“, „OneDrive“, „Local“, „WOPI“ ir t. t., abstraktus kategorizavimas, ir aiškus nurodymas, kad tai nėra faktinė failo vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1400">**Data_ ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like “SharePoint”, “OneDrive”, “Local”, “WOPI”, etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1401">**Data_InviteeCount** – bendras kontaktų, pakviestų prisijungti prie dokumento atliekant vieną kvietimo veiksmą, skaičius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1401">**Data_InviteeCount** - The total number of contacts invited to a document in one invite action.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1402">**Data_LinkType** – užprogramuota eilutė, aprašanti kvietimo operacijos rūšį, pvz., „ViewOnly“ ir „ViewAndEdit“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1402">**Data_LinkType** - A hard-coded string that describes the kind of invite operation performed like “ViewOnly” and “ViewAndEdit”.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1403">**Data_MessageLength** – bendras išsiųsto pakvietimo pranešimo simbolių skaičius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1403">**Data_MessageLength** - A numerical count of the total number of characters sent in the invite message.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1404">**Data_ShareScenario** – užprogramuota eilutė, aprašanti, ar failas buvo bendrintas iš taikomosios programos vartotojo sąsajos, įskaitant, bet neapsiribojant „FileMenu“, „OpenTabShareActionMenu“ ar „RecentTabShareActionMenu“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1404">**Data_ShareScenario** - A hard coded string description of where within the application’s user interface the file is being shared from including but not limited to, “FileMenu”, “OpenTabShareActionMenu”, “RecentTabShareActionMenu”.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_sharingui_sendacopyoperation"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1405">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_SendACopyOperation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1405">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_SendACopyOperation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1406">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1406">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1407">Įvykis fiksuoja, kada vartotojas pasirenka siųsti dokumento kopiją ir yra naudojamas norint geriau suprasti ir nustatyti vartotojo patirties prioritetus, atsižvelgiant į dokumentų bendrinimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1407">The event records when a user chooses to send a copy of a document and is used to better understand and prioritize user-experiences based on sharing documents.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1408">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1408">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1409">**Data_IsHomeTabEnabled** – Bulio logikos reikšmė, nurodanti, ar skirtukas Pagrindinis šiuo metu pasiekiamas vartotojui.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1409">**Data_IsHomeTabEnabled** - A Boolean value that indicates if the Home tab is currently available to the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1410">**Data_IsRecommendedEnabled** – Bulio logikos reikšmė, nurodanti, ar patirtis Rekomenduojama šiuo metu pasiekiamas vartotojui.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1410">**Data_IsRecommendedEnabled** - A Boolean value that indicates if the “Recommended” experience is currently available to the user.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1411">**Data_OperationType** – skaitinė reikšmė, nurodanti vykdomos kopijos siuntimo operacijos tipą, pvz., siųsti kopiją el. paštu arba nusiųsti kopiją naudojantis „Apple“ bendrinimo valdymo funkcija.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1411">**Data_OperationType** - A numerical value to indicate what kind of send a copy operation is taking place like sending a copy in an email or sending a copy through Apple’s share control.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1412">**Data_ServiceType** – failo vietos, pvz., „SharePoint“, „OneDrive“, „Local“, „WOPI“ ir t. t., abstraktus kategorizavimas, ir aiškus nurodymas, kad tai nėra faktinė failo vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1412">**Data_ServiceType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like “SharePoint”, “OneDrive”, “Local”, “WOPI”, etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1413">**Data_ShareFileType** – užprogramuotas eilutės aprašas, nurodantis bendrinamo objekto tipą, įskaitant, bet neapsiribojant „Dokumentas“, „PDF“ ar „Paveikslėlis“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1413">**Data_ShareFileType** - A hard coded string description of what type of object is being shared including but not limited to, “Document”, “PDF”, “Picture”.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1414">**Data_ShareScenario** – užprogramuota eilutė, aprašanti, ar failas buvo bendrintas iš taikomosios programos vartotojo sąsajos, įskaitant, bet neapsiribojant „FileMenu“, „OpenTabShareActionMenu“ ar „RecentTabShareActionMenu“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1414">**Data_ShareScenario** - A hard coded string description of where within the application’s user interface the file is being shared from including but not limited to, “FileMenu”, “OpenTabShareActionMenu”, “RecentTabShareActionMenu”.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1415">**Data_SharingService** – Bulio logika, nurodanti, ar failas buvo sukurtas, kai vartotojas ieškojo šablono.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1415">**Data_SharingService** - A Boolean that indicates whether the file was created when the user was searching for a template.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_docsui_sharingui_upsellshare"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1416">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_UpsellShare</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1416">Office_DocsUI_SharingUI_UpsellShare</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1417">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1417">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1418">Šis įvykis įrašo, kai vartotojas peržvelgia papildomo debesies srauto pardavimo dokumentą, kai bando bendrinti dokumentą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1418">This event records when a user goes through the document upsell to cloud flow when trying to share a document.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1419">Šie duomenys naudojami, kad geriau suprasti ir nustatyti vartotojo patirčių prioritetus, susijusius su dokumentų perkėlimu į debesį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1419">This data is used to better understand and prioritize user experiences relating to moving documents to cloud locations.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1420">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1420">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1421">**Data_FileOperationResult** – skaitinė reikšmė, nurodanti, ar pavyko atlikti operaciją.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1421">**Data_FileOperationResult** - A numerical value to indicate whether the operation succeeded.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1422">**Data_HostedFromDocStage** – Bulio logika, nurodanti, ar vartotojas peržiūri debesies srauto reklamą naudodami DocStage funkcijas arba iš atidaryto dokumento.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1422">**Data_HostedFromDocStage** - A Boolean to indicate if a user is going through the upsell to cloud flow from the DocStage experience or from an open document.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1423">**Data_isLocalCopyOn** – Bulio logika, nurodanti, ar naudoti pasirinko saugoti dokumento vietinę kopiją, kuri buvo nusiųsta į debesį arba perkelti esamą dokumentą į debesį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1423">**Data_isLocalCopyOn** - A Boolean to indicate if the use chose to keep a local copy of the document being uploaded to a cloud location or move the existing document to a cloud location.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1424">**Data_NewFileType** – naujos failo vietos, pvz., „SharePoint“, „OneDrive“, „Local“, „WOPI“ ir t. t., abstraktus kategorizavimas, ir aiškus nurodymas, kad tai nėra faktinė failo vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1424">**Data_NewFileType** - An abstract categorization of the location of the new location of the file like “SharePoint”, “OneDrive”, “Local”, “WOPI”, etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1425">**Data_OriginalFileType** – failo vietos, pvz., „SharePoint“, „OneDrive“, „Local“, „WOPI“ ir t. t., abstraktus kategorizavimas, ir aiškus nurodymas, kad tai nėra faktinė failo vieta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1425">**Data_OriginalFileType** - An abstract categorization of the location of a file like “SharePoint”, “OneDrive”, “Local”, “WOPI”, etc., and explicitly not the actual location of the file.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1426">**Data_UploadButtonPressed** – Bulio logika, nurodanti, ar vartotojas pasirinko įkelti dabartinį dokumentą į vietą debesyje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1426">**Data_UploadButtonPressed** - A Boolean to indicate if the user chose to upload the current document to a cloud location.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1427">**Data_UploadError** – skaitinė reikšmė, nurodanti klaidos tipą, jei įkėlimo operacijos atlikti nepavyksta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1427">**Data_UploadError** - A numerical value that indicates the kind of error that occurred if an upload operation fails.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1428">**Data_UpsellAppearsFromDelegate** – Bulio logikos reikšmė, nurodanti, ar rodinys buvo rodomas bendrinamame meniu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1428">**Data_UpsellAppearsFromDelegate** - A Boolean value to indicate if the view was shown from the share menu.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1454">Leidžia mums žinoti, ar failas iš FIO sluoksnio atidarytas sėkmingai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1454">Allows us to know if a file successfully opened from the FIO Layer.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1455">Naudojama funkcijos sveikatai užtikrinti ir stebėti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1455">Used for feature health and monitoring.</span></span>
