#### <a name="officefileiocsiccachedfilecsisavefilebasic"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1578">Office.FileIO.CSI.CCachedFileCsiSaveFileBasic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1578">Office.FileIO.CSI.CCachedFileCsiSaveFileBasic</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1579">Leidžia mums žinoti, ar failas iš FIO sluoksnio įrašytas sėkmingai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1579">Allows us to know if a file was successfully saved from the FIO Layer.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1580">Naudojama funkcijos sveikatai užtikrinti ir stebėti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1580">Used for Feature Health and monitoring.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1581">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1581">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1582">**Activity.Group –** žymė, leidžianti nustatyti stebimų įvykių rinkinį, grupuojamą sėkmingam atlikimui valdyti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1582">**Activity.Group -** tag that allows a set of monitoring events to be grouped to manage overall success</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1583">**Activity.IsHVA –** žyma, nurodanti, kad įvykis yra kritinis vartotojų sėkmingiems veiksmams užtikrinti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1583">**Activity.IsHVA -** flag to indicate that event is critical to user success</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1584">**Data.AsyncOpen –** žyma, nurodanti, kad dokumentas buvo atidarytas su turiniu, gautu po pagrindinės dalies atidarymo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1584">**Data.AsyncOpen -** flag to indicate that the document was opened with content that arrived after the main body was opened</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1585">**Data.BaseDownloadTriggered –** keičia sekimo diagnostiką, nurodančią, kad buvo užklausta pagrindinė dokumento versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1585">**Data.BaseDownloadTriggered -** Change tracking diagnostic indicating that the base version of the document was requested</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1586">**Data.BlockAutoUploadReasons –** užblokuotos nusiuntimo būsenos priežasčių kodai (pvz. automatinis įrašymas išjungtas, dokumentas perkeliamas)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1586">**Data.BlockAutoUploadReasons -** Reason codes for blocked upload state (e.g. Autosave is turned off, the document is transitioning)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1587">**Data.BlockUploadDueToFailedSaveAsOverExisting –** nusiuntimas užblokuotas, nes kartojant jis nepavyks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1587">**Data.BlockUploadDueToFailedSaveAsOverExisting -** Upload is blocked as it would fail if retried</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1588">**Data.CacheFileId –** prisijungia prie „Office“ dokumentų talpyklos telemetrijos, kad atliktų vartotojo patiriamų talpyklos problemų analizę</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1588">**Data.CacheFileId -** connects to Office Document Cache telemetry to enable impact analysis of cache issues on the user experience</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1589">**Data.ChartType –** nebenaudojamas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1589">**Data.ChartType -** Obsolete</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1590">**Data.CoAuthStatus –** informuoja apie dokumento bendradarbiavimo būseną įrašant</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1590">**Data.CoAuthStatus -** reports collaborative status of the document on Save</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1591">**Data.CoauthUpdatesContext –** pranešamas kontekstas (suliejimas / laipsniškas atidarymas)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1591">**Data.CoauthUpdatesContext -** reports context (Merge/Incremental Open)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1592">**Data.CountOfMultiRoundTripsDownload –** kelionių į serverį ir atgal skaičius, naudotas veikimo triktims ir tinklo problemoms šalinti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1592">**Data.CountOfMultiRoundTripsDownload -** Count of round trips to the server used to troubleshoot performance and network issues</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1601">**Data.Doc.AsyncOpenKind** – nurodo, ar debesies dokumento talpykloje esanti versija buvo atidaryta, ir kuri asinchroninio atnaujinimo logika buvo naudojama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1601">**Data.Doc.AsyncOpenKind –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

#### <a name="officefindtimeappfailedtostart"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1725">Office.FindTime.AppFailedToStart</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1725">Office.FindTime.AppFailedToStart</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1726">Surinkta, kai taikomoji programa nepasileidžia dėl netikėtos klaidos paleidimo metu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1726">Collected when app fails to start due to an unexpected error during startup.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1727">Naudojama sekti išimtis ir gedimus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1727">Used to track exceptions & crashes.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1728">Padeda stebėti ir derinti taikomosios programos sveikatą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1728">Helps monitor & debug app health.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1729">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1729">The following fields are collected:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1730">**DateTime** – laiko žyma, kada įvykis užregistruotas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1730">**DateTime** - Timestamp of when the event is logged</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1731">**EventName** – užregistruoto įvykio pavadinimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1731">**EventName** - The name of the event being logged</span></span>

#### <a name="office_firstrun_apple_activationresult"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1732">Office_FirstRun_Apple_ActivationResult</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1732">Office_FirstRun_Apple_ActivationResult</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1733">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1733">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1734">Įvykis naudojamas mūsų taikomosios programos aktyvinimo srauto sveikatai stebėti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1734">The event is used to monitor the health of our application activation flow.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1735">Renkame duomenis, kad išsiaiškintume „O365“ prenumeratos aktyvinimo rezultatus kartu su aktyvinimui naudojamu srautu (pirmojo sistemos paleidimo programa (FRE), srautas taikomojoje programoje, pirkimas ir t. t.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1735">We collect data to figure out the outcome of the O365 subscription activation along with the flow used to activate (First Run Experience, In-App-Flow, Purchase, etc.).</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1736">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1736">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1737">**Data_ActivationStatusCollectionTime** – laiko žyma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1737">**Data_ActivationStatusCollectionTime** – A timestamp</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1738">**Data_ActivationStatusError** – aktyvinimo klaidos kodas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1738">**Data_ActivationStatusError** – An activation error code.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1739">**Data_ActivationStatusFlowType** – skaitinė reikšmė, nurodanti aktyvinimo srauto tipą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1739">**Data_ActivationStatusFlowType** – A numeric value indicating the type of activation flow</span></span>

#### <a name="office_firstrun_apple_activationstatus"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1740">Office_FirstRun_Apple_ActivationStatus</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1740">Office_FirstRun_Apple_ActivationStatus</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1741">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1741">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1742">Įvykis naudojamas išsiaiškinti „O365“ prenumeratos aktyvinimo rezultatus kartu su aktyvinimui naudojamu srautu (pirmojo sistemos paleidimo programa, srautas taikomojoje programoje, pirkimas ir t. t.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1742">The event is used to figure out the outcome of the O365 subscription activation along with the flow used to activate (FRE, InApp, Purchase, etc.).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1743">Renkame duomenis, kuriuose yra aktyvinimo tipas, srauto tipas (FRE/DocStage/pirkimas) ir „Office“ licencijavimo tarnybos ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1743">We collect data containing the Activation type, flow type (FRE/DocStage/Purchase) and Office Licensing Service ID.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1744">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1744">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1745">**Data_ActivationTypeCollectionTime** – laiko žyma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1745">**Data_ActivationTypeCollectionTime** – A timestamp</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1746">**Data_ActivationTypeFlowType** – skaitinė reikšmė, nurodanti aktyvinimo srauto tipą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1746">**Data_ActivationTypeFlowType** – A numeric value indicating the type of activation flow</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1747">**Data_ActivationTypeOLSLicense** – licencijos identifikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1747">**Data_ActivationTypeOLSLicense** – An identifier of the License</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1748">**Data_ActivationTypeStatus** – aktyvinimo būsenos kodas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1748">**Data_ActivationTypeStatus** – An activation status code.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_firstrun_apple_firstruncomplete"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1749">Office_FirstRun_Apple_FirstRunComplete</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1749">Office_FirstRun_Apple_FirstRunComplete</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1881">**Data.UserInfo.OMSTenantId** – nuomotojas, su kuriuo yra susieta vartotojo prenumerata.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1881">**Data.UserInfo.OMSTenantId** - The tenant that a user’s subscription is tied to.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1882">Leidžia mums klasifikuoti problemas ir nustatyti, ar problema yra plačiai paplitusi, ar izoliuota atskirų nuomotojų grupėje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1882">Allows us to classify issues and identify whether a problem is widespread or isolated to a set of users or a specific tenant</span></span>

#### <a name="officemanageabilityclient-fetchpolicyprechecks"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1900">Office.Manageability.Client Fetch.PolicyPreChecks</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1900">Office.Manageability.Client Fetch.PolicyPreChecks</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1901">Svarbu, kad telemetrija sektų sėkmingą\\nesėkmingą debesies strategijos iškvietimą pirminiam tikrinimui patvirtinti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1901">Critical telemetry to track failure\\success for cloud policy fetch precheck validation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1902">ExitReason turi surašytuvo žemėlapį, iš anksto tikrinantį nepavykusią sąlygą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1902">ExitReason contains an enumerator map to the pre-check condition that failed.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-1903">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-1903">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2128">Surinkta uždarius „PowerPoint“ pateiktis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2128">Collected when PowerPoint presentations are closed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2129">Joje yra informacija, reikalinga tinkamai nustatyti ir diagnozuoti problemas, įvykusias uždarymo proceso metu, ir kurios yra vartotojo duomenų išlaikymo ir sinchronizavimo ribojimo priežastimi.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2129">It contains the information needed to be able to properly investigate and diagnose issues that happen through the close process which entail persisting and syncing the user's data.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2130">„Microsoft“ naudoja šiuos duomenis, kad užtikrintų, jog uždarymas veikia kaip priklauso ir vartotojo turinys yra sėkmingai išlaikomas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2130">Microsoft uses this data to ensure that close is working as expected and user content is successfully being persisted.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2131">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2131">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2132">**Data\_AddDocTelemetryResult:long –** ar šis žurnalo įrašas turi visą reikiamą dokumento telemetriją (Data\_Doc\_\* laukus)?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2132">**Data\_AddDocTelemetryResult:long -** Does this log entry have all necessary document telemetry (Data\_Doc\_\* fields)?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2133">Jei ne, kodėl?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2133">If not, why?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2134">**Data\_AutoSaveDisabledReasons:string –** iš anksto nustatytų reikšmių, nurodančių kodėl šiame dokumente buvo išjungtas automatinis įrašymas, rinkinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2134">**Data\_AutoSaveDisabledReasons:string -** Predefined set of values of why was autosave disabled on this document?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2135">(Suliejomo klaida, įrašymo klaida, grupės strategija ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2135">(Merge error, Save error, Group policy etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2136">**Data\_CloseReason:long –** kaip buvo vykdomas uždarymas?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2136">**Data\_CloseReason:long -** How was close performed?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2137">Uždarant dokumentą?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2137">Closing document?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2138">Uždarant programą?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2138">Closing app?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2139">**Data\_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long –** neapdorojamų išimčių skaičius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2139">**Data\_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long -** Number of unhandled exceptions</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2140">**Data\_DetachedDuration:long –** veiklos atskyrimo / neveikimo trukmė</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2140">**Data\_DetachedDuration:long -** Time for which Activity was detached/not running</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2141">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode:long –** kaip šis dokumentas buvo atidarytas (tik skaityti | skaityti ir rašyti)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2141">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode:long -** How was this document opened (Read only | read write)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2142">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons:long –** iš anksto apibrėžtų reikšmių, nurodančių dokumento atidarymo pagalbiniu skaitymo režimu priežastis, rinkinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2142">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons:long -** Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2143">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long** – nurodo, ar debesies dokumento talpykloje esanti versija buvo atidaryta, ir kuri asinchroninio atnaujinimo logika buvo naudojama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2143">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2144">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType:long –** kaip dokumentas saugomas programoje „SharePoint“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2144">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType:long -** How is document stored in SharePoint</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2145">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState:long –** dokumento įmonės duomenų apsaugos būsena</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2145">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState:long -** Enterprise Data Protection state of document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2146">**Data\_Doc\_Ext:string –** dokumento plėtinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2146">**Data\_Doc\_Ext:string -** Document extension</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2147">**Data\_Doc\_Extension:string –** dokumento plėtinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2147">**Data\_Doc\_Extension:string -** Document extension</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2148">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat:long –** iš anksto nustatytų failo formato reikšmių rinkinys (detalesnis nei plėtinio)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2148">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat:long -** Predefined set of values of format of file (more granular than extension)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2149">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn:string –** vieta, kurioje saugomas dokumentas (SharePoint.com, live.net) galima tik „Office 365“ domenams</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2149">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn:string -** Where is document stored (SharePoint.com, live.net), only available for Office 365 domains</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointdocoperationnewdocument"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2198">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.NewDocument</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2198">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.NewDocument</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2199">Surinkta, „PowerPoint“ naujos pateikties sukūrimo metu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2199">Collected when PowerPoint creates a new presentation.</span></span><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2200"> Apima sėkmingą klaidos šalinimą ir našumo metrikas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2200"> Includes success failure and performance metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2201">Ši informacija naudojama užtikrinti, kad galime sukurti failus sėkmingai, nemažinant našumo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2201">This information is used to ensure we can create files successfully and with no degradation in performance.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2202">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2202">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2203">**NewDocumentType** – ar naujas dokumentas sukurtas naudojant šabloną, ar sukurtas tik tuščias dokumentas?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2203">**NewDocumentType** – Whether new document is created from template or just created blank?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2204">**FLifeguarded** – dokumento apsauga (funkcija, atkurianti sugadintos būsenos dokumentą nepateikdami raginimo vartotojui)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2204">**FLifeguarded** – Is document life guarded (feature that restores corrupt document state without prompting user)</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointdocoperationopencompleteprotocol"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2205">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.OpenCompleteProtocol</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2205">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.OpenCompleteProtocol</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2206">Surinkta „PowerPoint“ atidarius pateiktis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2206">Collected when PowerPoint opens presentations.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2207">Joje yra informacija, reikalinga tinkamai nustatyti ir diagnozuoti problemas, įvykusias atidarymo proceso baigiamosiose stadijose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2207">It contains the information needed to be able to properly investigate and diagnose issues that happen through the end stages of the open process.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2208">„Microsoft“ naudoja šiuos duomenis užtikrinti, jog funkcija veikia kaip numatyta ir pateikčių atidarymas nesuprastėjo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2208">Microsoft uses this data to ensure the feature is working as expected and there is no degradation to opening presentations.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2209">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2209">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2210">**Data\_AntiVirusScanMethod:long –** iš anksto apibrėžtas antivirusinės programos nuskaitymo tipo reikšmių rinkinys (IOAV, AMSI, None ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2210">**Data\_AntiVirusScanMethod:long -** Predefined set of values of type of AntiVirus scanned (IOAV, AMSI, None etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2211">**Data\_AntiVirusScanStatus:long –** iš anksto apibrėžtas antivirusinės programos nuskaitymo, atliekamo atidarant kiekvieną dokumentą, reikšmių rinkinys (NoThreatsDetected, Failed, MalwareDetected ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2211">**Data\_AntiVirusScanStatus:long -** Predefined set of values of anti-virus scan that happens for every document opened (NoThreatsDetected, Failed, MalwareDetected etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2212">**Data\_CloseAndReopen:bool –** ar šis dokumentas buvo uždarytas, ar pakartotinai atidarytas?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2212">**Data\_CloseAndReopen:bool -** Was this document closed and reopened?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2213">**Data\_DetachedDuration:long –** veiklos atskyrimo / neveikimo trukmė</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2213">**Data\_DetachedDuration:long -** Time for which Activity was detached/not running</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2214">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode:long –** kaip šis dokumentas buvo atidarytas (tik skaityti | skaityti ir rašyti)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2214">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode:long -** How was this document opened (Read only | read write)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2215">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons:long –** iš anksto apibrėžtų reikšmių, nurodančių dokumento atidarymo pagalbiniu skaitymo režimu priežastis, rinkinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2215">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons:long -** Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2216">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long** – nurodo, ar debesies dokumento talpykloje esanti versija buvo atidaryta, ir kuri asinchroninio atnaujinimo logika buvo naudojama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2216">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2217">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType:long –** kaip dokumentas saugomas programoje „SharePoint“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2217">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType:long -** How is document stored in SharePoint</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointdocoperationsave"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2265">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.Save</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2265">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.Save</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2266">Surinkti kiekvieną kartą, kai „PowerPoint“ įrašo naudodama modernų kodo kelią.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2266">Collected whenever PowerPoint performs a save using the modern code path.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2267">Apima sėkmingai arba nesėkmingai atlikto našumo metrikų ir susijusio dokumento metaduomenų įrašymo rezultato tipą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2267">Includes success or failure result type of save performance metrics and relevant document metadata.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2268"> Nepavykus įrašymui, duomenys gali būti prarasti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2268"> Failures in save can result in data loss.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2269">„Microsoft“ naudoja šiuos duomenis, kad užtikrintų, jog funkcija veikia kaip priklauso ir vartotojo turinys yra sėkmingai išlaikomas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2269">Microsoft uses this data to ensure the feature is working as expected and user content is successfully being persisted.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2270">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2270">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2271">**Data\_AddDocTelemetryResult:long –** ar šis žurnalo įrašas turi visą reikiamą dokumento telemetriją (Data\_Doc\_\* laukus)?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2271">**Data\_AddDocTelemetryResult:long -** Does this log entry have all necessary document telemetry (Data\_Doc\_\* fields)?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2272">Jei ne, kodėl?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2272">If not, why?</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2273">**Data\_BeforeSaveEvent:long –** laikas, skirtas pakelti dokumentą prieš įrašymo įvykį</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2273">**Data\_BeforeSaveEvent:long -** Time taken to raise Document Before Save Event</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2274">**Data\_CheckDownRevSaveTimeMS:long –** laikas, skirtas peržiūrai tikrinti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2274">**Data\_CheckDownRevSaveTimeMS:long -** Time taken to check revision</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2275">**Data\_CheckMacroSaveTimeMS:long –** laikas, skirtas makrokomandoms įrašyti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2275">**Data\_CheckMacroSaveTimeMS:long -** Time taken to save macros</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2276">**Data\_ClearAutoSaveTimeMS:long –** laikas, skirtas automatinio įrašymo žymei valyti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2276">**Data\_ClearAutoSaveTimeMS:long -** Time taken to clear AutoSave flag</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2277">**Data\_ClearDirtyFlagTimeMS:long –** laikas, skirtas dokumento neatnaujintai žymei valyti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2277">**Data\_ClearDirtyFlagTimeMS:long -** Time taken to clear document dirty flag</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2278">**Data\_CloneDocumentTimeMS:long –** laikas, skirtas dokumentą prieš įrašymą klonuoti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2278">**Data\_CloneDocumentTimeMS:long -** Time taken to clone document before starting the save</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2279">**Data\_CommitTransactionTimeMS:long –** laikas, skirtas įrašymo operacijai atlikti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2279">**Data\_CommitTransactionTimeMS:long -** Time taken to commit the save transaction</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2280">**Data\_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long –** veiklos veikimo metu neaptiktos vietinės išimtys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2280">**Data\_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long -** Uncaught native exceptions while activity was running</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2281">**Data\_DetachedDuration:long –** veiklos atskyrimo / neveikimo trukmė</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2281">**Data\_DetachedDuration:long -** Time for which Activity was detached/not running</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2282">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode:long –** kaip šis dokumentas buvo atidarytas (tik skaityti | skaityti ir rašyti)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2282">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode:long -** How was this document opened (Read only | read write)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2283">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons:long –** iš anksto apibrėžtų reikšmių, nurodančių dokumento atidarymo pagalbiniu skaitymo režimu priežastis, rinkinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2283">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons:long -** Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2284">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long** – nurodo, ar debesies dokumento talpykloje esanti versija buvo atidaryta, ir kuri asinchroninio atnaujinimo logika buvo naudojama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2284">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2285">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType:long –** kaip dokumentas saugomas programoje „SharePoint“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2285">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType:long -** How is document stored in SharePoint</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2286">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState:long –** dokumento įmonės duomenų apsaugos būsena</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2286">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState:long -** Enterprise Data Protection state of document</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointdocoperationsaveas"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2351">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.SaveAs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2351">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.SaveAs</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2352">Surinkti kiekvieną kartą, kai „PowerPoint“ atlieka operaciją įrašyti kaip.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2352">Collected whenever PowerPoint performs a Save As.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2353">Apima sėkmingai arba nesėkmingai atlikto našumo metrikų ir susijusio dokumento metaduomenų įrašymo rezultato tipą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2353">Includes success or failure result type of save performance metrics and relevant document metadata.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2354">Nepavykus įrašymui, duomenys gali būti prarasti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2354">Failures in save can result in data loss.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2355">„Microsoft“ naudoja šiuos duomenis, kad užtikrintų, jog funkcija veikia kaip priklauso ir vartotojo turinys yra sėkmingai išlaikomas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2355">Microsoft uses this data to ensure the feature is working as expected and user content is successfully being persisted.</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointdocoperationsavelegacy"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2448">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.SaveLegacy</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2448">Office.PowerPoint.DocOperation.SaveLegacy</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2449">Surinkti kiekvieną kartą, kai „PowerPoint“ įrašo naudodama senesnį kodo kelią.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2449">Collected whenever PowerPoint performs a save using the legacy code path.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2450">Apima sėkmingai arba nesėkmingai atlikto našumo metrikų ir susijusio dokumento metaduomenų įrašymo rezultato tipą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2450">Includes success or failure result type of save performance metrics and relevant document metadata.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2451">Nepavykus įrašymui, duomenys gali būti prarasti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2451">Failures in save can result in data loss.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2452">„Microsoft“ naudoja šiuos duomenis, kad užtikrintų, jog funkcija veikia kaip priklauso ir vartotojo turinys yra sėkmingai išlaikomas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2452">Microsoft uses this data to ensure the feature is working as expected and user content is successfully being persisted.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2453">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2453">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2454">**Data_AddDocTelemetryResult:long** – ar šis žurnalo įrašas turi visą reikiamą dokumento telemetriją (Data_Doc_\* fields)?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2454">**Data_AddDocTelemetryResult:long** - Does this log entry have all necessary document telemetry (Data_Doc_\* fields)?</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2455">Jei ne, kodėl?</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2455">If not, why?</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2456">**Data_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long** – veiklos veikimo metu neaptiktos vietinės išimtys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2456">**Data_CppUncaughtExceptionCount:long** - Uncaught native exceptions while activity was running</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2457">**Data_DetachedDuration:long** – veiklos atskyrimo / neveikimo trukmė</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2457">**Data_DetachedDuration:long** - Time for which Activity was detached/not running</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2458">**Data_Doc_AccessMode:long** – nurodo, kaip šis dokumentas buvo atidarytas (tik skaityti | skaityti ir rašyti)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2458">**Data_Doc_AccessMode:long** - How was this document opened (Read only | read write)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2460">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long** – nurodo, ar debesies dokumento talpykloje esanti versija buvo atidaryta, ir kuri asinchroninio atnaujinimo logika buvo naudojama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2460">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind:long –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2592">Informacijos apie trikti per skaidrių demonstravimą, kuris yra svarbiausia „PowerPoint“ funkcija, rinkimas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2592">Collecting failures during slide show as a key feature for PowerPoint.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2593">„Microsoft“ skaidrių demonstravimo metu renka informaciją apie klaidos įvykimą, kad padėtų tobulinti naudotojo patirtį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2593">Microsoft is collecting when error happens during slide show to help improve user experience on slide show.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2594">„Microsoft“ šiuos duomenis naudoja gauti diagnostinę informaciją apie tai, kur klaida įvyksta, kai vartotojas naudoja skaidrių demonstravimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2594">Microsoft uses this data to get diagnostic information about where the error happens while user is using slide show.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2595">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2595">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2596">**CountOArtErrors** – bendras OArt klaidų skaičius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2596">**CountOArtErrors** - total number of OArt errors</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2597">**CountOtherErrors** – bendras kitų klaidų skaičius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2597">**CountOtherErrors** - total number of other errors</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2598">**CountPPTErrors** – bendras PPT klaidų skaičius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2598">**CountPPTErrors** - total number of PPT errors</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2599">**CountSlideShowErrors** – bendras skaidrių demonstravimo klaidų skaičius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2599">**CountSlideShowErrors** - total number of slide show errors</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2600">**FirstOArtError** – pirma klaida, įvykusi OArt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2600">**FirstOArtError** - first error happened in OArt</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2601">**FirstOtherError** – pirma klaida, įvykusi kitoje srityje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2601">**FirstOtherError** - first error happened in other area</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2602">**FirstPPTError** – pirma klaida, įvykusi PPT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2602">**FirstPPTError** - first error happened in PPT</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2603">**FirstSlideShowError** – pirma klaida, įvykusi skaidrių demonstravimo metu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2603">**FirstSlideShowError** - first error happened in slide show</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2608">**Data_PrintWithSlideNumbers** – Bulio logika, nurodanti, ar vartotojas spausdindamas naudoja skaidrių numerius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2608">**Data_PrintWithSlideNumbers** - Boolean indicating if the user is printing with slide numbers.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2609">**Data_SavePrintLayoutType** – spausdinimo maketo tipas tuo metu, kai pradedama spausdinti arba eksportuoti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2609">**Data_SavePrintLayoutType** - The print layout type at the time of starting the print or export operation.</span></span>

#### <a name="officetargetedmessagingabexperimentmessagetrigger"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2657">Office.TargetedMessaging.ABExperimentMessageTrigger</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2657">Office.TargetedMessaging.ABExperimentMessageTrigger</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2658">Seka, kiek vartotojų gavo BizBar ir dinaminės matomosios tinklalapio srities pranešimus iš TargetedMessagingService (TMS).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2658">Tracks the number of users receiving BizBar and Dynamic Canvas messages from TargetedMessagingService (TMS).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2659">Šie duomenys yra labai svarbūs suprasti, kokius gauna laiškus vartotojai ir kokioje darbinėje srityje, kad galėtume užtikrinti, jog jiems netrūksta jokių pranešimų, kurie gali būti labai svarbūs tolimesniam produkto naudojimui.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2659">This data is critical to understand what messages users are getting and on what surface so that we can ensure they are not missing any messages that may be critical to their continued use of the product.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2660">Taip pat jie reikalingi tiksliai išmatuoti savo bandymų per TMS vykdomų kampanijų atlikimo sėkmingumą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2660">Also needed to accurately measure the success of our experiments and campaigns run through TMS.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2661">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2661">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2662">**Data\_Surface** – darbinės srities, kuriai skirtas šios tarnybos pristatytas pranešimas, pavadinimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2662">**Data\_Surface** – Name of the surface that this service delivered message is meant for</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2663">**Data\_Flight** – ECS/CT testuojamo varianto identifikatorius, naudojamas pranešimui siųsti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2663">**Data\_Flight** – ECS/CT Flight identifier that was used to deliver this message</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2664">**Data\_CampaignId** – kampanijos, kurios dalis yra šis pranešimas, identifikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2664">**Data\_CampaignId** – identifier of the campaign that this message is part of</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2665">**Data\_MessageId** – šios tarnybos, pristačiusios pranešimą, identifikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2665">**Data\_MessageId** – identifier of this service delivered message</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2666">**Data\_TransactionId** – šios operacijos su tarnyba identifikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2666">**Data\_TransactionId** – identifier of this transaction with the service</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2667">**Data\_TriggerPoint** – veiksmas, kuriame šis įvykis buvo užfiksuotas (gauto pranešimo palyginimas su rodomu)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2667">**Data\_TriggerPoint** – The step in which this event was logged (message received vs message displayed)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2744">Renka informaciją apie tai, ar pasirinktos dalies vertimas, kurį vartotojas įjungė Translator SDX, atliktas sėkmingai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2744">Collects success or failure of a selection translation that a user action triggers in the Translator SDX.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2745">Labai svarbu įvertinti vertimo funkcijos sveikatą ir reaguoti į bet kokius sutrikimus, kurie gali atsirasti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2745">This is critical to evaluate the health of the translation feature and react to any outages that might occur.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2746">Naudojama stebėti „Excel“, „PowerPoint“ ir „Word“ scenarijaus „Vertimo pasirinkimas“ sveikatą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2746">Used to monitor the health of the "Translate Selection" scenario in Excel, PowerPoint, Word.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2747">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2747">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

#### <a name="officevisiosharedwritebacktoexcel"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2818">Office.Visio.Shared.WritebackToExcel</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2818">Office.Visio.Shared.WritebackToExcel</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2822">**Data\_ConnectorsBasedOnSequence:bool** - „True“ nurodo jungtis, kurios sukurtos pagrindžiant sekos parametrais</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2822">**Data\_ConnectorsBasedOnSequence:bool** - true means connectors are created based on sequence settings</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2825">**Data\_NoOfShapesAdded:int** - Figūrų, kurios pridėtos įrašant „Excel“ funkcijos kopiją skaičius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2825">**Data\_NoOfShapesAdded:int** - Number of shapes added during writeback to Excel functionality</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2826">**Data\_NoOfShapesDeleted:int** - Figūrų, kurios panakintos įrašant „Excel“ funkcijos kopiją skaičius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2826">**Data\_NoOfShapesDeleted:int** - Number of shapes deleted during writeback to Excel functionality</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2827">**Data\_OverwriteSelected:bool** - „True“ nurodo, ar vartotojas pasirinko duomenų perrašymo parinktį</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2827">**Data\_OverwriteSelected:bool** - true indicate user selected overwrite data option</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2828">**Data\_SourceDataModified:bool** - „True“ nurodo, kad pakeisti šaltinio duomenys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2828">**Data\_SourceDataModified:bool** - true indicates source data is modified</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2829">**Data\_WarningShown:bool** - „True“ reiškia, kad vartotojui rodomas duomenų naujinimo įspėjimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2829">**Data\_WarningShown:bool** - true means data update warning shown to the user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2830">**Data\_WarningShownBecauseOfPresenceOfFormula:bool** - „True“ nurodo vartotojui rodomą įspėjimą dėl formulės programoje „Excel“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2830">**Data\_WarningShownBecauseOfPresenceOfFormula:bool** - true indicates warning shown to the user because of presence of formula in Excel</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2831">**Data\_WarningShownToAddNextStepID:bool** - „True“ nurodo vartotojui rodomą įspėjimą dėl kitų identifikavimo priemonės programoje „Excel“ praleistų veiksmų</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2831">**Data\_WarningShownToAddNextStepID:bool** - true indicates warning show to the user because next step Identifier missing in Excel</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2832">**Data\_WarningShownToConvertToTable:bool** - „True“ nurodo vartotojui rodomą įspėjimą konvertuoti „Excel“ duomenis į lentelės formatą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2832">**Data\_WarningShownToConvertToTable:bool** - true indicates warning shown to the user to convert Excel data to table format</span></span>


#### <a name="officewordexperimentationdocumentstatsoncloseandsuspend"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2833">Office.Word.Experimentation.DocumentStatsOnCloseAndSuspend</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2833">Office.Word.Experimentation.DocumentStatsOnCloseAndSuspend</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2834">Šis įvykis registruoja dokumentų statistiką kiekvienam dokumentui, kai „Office Word“ yra uždaryta ar sustabdyta.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2834">This event logs document statistics for each document when Office Word is closed or suspended.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2835">Įvykis naudojamas norint susieti dokumento keitimus, dydį ir t. t. su dokumento įrašymo, dokumento bendrinimo ir dokumento internetinio bendradarbiavimo klaidomis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2835">The event is used to correlate document edits, size, etc. with document-save, document-share, and document online collaboration errors.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2836">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2836">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2837">**Data_BkmkRefCount** – žymelių nuorodų skaičius dokumente</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2837">**Data_BkmkRefCount** - Number of bookmark references in the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2838">**Data_CharacterCount** – simbolių skaičius dokumente</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2838">**Data_CharacterCount** - Number of characters in the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2839">**Data_CharactersWithSpaceCount** – simbolių ir tarpų skaičius dokumente</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2839">**Data_CharactersWithSpaceCount** - Number of characters and spaces in the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2840">**Data_ChartCount** – diagramų skaičius dokumente</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2840">**Data_ChartCount** - Number of charts in the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2841">**Data_CitationCount** – citatų skaičius dokumente</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2841">**Data_CitationCount** - Number of citations in the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2842">**Data_DocumentLocation** – nurodo dokumentą pateikusią tarnybą („OneDrive“, „File Server“, „SharePoint“ ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2842">**Data_DocumentLocation** - Indicates which service provided the document (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2843">**Data_ETW_TrackbackTag** – nurodo kodo vietą, iš kurios šis įvykis buvo išleistas (Close arba Suspend)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2843">**Data_ETW_TrackbackTag** - Identifies the place in code where this event was fired from (Close or Suspend)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2844">**Data_EndnoteDocCount** – dokumentų išnašų skaičius dokumente</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2844">**Data_EndnoteDocCount** - Number of endnotes in the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2845">**Data_FootnoteDocCount** – puslapio išnašų skaičius dokumente</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2845">**Data_FootnoteDocCount** - Number of footnotes in the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2846">**Data_HasBibliography** – nurodo, ar dokumente yra bibliografija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2846">**Data_HasBibliography** - Indicates whether the document contains bibliography</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2847">**Data_HasHeader** – nurodo, ar dokumente yra antraštė</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2847">**Data_HasHeader** - Indicates whether the document contains a header</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2848">**Data_IsImeUsed** – nurodo, ar dokumente buvo naudota įvesties metodo rengyklė</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2848">**Data_IsImeUsed** - Indicates whether Input Method Editor been was used in the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2849">**Data_IsPageCountInProgress** – nurodo, ar šiuo metu skaičiuojami dokumento puslapiai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2849">**Data_IsPageCountInProgress** - Indicates whether page count is currently in progress for the document.</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2850">**Data_IsTouchUsed** – nurodo, ar dokumente buvo naudojama lietimo įvestis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2850">**Data_IsTouchUsed** - Indicates whether touch input was used in the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2851">**Data_IsTrackChangesOn** – nurodo, ar dokumentui buvo įjungtas keitimų sekimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2851">**Data_IsTrackChangesOn** - Indicates whether track-changes was on for the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2852">**Data_LineCount** – dokumento eilučių skaičius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2852">**Data_LineCount** - Number of lines in the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2853">**Data_MainPdod** – dokumento identifikatorius vykstant „Office Word“ procesui.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2853">**Data_MainPdod** - The document identifier in Office Word process.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2854">**Data_PageCount** – dokumento puslapių skaičius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2854">**Data_PageCount** - Number of pages in the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2855">**Data_PageNumberFieldCount** – puslapio numerių laukų skaičius dokumente</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2855">**Data_PageNumberFieldCount** - Number of page number fields in the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2856">**Data_ParagraphCount** – pastraipų skaičius dokumente</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2856">**Data_ParagraphCount** - Number of paragraphs in the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2857">**Data_PicCount** – paveikslėlių skaičius dokumente</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2857">**Data_PicCount** - Number of pictures in the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2858">**Data_RsidCount** – įrašytų peržiūrų identifikatorių skaičius dokumente</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2858">**Data_RsidCount** - Number of revisions save identifier in the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2859">**Data_TocCount** – turinio lentelių skaičius dokumente</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2859">**Data_TocCount** - Number of table of contents in the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2860">**Data_UrlHash** – vienpusė maiša, skirta „naïve“ dokumento identifikatoriui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2860">**Data_UrlHash** - One-way hash to create a naïve document identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2861">**Data_UserActionID** – šis duomenų laukas nenaudojamas (reikšmė visada yra 0).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2861">**Data_UserActionID** - this data field is not used (the value is always 0).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2862">**Data_UserActionName** – visada „DocumentStatsOnCloseAndSuspend“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2862">**Data_UserActionName** - always “DocumentStatsOnCloseAndSuspend”</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2863">**Data_UserInteractionTimeMsec** – vartotojo aktyvios sąveikos su dokumentu trukmė milisekundėmis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2863">**Data_UserInteractionTimeMsec** - Number of milliseconds that the user was actively interacting with the document</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2864">**Data_WordCount** – žodžių skaičius dokumente</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2864">**Data_WordCount** - Number of words in document</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfilenewcreatenewfile"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2865">Office.Word.FileNew.CreateNewFile</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2865">Office.Word.FileNew.CreateNewFile</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2866">Šis įvykis nurodo, kad sukurtas naujas dokumentas „Office Word“ ir sekamas sėkmingas arba nesėkmingas operacijų atlikimas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2866">This event indicates that a new document is created in Office Word and tracks success or failure of the operation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2867">Įvykis naudojamas stebėti, ar naujų dokumentų kūrimas veikia tinkamai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2867">The event is used to monitor that new document creation is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2868">Jis taip pat naudojamas mėnesio aktyviems vartotojams / įrenginiams ir debesies patikimumo rodikliams apskaičiuoti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2868">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2869">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2869">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2870">**Data\_DirtyState** – ar dokumentas buvo sukurtas neatnaujintoje būsenoje (su pakeitimais, kurie turi būti įrašyti)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2870">**Data\_DirtyState** - whether the document was created in a dirty state (with changes that need to be saved)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2871">**Data\_ErrorID** – klaidų identifikatorius operacijos gedimo atveju</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2871">**Data\_ErrorID** - error identifier in case of operation failure</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2872">**Data\_MainPdod –** dokumento identifikatorius šio proceso seanso metu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2872">**Data\_MainPdod** - The document identifier during this process session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2873">**Data\_UsesCustomTemplate** – nurodo, ar dokumentas buvo sukurtas naudojant pasirinktinį šabloną</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2873">**Data\_UsesCustomTemplate** - indicates whether the document was created from a custom template</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfileopenuserinitiatedopen"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2874">Office.Word.FileOpen.UserInitiatedOpen</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2874">Office.Word.FileOpen.UserInitiatedOpen</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2875">Šis įvykis nurodo, kad „Office Word“ atidaro dokumentą vartotojo inicijavimu, o ne programiškai iš „Office Word“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2875">This event indicates Office Word opens a document by user initiation instead of by Office Word programmatically.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2876">Jame taip pat yra svarbių failo atidarymo našumo duomenų ir yra programėlės pradžios įvykis vertinant iš vartotojo perspektyvos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2876">It also contains critical file open performance data and is an app start event from user perspective.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2877">Įvykis stebi ar file-open veikia tinkamai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2877">The event monitors whether file-open is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2878">Jis taip pat naudojamas mėnesio aktyviems vartotojams / įrenginiams ir debesies patikimumo rodikliams apskaičiuoti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2878">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices, and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span> 
 
<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2879">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2879">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2880">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** – nurodo, ar įvykyje galima tinkamai užpildyti kitų dokumentų telemetrijos susijusias reikšmes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2880">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2881">Naudojama duomenų kokybės diagnostikai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2881">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2882">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** – baitų (suglaudintų), kurie, kaip manoma, gali atidaryti failą, skaičius, nepaisant, ar mes juos gausime iki tol, kol vartotojas nori pradėti redaguoti arba galbūt įrašyti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2882">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we believe we can open the file without if we get them before the user wants to start editing or maybe saving.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2883">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** – baitų (suglaudintų), kuriuos naudodami galėtume atidaryti failą, skaičius, tačiau norint, kad tai įvyktų, reikės daug investuoti į kodą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2883">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we might be able to open the file without but would require significant code investments to make it happen</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2884">**Data_BytesSynchronous** – baitų (suglaudintų) skaičius, kuriuos privalome turėti prieš pradėdami atidaryti failą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2884">**Data_BytesSynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we must have before we can start opening the file</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2885">**Data_BytesUnknown** – baitų skaičius dokumento dalyse, kurių nesitikėjome rasti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2885">**Data_BytesUnknown** - Number of bytes in document parts that we don’t expect to find.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2886">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** – nurodo, ar dokumentas yra skirtas tik skaityti, ar redaguojamas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2886">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - Document is read only/editable</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2887">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** – iš anksto nustatytų dokumento atidarymo pagalbiniu skaitymo režimu priežasčių reikšmių rinkinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2887">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2888">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** – elementai, naudojami nuosekliam dokumento atidarymui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2888">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - Units used for incremental document open</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2889">**Data_Doc_EdpState** – dokumentui taikomas elektroninių duomenų apsaugos parametras</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2889">**Data_Doc_EdpState** - Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2890">**Data_Doc_Ext** – dokumento plėtinys (docx, xlsb, pptx ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2890">**Data_Doc_Ext** - Document extension (docx/xlsb/pptx, etc.)</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2891">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** – failo formato protokolo versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2891">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** - File format protocol version</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2892">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** – „OneDrive“ arba „SharePoint“ interneto domeno vardas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2892">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** - OneDrive or SharePoint Online Domain Name</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2893">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** – kliento identifikuojamo domeno vardo vienpusė maiša</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2893">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** - One-way hash of customer identifiable domain name</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2894">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** – vartotojo tapatybės, naudojamos atidarymui, vienpusė maiša</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2894">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** - A one-way hash of the user identity used to perform the open</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2895">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** – įrašo, kaip dokumentas buvo atidarytas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2895">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** - Records how the document was opened</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2896">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** – informuoja apie į talpyklą įtrauktas žymes, naudotas nustatyti užklausos parinktis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2896">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** - Reports on the cached flags used to set open request options</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2897">**Data_Doc_IrmRights** – veiksmai, leidžiami elektroninių duomenų apsaugos strategijos, kuri buvo taikyta dokumentui arba vartotojui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2897">**Data_Doc_IrmRights** - Actions permitted by the Electronic Data Protection policy that has been applied to the document/user</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2898">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** – žymė, nurodanti, kad dokumentas buvo palaipsniui atidarytas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2898">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** - Flag indicating that the document has been incrementally opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2900">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** – žymė, nurodanti, kad atidaryta autonominė dokumento kopija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2900">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** - Flag indicating that the offline copy of a document was opened</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2901">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** – žymė, nurodanti, kad automatiškai sinchronizuota dokumento kopija yra kompiuteryje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2901">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** - Flag indicating that an auto synced copy of the document exists on the computer</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2902">**Data_Doc_Location** – nurodo tarnybą, pateikusią dokumentą („OneDrive“, „File Server“, „SharePoint“)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2902">**Data_Doc_Location** - Indicates which service provided the document (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint)</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2903">**Data_Doc_LocationDetails** – nurodo įrenginyje saugomo dokumento žinomą aplanką</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2903">**Data_Doc_LocationDetails** - Indicates which Known Folder provided a locally stored document</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2904">**Data_Doc_NumberCoAuthors** – skaičiuoja bendro redagavimo seanso metu bendradarbiaujančių vartotojų skaičių</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2904">**Data_Doc_NumberCoAuthors** - Count of the number of fellow users in a collaborative editing session</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2905">**Data_Doc_PasswordFlags** – nurodo, ar nustatytas skaitymo arba skaitymo / rašymo slaptažodžio žymių rinkinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2905">**Data_Doc_PasswordFlags** - Indicates read or read/write password flags set</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2906">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** – dokumento atidarymo tik kaip skaitomo priežastys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2906">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** - Reasons why the document was opened read only</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2907">**Data.Doc.ResourceIdHash** – anonimiškai pateiktų dokumentų identifikatorius, naudojamas problemoms diagnozuoti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2907">**Data_Doc_ResourceIdHash** - An anonymized document Identifier used to diagnose problems</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2908">**Data.Doc.ServerDocId** – nekintamų anonimiškai pateiktų dokumentų identifikatorius, naudojamas problemoms diagnozuoti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2908">**Data_Doc_ServerDocId** - An immutable anonymized document Identifier used to diagnose problems</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2913">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** – „SharePoint Online“ užklausų diagnostinė informacija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2913">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** - Diagnostic information from SharePoint Online requests</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2914">**Data_Doc_SizeInBytes** – dokumento dydžio indikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2914">**Data_Doc_SizeInBytes** - Indicator of document size</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2915">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** – dokumento URL arba kelio specialiųjų simbolių indikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2915">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** - Indicator of special chars in the document's URL or Path</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2917">**Data_Doc_SyncBackedType** – dokumento tipo indikatorius (vietinis arba pagrįstas tarnyba)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2917">**Data_Doc_SyncBackedType** - Indicator as to the type of document (local or service based)</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2918">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** – vienpusė maiša, skirta „naïve“ dokumento identifikatoriui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2918">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** - One-way hash to create a naïve document identifier</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2919">**Data_Doc_WopiServiceId** – apima unikalų WOPI tarnybos teikėjo identifikatorių</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2919">**Data_Doc_WopiServiceId** - Contains unique identifier of WOPI service provider</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2925">**Data_LinkStyles** – nurodo, ar mes susieti su šablono stiliais</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2925">**Data_LinkStyles** - Indicates whether we are linking to the template styles</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2926">**Data_MainPdod** – dokumento identifikatorius vykstant „Office Word“ procesui.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2926">**Data_MainPdod** - The document identifier in Office Word process</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2927">**Data_Measurements** – užkoduota eilutė, kurioje pateiktas skirtingų dalių atidarymo laiko suskirstymas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2927">**Data_Measurements** - Encoded string containing the time breakdown of the different parts of open.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2928">Skirtas diagnozuoti atvirai veiklai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2928">Used to diagnose open performance.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2929">**Data_MoveDisabledReason** – klaida, kuri yra išjungia dokumento perkėlimą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2929">**Data_MoveDisabledReason** - Error that is disabling move for the document</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2930">**Data_MoveFlightEnabled** – nurodo, ar įjungta perkėlimo testavimo funkcija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2930">**Data_MoveFlightEnabled** - Whether the flight for the move feature is enabled</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2931">**Data_OpenInitiateKind** – scenarijaus tipas, kai vartotojas pradėjo šią file-open operaciją.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2931">**Data_OpenInitiateKind** – Type of the scenario where users started this file-open operation.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2936">**Data_SecondaryTag** – unikali kodo iškvietimo vietos žymė, naudojama papildomiems trikties duomenims atidaryti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2936">**Data_SecondaryTag** - Unique tag for code call site used to add additional failure data for open.</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2937">**Data_TemplateFormat** – šablono failo, kuriuo pagrįstas dokumentas, formatas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2937">**Data_TemplateFormat** - File format of the template that the document is based on.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2939">**Data_VerboseMeasurements** – užkoduota eilutė, kurioje pateiktas skirtingų dalių atidarymo išsamus laiko suskirstymas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2939">**Data_VerboseMeasurements** - Encoded string containing the detailed time breakdown of the different parts of open.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2940">Naudojama matuoti efektyvumą, įgalinta tik vidiniams žiedams.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2940">Used to measure performance, only enabled for internal rings.</span></span> 



#### <a name="officewordfilesaveactcmdgosubsaveas"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2941">Office.Word.FileSave.ActCmdGosubSaveAs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2941">Office.Word.FileSave.ActCmdGosubSaveAs</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2942">Šis įvykis nurodo, kad vartotojas įrašo savo pakeitimus į naują dokumentą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2942">This event indicates that a user is saving their changes to a new document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2943">Įvykis stebi, ar įrašymas į naują dokumentą veikia tinkamai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2943">The event monitors whether saving to a new document is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2944">Jis taip pat naudojamas mėnesio aktyviems vartotojams / įrenginiams ir debesies patikimumo rodikliams apskaičiuoti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2944">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2945">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2945">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2992">Šis įvykis nurodo, kad „Office Word“ įrašo automatinio atkūrimo dokumentą, kuris anksčiau nebuvo įrašytas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2992">This event indicates Office Word saves an auto-recovery document that has not been saved before.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2993">Tai suteikia galimybę „Microsoft“ aptikti automatinio atkūrimo klaidas, svarbias dokumento duomenų saugumui.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2993">It allows Microsoft to detect errors in auto-recovery which is important for document data safety.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2994">Įvykis stebi, ar automatinio atkūrimo įrašymo funkcija veikia tinkamai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2994">The event monitors whether auto-recovery-save is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2995">Jis taip pat naudojamas mėnesio aktyviems vartotojams / įrenginiams ir debesies patikimumo rodikliams apskaičiuoti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2995">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2996">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2996">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-2997">**Data_DetachedDuration** – nurodo, kiek laiko gijoje nebuvo veiklos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-2997">**Data_DetachedDuration** - How long was the activity detached from the thread</span></span>
