#### <a name="officewordfilesaveactfconfirmsavedoccorequerysave"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3042">Office.Word.FileSave.ActFConfirmSaveDocCoreQuerySave</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3042">Office.Word.FileSave.ActFConfirmSaveDocCoreQuerySave</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3043">Šis įvykis nurodo, kad „Office Word“ ragina vartotoją įrašyti keitimus, kai programa bando uždaryti dokumentą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3043">This event indicates Office Word prompts the user to save changes when it tries to close the document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3044">Tai leidžia „Microsoft“ stebėti, ar įrašymas išėjimo metu veikia tinkamai, kad neprarasti dokumento duomenų.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3044">It allows Microsoft to monitor whether save-at-quit works as expected to avoid document data loss.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3045">Įvykis stebi, ar funkcija įrašyti išėjimo metu veikia tinkamai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3045">The event monitors whether save-at-quit is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3046">Jis taip pat naudojamas mėnesio aktyviems vartotojams / įrenginiams ir debesies patikimumo rodikliams apskaičiuoti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3046">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3047">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3047">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3048">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** – nurodo, ar įvykyje galima tinkamai užpildyti kitų dokumentų telemetrijos susijusias reikšmes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3048">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3049">Naudojama duomenų kokybės diagnostikai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3049">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3050">**Data_DetachedDuration** – nurodo, kiek laiko gijoje nebuvo veiklos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3050">**Data_DetachedDuration** - How long was the activity detached from the thread</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3051">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** – nurodo, ar dokumentas yra skirtas tik skaityti, ar redaguojamas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3051">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - Document is read only/editable</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3052">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** – iš anksto nustatytų dokumento atidarymo pagalbiniu skaitymo režimu priežasčių reikšmių rinkinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3052">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3053">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind** – nurodo, ar debesies dokumento talpykloje esanti versija buvo atidaryta, ir kuri asinchroninio atnaujinimo logika buvo naudojama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3053">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3054">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** – elementai, naudojami nuosekliam dokumento atidarymui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3054">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - Units used for incremental document open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3055">**Data_Doc_EdpState** – dokumentui taikomas elektroninių duomenų apsaugos parametras</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3055">**Data_Doc_EdpState** - Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3056">**Data_Doc_Ext** – dokumento plėtinys (docx, xlsb, pptx ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3056">**Data_Doc_Ext** - Document extension (docx/xlsb/pptx etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3057">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** – failo formato protokolo versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3057">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** - File format protocol version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3058">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** – „OneDrive“ arba „SharePoint“ interneto domeno vardas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3058">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** - OneDrive or SharePoint Online Domain Name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3063">**Data_Doc_IrmRights** – veiksmai, leidžiami elektroninių duomenų apsaugos strategijos, kuri buvo taikyta dokumentui arba vartotojui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3063">**Data_Doc_IrmRights** - Actions permitted by the Electronic Data Protection policy that has been applied to the document/user</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfilesavesaveassavefile"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3104">Office.Word.FileSave.SaveAsSaveFile</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3104">Office.Word.FileSave.SaveAsSaveFile</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3105">Šis įvykis nurodo, kad „Office Word“ įrašo dokumentą į naują dokumentą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3105">This event indicates Office Word saves a document into a new document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3106">Tai leidžia „Microsoft“ aptikti funkcijos Įrašyti kaip klaidas, o tai svarbu norint išvengti dokumento duomenų praradimo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3106">It allows Microsoft to detect errors in save-as which is important to avoid document data loss.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3107">Įvykis stebi, ar funkcija Įrašyti kaip veikia tinkamai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3107">The event monitors whether save-as is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3108">Jis taip pat naudojamas mėnesio aktyviems vartotojams / įrenginiams ir debesies patikimumo rodikliams apskaičiuoti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3108">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3109">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3109">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3112">**Data_AddDocTelemResDst** – nurodo, ar paskirties dokumento įvykyje galima tinkamai užpildyti susijusias kitų dokumentų telemetrijos reikšmes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3112">**Data_AddDocTelemResDst** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event for the destination document.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3113">Naudojama duomenų kokybės diagnostikai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3113">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3116">**Data_DetachedDuration** – nurodo, kiek laiko gijoje nebuvo veiklos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3116">**Data_DetachedDuration** - How long was the activity detached from the thread</span></span>

#### <a name="officeextensibilitysandboxodpactivationhanging"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3534">Office.Extensibility.Sandbox.ODPActivationHanging</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3534">Office.Extensibility.Sandbox.ODPActivationHanging</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3535">Renka, kai paleisti „Office“ papildinį užtrunka netikėtai ilgai (> 5 sek.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3535">Collects when an Office add-in takes unexpectedly long to launch (>5 sec).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3536">Naudojama „Office“ papildinių paleidimo triktims aptikti ir pašalinti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3536">Used to detect and fix problems with Office add-ins launching.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3537">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3537">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3538">**AppId** – taikomosios programos ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3538">**AppId** - ID of the App</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3539">**AppInfo** – duomenys, susiję su papildinio tipu (užduočių sritis arba be sąsajos, arba turinys ir t. t.) ir teikėjo tipu (domenas, "SharePoint", failų sistema ir t. t.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3539">**AppInfo** - data regarding the type of add-in (task pane or UILess or in content etc.) and the provider type (omen, SharePoint, filesystem etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3540">**AppInstanceId** – taikomosios programos egzemplioriaus ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3540">**AppInstanceId** - ID of the app instance</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3541">**AssetId** – taikomosios programos ištekliaus ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3541">**AssetId** - asset ID of the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3542">**NumberOfAddinsActivated** – suaktyvintas papildinių skaitiklis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3542">**NumberOfAddinsActivated** - counter of add-ins activated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3543">**RemoterType** – nurodo nuotolinio elemento, kuris naudojamas norint suaktyvinti papildinį, tipą (patikimas, nepatikimas, „Win32webView“, patikimas UDF ir t. t.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3543">**RemoterType** - specifies the type of remoter (Trusted, untrusted, Win32webView, Trusted UDF etc.) used to activate the add-in</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3544">**StoreType** – taikomosios programos kilmė</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3544">**StoreType** - origin of the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3545">**TimeForAuth** – autentifikacijai sugaištas laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3545">**TimeForAuth** - time spent on auth</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointpptdesktopbootime"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3737">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Desktop.Bootime</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3737">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Desktop.Bootime</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3738">Renka, kaip paleista „PowerPoint“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3738">Collecting how PowerPoint is booted.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3739">Jis apima „PowerPoint“ paleistį apsaugotame rodinyje, pagalbiniu skaitymo režimu nuo makro režimo, spausdinimo, naujo ir tuščio dokumento atkūrimo iki automatizavimo ir ar jis yra paleistas paspaudžiant.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3739">It includes boot PowerPoint in protected view, in assisted reading mode, from Macro, print, new and blank document, document recovery, from automation and if it is click- to-run.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3740">Taip pat renka kiek laiko užtrunka paleisti „PowerPoint“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3740">It also collects how long it takes PowerPoint to boot.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3741">Šie duomenys yra labai svarbūs norint užtikrinti, kad „PowerPoint“ veiktų tinkamai, kai įkeliama iš skirtingų režimų.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3741">This data is critical to guarantee PowerPoint performs well when booted from different modes.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3742">„Microsoft“ naudoja šiuos duomenis, kad fiksuotų ilgą paleidimo laiką, kai atidaroma „PowerPoint“ iš skirtingų režimų.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3742">Microsoft uses this data to catch long booting time when opening PowerPoint from different modes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3743">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3743">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3744">**AssistedReading -** pagalbimiu skaitymo režimu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3744">**AssistedReading -** in assisted reading mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3745">**Automation -** automatizavimo režimu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3745">**Automation -** from automation</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3746">**Benchmark -** paleidžiamas vykdymo kontrolinis etalonas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3746">**Benchmark -** run performance benchmark</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3747">**Blank -** Tuščias dokumentas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3747">**Blank -** blank document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3748">**BootTime -** seanso paleidimo laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3748">**BootTime -** session boot time</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3749">**Embedding -** Dokumento įdėjimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3749">**Embedding -** embedding document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3750">**IsC2R -** Technologija „Spustelėkite ir naudokitės“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3750">**IsC2R -** is click-to-run</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3751">**IsNew -** Naujas dokumentas </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3751">**IsNew -** new document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3752">**IsOpen -** Atidaryta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3752">**IsOpen -** is open</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3753">**Macro1 -** Vykdoma makrokomanda</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3753">**Macro1 -** run Macro</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3756">**Print -** Spausdinamas dokumentas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3756">**Print -** print document</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3811">Taikoma visoms „Office“ „Windows“ pagrįstomis programomis: win32 ir UWP</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3811">Applicable to all the Office windows-based applications: win32 and UWP</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3812">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3812">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3813">**OfficeProcessSessionStart** Siunčia pagrindinę informaciją į naują „Office“ seanso pradžią.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3813">**OfficeProcessSessionStart** sends basic information upon the start of a new Office session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3814">Naudojamas norint suskaičiuoti unikalius seansus, matomus šiais įrenginiais.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3814">This is used to count the number of unique sessions seen on a given device.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3815">Jis naudojamas kaip pasikartojantis įvykis, kad užtikrintų, jog taikomoji programa paleista įrenginyje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3815">This is used as a heartbeat event to ensure that the application is running on a device or not.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3816">Be to, tai yra svarbus visos programos patikimumo signalas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3816">In addition, it serves as a critical signal for overall application reliability</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3817">**ProgramosSeansoVedikl** – konkrečios taikomosios programos seanso pradžios identifikatorius, naudojamas nuo proceso kūrimo pradžios ir iki proceso pabaigos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3817">**AppSessionGuid** - An identifier of a particular application session starting at process creation time and persisting until process end.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3818">Jis yra suformuotas kaip standartinis 128 bitų GUID, tik sudarytas iš 4 dalių.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3818">It is formatted as a standard 128-bit GUID but constructed of 4 parts.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3819">Šios keturios dalys eil4s tvarka yra (1) 32 bitų proceso ID (2) 16 bitų seanso ID (3) 16 bitų įkrovos ID (4) 64 bitų proceso sukūrimo laikasm išreikštas UTC 100ns</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3819">Those four parts in order are (1) 32 bit Process ID (2) 16 bit Session ID (3) 16 bit Boot ID (4) 64 bit Process creation time in UTC 100ns</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3820">**processSessionId** - Atsitiktinai sugeneruotas žinynas, skirtas programos seansui identifikuoti </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3820">**processSessionId** - Randomly generated guid to identify the app session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3821">**UTCReplace_AppSessionGuid** - Pastovi Bulio logikos vertė.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3821">**UTCReplace_AppSessionGuid** - Constant boolean value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3822">Visuomet „True“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3822">Always true.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3824">Nurodo, kad dabartinis „Office“ seansas yra perdavimo seansas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3824">Indicates that the current Office session is a handoff session.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3825">Tai reiškia, kad vartotojo prašymo atidaryti dokumentą tvarkymas perduodamas į tos pačios taikomosios programos jau veikiantį egzempliorių.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3825">This means that handling of a user’s request to open a document is being handed off to an already running instance of the same application.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3847">**sessionID** – atsitiktinai sugeneruotas GUID, skirtas nustatyti taikomosios programos seansą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3847">**childSessionID** - Randomly generated guid to identify the app session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3848">**parentSessionId** – atsitiktinai sugeneruotas GUID, skirtas nustatyti taikomosios programos seansą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3848">**parentSessionId** - Randomly generated guid to identify the app session</span></span>

#### <a name="officevisiovisioiosappboottime"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3849">Office.Visio.VisioIosAppBootTime</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3849">Office.Visio.VisioIosAppBootTime</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3850">Jis suaktyvinamas kiekvieną kartą, kai paleidžiama „Visio iOS“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3850">This is triggered every time the Visio iOS application boots.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3851">Labai svarbu suprasti taikomosios programos „Visio iOS“ paleidimo rezultatus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3851">It is essential to understand boot performance of the Visio iOS app.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3852">Naudojama prasto veikimo trikčių diagnostikai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3852">Used to troubleshoot poor performance.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3853">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3853">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3854">**Data_AppBootTime** – taikomosios programos paleidimo trukmė, išreikšta milisekundėmis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3854">**Data_AppBootTime** - Duration taken for app to boot, in milliseconds.</span></span>

#### <a name="officevisiovisioiosappresumetime"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3855">Office.Visio.VisioIosAppResumeTime</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3855">Office.Visio.VisioIosAppResumeTime</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3856">Šis įvykis paleidžiamas kiekvieną kartą, kai taikomoji programa „Visio iOS“ tęsia fokusavimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3856">This event is triggered every time the Visio iOS app resumes focus.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3857">Būtina išmatuoti taikomosios programos tęsimo našumą ir taikomosios programos „Visio iOS“ trikčių diagnostikos našumo problemas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3857">It is essential to measure app resume performance and troubleshoot performance issues of Visio iOS app.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3858">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3858">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3859">**Data_AppResumeTime** – programos trukmė iki tęsimo, išreikšta milisekundėmis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3859">**Data_AppResumeTime** - Duration for app to resume in milliseconds.</span></span>

#### <a name="officewordfileopenopencmdfilemrupriv"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3860">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenCmdFileMruPriv</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3860">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenCmdFileMruPriv</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3861">Šis įvykis nurodo „Office Word“ atidaryti dokumentą iš vėliausiai naudoto (MRU) sąrašo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3861">This event indicates Office Word opens a document from the Most Recent Used (MRU) list.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3862">Jame taip pat yra svarbių failo atidarymo našumo duomenų ir yra programėlės pradžios įvykis vertinant iš vartotojo perspektyvos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3862">It also contains critical file open performance data and is an app start event from user perspective.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3863">Įvykis stebi, ar file-open-from-MRU veikia tinkamai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3863">The event monitors whether fileopen-from-MRU is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3864">Jis taip pat naudojamas mėnesio aktyviems vartotojams / įrenginiams ir debesies patikimumo rodikliams apskaičiuoti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3864">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices, and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3865">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3865">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3866">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** – nurodo, ar įvykyje galima tinkamai užpildyti kitų dokumentų telemetrijos susijusias reikšmes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3866">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3867">Naudojama duomenų kokybės diagnostikai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3867">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3868">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** – baitų (suglaudintų), kurie, kaip manoma, gali atidaryti failą, skaičius, nepaisant, ar mes juos gausime iki tol, kol vartotojas nori pradėti redaguoti arba galbūt įrašyti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3868">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we believe we can open the file without if we get them before the user wants to start editing or maybe saving</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3869">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** – baitų (suglaudintų), kuriuos naudodami galėtume atidaryti failą, skaičius, tačiau norint, kad tai įvyktų, reikės daug investuoti į kodą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3869">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we might be able to open the file without but would require significant code investments to make it happen</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3870">**Data_BytesSynchronous** – baitų (suglaudintų) skaičius, kuriuos privalome turėti prieš pradėdami atidaryti failą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3870">**Data_BytesSynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we must have before we can start opening the file</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3871">**Data_BytesUnknown** – baitų skaičius dokumento dalyse, kurių nesitikėjome rasti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3871">**Data_BytesUnknown** - Number of bytes in document parts that we don’t expect to find</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3872">**Data_DetachedDuration** – nurodo, kiek laiko gijoje nebuvo veiklos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3872">**Data_DetachedDuration** - How long was the activity detached from the thread</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3873">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** – nurodo, ar dokumentas yra skirtas tik skaityti, ar redaguojamas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3873">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - Document is read-only/editable</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3874">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** – iš anksto nustatytų dokumento atidarymo pagalbiniu skaitymo režimu priežasčių reikšmių rinkinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3874">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3875">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind** – nurodo, ar debesies dokumento talpykloje esanti versija buvo atidaryta, ir kuri asinchroninio atnaujinimo logika buvo naudojama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3875">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3876">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** – elementai, naudojami nuosekliam dokumento atidarymui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3876">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - Units used for incremental document open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3877">**Data_Doc_EdpState** – dokumentui taikomas elektroninių duomenų apsaugos parametras</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3877">**Data_Doc_EdpState** - Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3878">**Data_Doc_Ext** – dokumento plėtinys (docx, xlsb, pptx ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3878">**Data_Doc_Ext** - Document extension (docx/xlsb/pptx etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3879">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** – failo formato protokolo versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3879">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** - File format protocol version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3880">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** – „OneDrive“ arba „SharePoint“ interneto domeno vardas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3880">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** - OneDrive or SharePoint Online Domain Name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3881">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** – kliento identifikuojamo domeno vardo vienpusė maiša</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3881">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** - One-way hash of customer identifiable domain name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3882">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** – vartotojo tapatybės, naudojamos atidarymui, vienpusė maiša</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3882">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** - A one-way hash of the user identity used to perform the open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3883">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** – įrašo, kaip dokumentas buvo atidarytas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3883">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** - Records how the document was opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3884">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** – informuoja apie į talpyklą įtrauktas žymes, naudotas nustatyti užklausos parinktis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3884">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** - Reports on the cached flags used to set open request options</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3885">**Data_Doc_IrmRights** – veiksmai, leidžiami elektroninių duomenų apsaugos strategijos, kuri buvo taikyta dokumentui arba vartotojui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3885">**Data_Doc_IrmRights** - Actions permitted by the Electronic Data Protection policy that has been applied to the document/user</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3886">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** – žymė, nurodanti, kad dokumentas buvo palaipsniui atidarytas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3886">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** - Flag indicating that the document has been incrementally opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3887">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** – žymė nurodanti, kad dokumentą palaiko bendradarbiavimo tarnyba</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3887">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** - Flag indicating that the document is supported in the collaboration service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3888">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** – žymė, nurodanti, kad atidaryta autonominė dokumento kopija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3888">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** - Flag indicating that the offline copy of a document was opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3889">**Data.Doc.IsSyncBacked –** žymė, nurodanti, kad automatiškai sinchronizuota dokumento kopija yra kompiuteryje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3889">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** - Flag indicating that an auto-synced copy of the document exists on the computer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3890">**Data_Doc_Location** – nurodo tarnybą, pateikusią dokumentą („OneDrive“, „File Server“, „SharePoint“ ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3890">**Data_Doc_Location** - Indicates which service provided the document (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3891">**Data_Doc_LocationDetails** – nurodo įrenginyje saugomo dokumento žinomą aplanką</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3891">**Data_Doc_LocationDetails** - Indicates which Known Folder provided a locally stored document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3892">**Data_Doc_NumberCoAuthors** – skaičiuoja bendro redagavimo seanso metu bendradarbiaujančių vartotojų skaičių</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3892">**Data_Doc_NumberCoAuthors** - Count of the number of fellow users in a collaborative editing session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3893">**Data_Doc_PasswordFlags** – nurodo, ar nustatytas skaitymo arba skaitymo / rašymo slaptažodžio žymių rinkinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3893">**Data_Doc_PasswordFlags** - Indicates read or read/write password flags set</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3894">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** – dokumento atidarymo tik kaip skaitomo priežastys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3894">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** - Reasons why the document was opened read only</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3895">**Data.Doc.ResourceIdHash** – anonimiškai pateiktų dokumentų identifikatorius, naudojamas problemoms diagnozuoti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3895">**Data_Doc_ResourceIdHash** - An anonymized document Identifier used to diagnose problems</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3896">**Data_Doc_RtcType** – nurodo, kaip buvo nustatytas realaus laiko kanalas (RTC) dabartiniam failui (išjungtas, nepalaikomas, pagal pageidavimą, visada įjungta, ir t. t.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3896">**Data_Doc_RtcType** -  Indicates how the real-time channel (RTC) was setup for current file (Disabled, unsupported, on demand, always on, etc.).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3897">**Data.Doc.ServerDocId** – nekintamų anonimiškai pateiktų dokumentų identifikatorius, naudojamas problemoms diagnozuoti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3897">**Data_Doc_ServerDocId** - An immutable anonymized document Identifier used to diagnose problems</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3898">**Data_Doc_ServerProtocol** – protokolo versija, naudojama norint susisiekti su tarnyba</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3898">**Data_Doc_ServerProtocol** - the protocol version used to communicate with the service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3899">**Data.Doc.ServerType** – tarnybą siūlančio serverio tipas („SharePoint“, „OneDrive“, WOPI ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3899">**Data_Doc_ServerType** - the type of the server offering the service (SharePoint, OneDrive, WOPI, etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3900">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** – serverio versija, siūlanti tarnybą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3900">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** - the server version offering the service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3901">**Data_Doc_SessionId** – nustato konkretų dokumentų redagavimo seansą visame seanse</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3901">**Data_Doc_SessionId** - Identifies a specific document edit session within the full session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3902">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** – „SharePoint Online“ užklausų diagnostinė informacija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3902">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** - Diagnostic information from SharePoint Online requests</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3903">**Data_Doc_SizeInBytes** – dokumento dydžio indikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3903">**Data_Doc_SizeInBytes** - Indicator of document size</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3904">**Data.Doc.SpecialChars** – dokumento URL specialiųjų simbolių indikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3904">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** - Indicator of special chars in the document's URL</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3905">**Data_Doc_SyncBackedType** – dokumento tipo indikatorius (vietinis arba pagrįstas tarnyba)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3905">**Data_Doc_SyncBackedType** - Indicator as to the type of document (local or service based)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3906">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** – vienpusė maiša, skirta „naïve“ dokumento identifikatoriui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3906">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** - One-way hash to create a naïve document identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3907">**Data_Doc_WopiServiceId** – apima unikalų WOPI tarnybos teikėjo identifikatorių</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3907">**Data_Doc_WopiServiceId** - Contains unique identifier of WOPI service provider</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3908">**Data_EditorDisablingRename** – pirmojo redaktoriaus, dėl kurio buvo išjungtas pervardijimas, identifikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3908">**Data_EditorDisablingRename** - Identifier of the first editor that caused for rename to be disabled</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3909">**Data_EditorsCount** – dokumento redaktorių skaičius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3909">**Data_EditorsCount** - Number of editors in the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3910">**Data_ForceReadWriteReason** – sveikasis skaičius, nurodantis priežastį, kodėl failas buvo priverstinai atidarytas skaitymo / rašymo režimu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3910">**Data_ForceReadWriteReason** - Integer value representing the reason why the file was forced into read/write mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3911">**Data_FSucceededAfterRecoverableFailure** – nurodo, kad atidaryti pavyko pašalinus triktį, įvykusią atidarant dokumentą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3911">**Data_FSucceededAfterRecoverableFailure** - Indicates that open succeeded after repairing a failure while opening the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3912">**Data_LastLoggedTag** – unikali kodo iškvietimo žymės vieta, naudojama nustatyti, kada dukart nepavyksta bandymas atidaryti (naudojama duomenų kokybės diagnostikai)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3912">**Data_LastLoggedTag** - Unique tag for code call site used to identify when we try to fail the open twice (used for data quality diagnostics)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3913">**Data_LinkStyles** – nurodo, ar mes susieti su šablono stiliais</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3913">**Data_LinkStyles** - Indicates whether we are linking to the template styles</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3914">**Data_MainPdod** – dokumento identifikatorius vykstant „Office Word“ procesui.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3914">**Data_MainPdod** - The document identifier in Office Word process</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3915">**Data_Measurements** – užkoduota eilutė, kurioje pateiktas skirtingų dalių atidarymo laiko suskirstymas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3915">**Data_Measurements** - Encoded string containing the time breakdown of the different parts of open.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3916">Skirta našumui vertinti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3916">Used to measure performance.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3917">**Data_MoveDisabledReason** – klaida, kuri yra išjungia dokumento perkėlimą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3917">**Data_MoveDisabledReason** - Error that is disabling move for the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3918">**Data_MoveFlightEnabled** – nurodo, ar įjungta perkėlimo testavimo funkcija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3918">**Data_MoveFlightEnabled** - Whether the flight for the move feature is enabled</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3919">**Data_PartsUnknown** – dokumento dalių, iš kurių nepavyko gauti duomenų, skaičius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3919">**Data_PartsUnknown** - the number of document parts that we couldn’t get data for</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3920">**Data_RecoverableFailureInitiationLocationTag** – unikali kodo iškvietimo vietos žymė, naudojama vietai kode, kurioje stengiamės sutvarkyti failą prieš jį atidarant, identifikuoti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3920">**Data_RecoverableFailureInitiationLocationTag** - Unique tag for code call site used to identify the place in code where we attempt to fix the file before opening it</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3921">**Data_RenameDisabledReason** – klaida, dėl kurios šiam dokumentui išjungiamas pervardijimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3921">**Data_RenameDisabledReason** - Error that is causing for rename to be disabled for this document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3922">**Data_RenameFlightEnabled** – nurodo, ar įjungta pervardijimo testavimo funkcija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3922">**Data_RenameFlightEnabled** - Whether the flight for the rename feature is enabled</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3923">**Data_SecondaryTag** – unikali kodo iškvietimo vietos žymė, naudojama papildomiems trikties duomenims atidaryti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3923">**Data_SecondaryTag** - Unique tag for code call site used to add additional failure data for open</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3924">**Data_TemplateFormat** – šablono failo, kuriuo pagrįstas dokumentas, formatas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3924">**Data_TemplateFormat** - File format of the template that the document is based on.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3925">**Data_UsesNormal** – nurodo, ar atidarytas dokumentas pagrįstas įprastu šablonu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3925">**Data_UsesNormal** - Indicates whether the open document is based on the normal template</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3926">**PathData_Doc_StreamAvailability** – indikatorius, nurodantis, ar dokumentų srautas yra pasiekiamas arba išjungtas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3926">**PathData_Doc_StreamAvailability** - Indicator if document stream is available/disabled</span></span>


#### <a name="officewordfileopenopenffileopenxstzcore"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3927">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenFFileOpenXstzCore</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3927">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenFFileOpenXstzCore</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3928">Šis įvykis nurodo, kad „Office Word“ atidaro dokumentą, kurį vartotojas dukart spustelėjo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3928">This event indicates Office Word opens a document who is double clicked by a user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3929">Jame taip pat yra svarbių failo atidarymo našumo duomenų ir yra programėlės pradžios įvykis vertinant iš vartotojo perspektyvos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3929">It also contains critical file open performance data and is an app start event from user perspective.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3930">Įvykis stebi, ar funkcija file-open-from-file-double-click veikia tinkamai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3930">The event monitors whether file-openfrom-file-double-click is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3931">Jis taip pat naudojamas mėnesio aktyviems vartotojams / įrenginiams ir debesies patikimumo rodikliams apskaičiuoti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3931">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices, and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3932">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3932">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3933">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** – nurodo, ar įvykyje galima tinkamai užpildyti kitų dokumentų telemetrijos susijusias reikšmes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3933">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3934">Naudojama duomenų kokybės diagnostikai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3934">Used for data quality diagnostics</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3935">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** – baitų (suglaudintų), kurie, kaip manoma, gali atidaryti failą, skaičius, nepaisant, ar mes juos gausime iki tol, kol vartotojas nori pradėti redaguoti arba galbūt įrašyti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3935">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we believe we can open the file without if we get them before the user wants to start editing or maybe saving</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3936">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** – baitų (suglaudintų), kuriuos naudodami galėtume atidaryti failą, skaičius, tačiau norint, kad tai įvyktų, reikės daug investuoti į kodą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3936">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we might be able to open the file without but would require significant code investments to make it happen</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3937">**Data_BytesSynchronous** – baitų (suglaudintų) skaičius, kuriuos privalome turėti prieš pradėdami atidaryti failą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3937">**Data_BytesSynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we must have before we can start opening the file</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3938">**Data_BytesUnknown** – baitų skaičius dokumento dalyse, kurių nesitikėjome rasti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3938">**Data_BytesUnknown** - Number of bytes in document parts that we don’t expect to find</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3939">**Data_DetachedDuration** – nurodo, kiek laiko gijoje nebuvo veiklos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3939">**Data_DetachedDuration** - How long was the activity detached from the thread</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3940">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** – nurodo, ar dokumentas yra skirtas tik skaityti, ar redaguojamas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3940">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - Document is read-only/editable</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3941">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** – iš anksto nustatytų dokumento atidarymo pagalbiniu skaitymo režimu priežasčių reikšmių rinkinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3941">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3942">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind** – nurodo, ar debesies dokumento talpykloje esanti versija buvo atidaryta, ir kuri asinchroninio atnaujinimo logika buvo naudojama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3942">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3943">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** – elementai, naudojami nuosekliam dokumento atidarymui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3943">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - Units used for incremental document open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3944">**Data_Doc_EdpState** – dokumentui taikomas elektroninių duomenų apsaugos parametras</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3944">**Data_Doc_EdpState** - Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3945">**Data_Doc_Ext** – dokumento plėtinys (docx, xlsb, pptx ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3945">**Data_Doc_Ext** - Document extension (docx/xlsb/pptx etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3946">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** – failo formato protokolo versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3946">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** - File format protocol version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3947">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** – „OneDrive“ arba „SharePoint“ interneto domeno vardas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3947">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** - OneDrive or SharePoint Online Domain Name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3948">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** – kliento identifikuojamo domeno vardo vienpusė maiša</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3948">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** - One-way hash of customer identifiable domain name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3949">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** – informuoja apie į talpyklą įtrauktas žymes, naudotas nustatyti užklausos parinktis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3949">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** - Reports on the cached flags used to set open request options</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3950">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** – vartotojo tapatybės, naudojamos atidarymui, vienpusė maiša</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3950">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** - A one-way hash of the user identity used to perform the open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3951">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** – įrašo, kaip dokumentas buvo atidarytas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3951">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** - Records how the document was opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3952">**Data_Doc_IrmRights** – veiksmai, leidžiami elektroninių duomenų apsaugos strategijos, kuri buvo taikyta dokumentui arba vartotojui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3952">**Data_Doc_IrmRights** - Actions permitted by the Electronic Data Protection policy that has been applied to the document/user</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3953">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** – žymė, nurodanti, kad dokumentas buvo palaipsniui atidarytas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3953">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** - Flag indicating that the document has been incrementally opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3954">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** – žymė nurodanti, kad dokumentą palaiko bendradarbiavimo tarnyba</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3954">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** - Flag indicating that the document is supported in the collaboration service</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3955">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** – žymė, nurodanti, kad atidaryta autonominė dokumento kopija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3955">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** - Flag indicating that the offline copy of a document was opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3956">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** – žymė, nurodanti, kad automatiškai sinchronizuota dokumento kopija yra kompiuteryje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3956">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** - Flag indicating that an auto synced copy of the document exists on the computer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3957">**Data_Doc_Location** – nurodo tarnybą, pateikusią dokumentą („OneDrive“, „File Server“, „SharePoint“ ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3957">**Data_Doc_Location** - Indicates which service provided the document (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint etc.)</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3958">**Data_Doc_LocationDetails** – nurodo įrenginyje saugomo dokumento žinomą aplanką</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3958">**Data_Doc_LocationDetails** - Indicates which Known Folder provided a locally stored document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3959">**Data_Doc_NumberCoAuthors** – skaičiuoja bendro redagavimo seanso metu bendradarbiaujančių vartotojų skaičių</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3959">**Data_Doc_NumberCoAuthors** - Count of the number of fellow users in a collaborative editing session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3960">**Data_Doc_PasswordFlags** – nurodo, ar nustatytas skaitymo arba skaitymo / rašymo slaptažodžio žymių rinkinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3960">**Data_Doc_PasswordFlags** - Indicates read or read/write password flags set</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3961">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** – dokumento atidarymo tik kaip skaitomo priežastys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3961">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** - Reasons why the document was opened read only</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3962">**Data.Doc.ResourceIdHash** – anonimiškai pateiktų dokumentų identifikatorius, naudojamas problemoms diagnozuoti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3962">**Data_Doc_ResourceIdHash** - An anonymized document Identifier used to diagnose problems</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3963">**Data_Doc_RtcType** – nurodo, kaip buvo nustatytas realaus laiko kanalas (RTC) dabartiniam failui (išjungtas, nepalaikomas, pagal pageidavimą, visada įjungta, ir t. t.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3963">**Data_Doc_RtcType** -  Indicates how the real-time channel (RTC) was setup for current file (Disabled, unsupported, on demand, always on, etc.).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3964">**Data.Doc.ServerDocId** – nekintamų anonimiškai pateiktų dokumentų identifikatorius, naudojamas problemoms diagnozuoti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3964">**Data_Doc_ServerDocId** - An immutable anonymized document Identifier used to diagnose problems</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3965">**Data_Doc_ServerProtocol** – protokolo versija, naudojama norint susisiekti su tarnyba</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3965">**Data_Doc_ServerProtocol** - the protocol version used to communicate with the service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3966">**Data_Doc_ServerType** – tarnybą siūlančio serverio tipas („SharePoint“, „OneDrive“, WOPI ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3966">**Data_Doc_ServerType** - the type of the server offering the service (SharePoint, OneDrive, WOPI etc.)</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3967">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** – serverio versija, siūlanti tarnybą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3967">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** - the server version offering the service</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3968">**Data_Doc_SessionId** – nustato konkretų dokumentų redagavimo seansą visame seanse</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3968">**Data_Doc_SessionId** - Identifies a specific document edit session within the full session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3969">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** – „SharePoint Online“ užklausų diagnostinė informacija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3969">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** - Diagnostic information from SharePoint Online requests</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3970">**Data_Doc_SizeInBytes** – dokumento dydžio indikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3970">**Data_Doc_SizeInBytes** - Indicator of document size</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3971">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** – dokumento URL arba kelio specialiųjų simbolių indikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3971">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** - Indicator of special chars in the document's URL or Path</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3972">**Data_Doc_StreamAvailability** – indikatorius, nurodantis, ar dokumentų srautas yra pasiekiamas arba išjungtas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3972">**Data_Doc_StreamAvailability** - Indicator if document stream is available/disabled</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3973">**Data_Doc_SyncBackedType** – dokumento tipo indikatorius (vietinis arba pagrįstas tarnyba)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3973">**Data_Doc_SyncBackedType** - Indicator as to the type of document (local or service based)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3974">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** – vienpusė maiša, skirta „naïve“ dokumento identifikatoriui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3974">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** - One-way hash to create a naïve document identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3975">**Data_Doc_WopiServiceId** – apima unikalų WOPI tarnybos teikėjo identifikatorių</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3975">**Data_Doc_WopiServiceId** - Contains unique identifier of WOPI service provider</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3976">**Data_EditorDisablingRename** – pirmojo redaktoriaus, dėl kurio buvo išjungtas pervardijimas, identifikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3976">**Data_EditorDisablingRename** - Identifier of the first editor that caused for rename to be disabled</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3977">**Data_EditorsCount** – dokumento redaktorių skaičius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3977">**Data_EditorsCount** - Number of editors in the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3978">**Data_FSucceededAfterRecoverableFailure** – nurodo, kad atidaryti pavyko pašalinus triktį, įvykusią atidarant dokumentą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3978">**Data_FSucceededAfterRecoverableFailure** - Indicates that open succeeded after repairing a failure while opening the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3979">**Data_ForceReadWriteReason** – sveikasis skaičius, nurodantis priežastį, kodėl failas buvo priverstinai atidarytas skaitymo / rašymo režimu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3979">**Data_ForceReadWriteReason** - Integer value representing the reason why the file was forced into read/write mode</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3980">**Data_LastLoggedTag** – unikali kodo iškvietimo žymės vieta, naudojama nustatyti, kada dukart nepavyksta bandymas atidaryti (naudojama duomenų kokybės diagnostikai)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3980">**Data_LastLoggedTag** - Unique tag for code call site used to identify when we try to fail the open twice (used for data quality diagnostics)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3981">**Data_LinkStyles** – nurodo, ar mes susieti su šablono stiliais</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3981">**Data_LinkStyles** - Indicates whether we are linking to the template styles</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3982">**Data_MainPdod** – dokumento identifikatorius vykstant „Office Word“ procesui.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3982">**Data_MainPdod** - The document identifier in Office Word process</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3983">**Data_Measurements** – užkoduota eilutė, kurioje pateiktas skirtingų dalių atidarymo laiko suskirstymas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3983">**Data_Measurements** - Encoded string containing the time breakdown of the different parts of open.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3984">Skirta našumui vertinti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3984">Used to measure performance.</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3985">**Data_MoveDisabledReason** – klaida, kuri yra išjungia dokumento perkėlimą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3985">**Data_MoveDisabledReason** - Error that is disabling move for the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3987">**Data_PartsUnknown** – dokumento dalių, iš kurių nepavyko gauti duomenų, skaičius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3987">**Data_PartsUnknown** - the number of document parts that we couldn’t get data for</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3988">**Data_RecoverableFailureInitiationLocationTag** – unikali kodo iškvietimo vietos žymė, naudojama vietai kode, kurioje stengiamės sutvarkyti failą prieš jį atidarant, identifikuoti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3988">**Data_RecoverableFailureInitiationLocationTag** - Unique tag for code call site used to identify the place in code where we attempt to fix the file before opening it.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3989">**Data_RenameDisabledReason** – klaida, dėl kurios šiam dokumentui išjungiamas pervardijimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3989">**Data_RenameDisabledReason** - Error that is causing for rename to be disabled for this document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3990">**Data_RenameFlightEnabled** – nurodo, ar įjungta pervardijimo testavimo funkcija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3990">**Data_RenameFlightEnabled** - Whether the flight for the rename feature is enabled</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3991">**Data_SecondaryTag** – unikali kodo iškvietimo vietos žymė, naudojama papildomiems trikties duomenims atidaryti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3991">**Data_SecondaryTag** - Unique tag for code call site used to add additional failure data for open.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3992">**Data_TemplateFormat** – šablono failo, kuriuo pagrįstas dokumentas, formatas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3992">**Data_TemplateFormat** - File format of the template that the document is based on.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3993">**Data_UsesNormal** – nurodo, ar atidarytas dokumentas pagrįstas įprastu šablonu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3993">**Data_UsesNormal** - Indicates whether the open document is based on the normal template.</span></span>


#### <a name="officewordfileopenopenifrinitargs"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3994">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenIfrInitArgs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3994">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenIfrInitArgs</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3995">Šis įvykis nurodo, kad „Office Word“ atidaro dokumentą naudojant COM aktyvinimą arba komandinę eilutę.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3995">This event indicates Office Word opens a document via COM activation or command line.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3996">Jame taip pat yra svarbūs failo atidarymo našumo duomenys ir yra programėlės pradžios įvykis vertinant iš vartotojo perspektyvos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3996">It also contains critical file open performance data, and is an app start event from user perspective.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3997">Įvykis stebi, ar file-open-from-command-line veikia tinkamai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3997">The event monitors whether file-open-from-command-line is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3998">Jis taip pat naudojamas mėnesio aktyviems vartotojams / įrenginiams ir debesies patikimumo rodikliams apskaičiuoti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3998">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices, and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-3999">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-3999">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4000">**Data\_AddDocTelemRes –** nurodo, ar įvykyje galima tinkamai užpildyti kitų dokumentų telemetrijos susijusias reikšmes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4000">**Data\_AddDocTelemRes -** Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4001">Naudojama duomenų kokybės diagnostikai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4001">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4002">**Data\_BytesAsynchronous -** Baitų (suglaudintų), kurie, kaip manoma, gali atidaryti failą, skaičius, nepaisant, ar mes juos gausime, kol vartotojas nori pradėti redaguoti arba galbūt įrašyti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4002">**Data\_BytesAsynchronous -** Number of bytes (compressed) that we believe we can open the file without if we get them before the user wants to start editing or maybe saving.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4003">**Data\_BytesAsynchronousWithWork -** Baitų (suglaudintų), kuriuos naudodami galėtume atidaryti failą, skaičius, tačiau norint, kad tai įvyktų, reikės daug investuoti į kodą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4003">**Data\_BytesAsynchronousWithWork -** Number of bytes (compressed) that we might be able to open the file without but would require significant code investments to make it happen</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4004">**Data\_BytesSynchronous -** Baitų (suglaudintų) skaičius, kuriuos privalome turėti prieš pradėdami atidaryti failą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4004">**Data\_BytesSynchronous -** Number of bytes (compressed) that we must have before we can start opening the file</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4005">**Data\_BytesUnknown -** Baitų skaičius dokumentų dalyse, kurių nesitikėjome rasti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4005">**Data\_BytesUnknown -** Number of bytes in document parts that we don’t expect to find.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4006">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode -** Dokumentas yra skirtas tik skaityti / redaguoti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4006">**Data\_Doc\_AccessMode -** Document is read only/editable</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4007">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons –** iš anksto nustatytų dokumento atidarymo pagalbiniu skaitymo režimu priežasčių reikšmių rinkinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4007">**Data\_Doc\_AssistedReadingReasons -** Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4008">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind** – nurodo, ar debesies dokumento talpykloje esanti versija buvo atidaryta, ir kuri asinchroninio atnaujinimo logika buvo naudojama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4008">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4009">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType –** vienetai, naudojami nuosekliam dokumento atidarymui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4009">**Data\_Doc\_ChunkingType -** Units used for incremental document open</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4010">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState -** Dokumentui taikomas elektroninių duomenų apsaugos parametras</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4010">**Data\_Doc\_EdpState -** Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4011">**Data\_Doc\_Ext -** Dokumento plėtinys (docx / xlsb / pptx ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4011">**Data\_Doc\_Ext -** Document extension (docx/xlsb/pptx, etc.)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4012">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat -** Failo formato protokolo versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4012">**Data\_Doc\_FileFormat -** File format protocol version</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4013">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn –** „OneDrive“ arba „SharePoint“ interneto domeno vardas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4013">**Data\_Doc\_Fqdn -** OneDrive or SharePoint Online Domain Name</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4014">**Data\_Doc\_FqdnHash –** kliento identifikuojamo domeno vardo vienpusė maiša</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4014">**Data\_Doc\_FqdnHash -** One-way hash of customer identifiable domain name</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4015">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags -** Informuoja apie į talpyklą įtrauktas žymes, naudotas užklausos parinktims nustatyti </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4015">**Data\_Doc\_IOFlags -** Reports on the cached flags used to set open request options</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4016">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityTelemetryId -** Vartotojo tapatybės, naudojamos atidarymui, vienpusė maiša</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4016">**Data\_Doc\_IdentityTelemetryId -** A one-way hash of the user identity used to perform the open</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4017">**Data\_Doc\_InitializationScenario -** Įrašo, kaip dokumentas buvo atidarytas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4017">**Data\_Doc\_InitializationScenario -** Records how the document was opened</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4018">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights –** veiksmai, leidžiami elektroninių duomenų apsaugos strategijos, kurie buvo taikyti dokumentui / vartotojui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4018">**Data\_Doc\_IrmRights -** Actions permitted by the Electronic Data Protection policy that has been applied to the document/user</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4019">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen -** Žymė, nurodanti, kad dokumentas buvo palaipsniui atidarytas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4019">**Data\_Doc\_IsIncrementalOpen -** Flag indicating that the document has been incrementally opened</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4020">**Data\_Doc\_IsOcsSupported -** Žyma, nurodanti, kad dokumentas palaikomas bendradarbiavimo tarnybos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4020">**Data\_Doc\_IsOcsSupported -** Flag indicating that the document is supported in the collaboration service</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4021">**Data\_Doc\_IsOpeningOfflineCopy -** Žyma, nurodanti, kad autonominė dokumento kopija atidaryta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4021">**Data\_Doc\_IsOpeningOfflineCopy -** Flag indicating that the offline copy of a document was opened</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4022">**Duomenų\_ad\_IsSyncBacked -** žyma, nurodanti, kad automatiškai sinchronizuota dokumento kopija yra kompiuteryje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4022">**Data\_Doc\_IsSyncBacked -** Flag indicating that an auto synced copy of the document exists on the computer</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4023">**Data\_Doc\_Location -** Nurodo, kuri tarnyba teikia dokumentą („OneDrive“, failų serveris, „SharePoint“)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4023">**Data\_Doc\_Location -** Indicates which service provided the document (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4024">**Data\_Doc\_LocationDetails -** Nurodo, kuriuose žinomuose aplankuose yra vietoje saugomų dokumentų</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4024">**Data\_Doc\_LocationDetails -** Indicates which Known Folder provided a locally stored document</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4025">**Data\_Doc\_NumberCoAuthors -** Skaičiuoja bendro redagavimo seanso metu bendradarbiaujančių vartotojų skaičių</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4025">**Data\_Doc\_NumberCoAuthors -** Count of the number of fellow users in a collaborative editing session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4026">**Data\_Doc\_PasswordFlags –** nurodo, ar nustatytas skaitymo arba skaitymo / rašymo slaptažodžio žymų rinkinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4026">**Data\_Doc\_PasswordFlags -** Indicates read or read/write password flags set</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4027">**Data\_Doc\_ReadOnlyReasons -** Priežastys, kodėl dokumentas buvo atidarytas tik kaip skaitomas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4027">**Data\_Doc\_ReadOnlyReasons -** Reasons why the document was opened read only</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4028">**Data\_Doc\_ResourceIdHash -** Anonimizuotų dokumentų identifikatorius, naudojamas problemoms diagnozuoti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4028">**Data\_Doc\_ResourceIdHash -** An anonymized document Identifier used to diagnose problems</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4029">**Data_Doc_RtcType** – nurodo, kaip buvo nustatytas realaus laiko kanalas (RTC) dabartiniam failui (išjungtas, nepalaikomas, pagal pageidavimą, visada įjungta, ir t. t.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4029">**Data_Doc_RtcType -**  Indicates how the real-time channel (RTC) was setup for current file (Disabled, unsupported, on demand, always on, etc.).</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4030">**Data\_Doc\_ServerDocId -** Nekintamų anonimizuotų dokumentų identifikatorius, naudojamas problemoms diagnozuoti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4030">**Data\_Doc\_ServerDocId -** An immutable anonymized document Identifier used to diagnose problems</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4031">**Data\_Doc\_ServerProtocol -** Protokolo versija, naudojama norint susisiekti su tarnyba</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4031">**Data\_Doc\_ServerProtocol -** the protocol version used to communicate with the service</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4033">**Data\_Doc\_ServerVersion -** Serverio versija, siūlanti tarnybą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4033">**Data\_Doc\_ServerVersion -** the server version offering the service</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4035">**Data\_Doc\_SharePointServiceContext -** Diagnostinė informacija iš „SharePoint Online“ užklausų</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4035">**Data\_Doc\_SharePointServiceContext -** Diagnostic information from SharePoint Online requests</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4036">**Data\_Doc\_SizeInBytes –** dokumento dydžio indikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4036">**Data\_Doc\_SizeInBytes -** Indicator of document size</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4037">**Data\_Doc\_SpecialChars –** dokumento URL arba kelio specialiųjų simbolių indikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4037">**Data\_Doc\_SpecialChars -** Indicator of special chars in the document's URL or Path</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4046">**Data\_LastLoggedTag -** Unikali kodo iškvietimo žymės vieta, naudojama nustatyti, kada dukart nepavyksta bandymas atidaryti (naudojama duomenų kokybės diagnostikai)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4046">**Data\_LastLoggedTag -** Unique tag for code call site used to identify when we try to fail the open twice (used for data quality diagnostics)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4056">**Data\_RenameFlightEnabled -** Ar įjungta pervardijimo testavimo funkcija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4056">**Data\_RenameFlightEnabled -** Whether the flight for the rename feature is enabled</span></span>
