  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4059">**Data\_UsesNormal -** Nurodo, ar atidarytas dokumentas pagrįstas įprastu šablonu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4059">**Data\_UsesNormal -** Indicates whether the open document is based on the normal template.</span></span>


#### <a name="officewordfileopenopenloadfile"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4060">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenLoadFile</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4060">Office.Word.FileOpen.OpenLoadFile</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4061">Šis įvykis nurodo, kad „Office Word“ atidaro dokumentą naudojant dialogo langą Atidaryti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4061">This event indicates Office Word opens a document via Open dialog.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4062">Jame taip pat yra svarbių failo atidarymo našumo duomenų ir yra programėlės pradžios įvykis vertinant iš vartotojo perspektyvos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4062">It also contains critical file open performance data and is an app start event from user perspective.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4063">Įvykis stebi, ar file-open-from-the-open-file-dialogas veikia tinkamai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4063">The event monitors whether file-open-from-the-open-filedialog is working as expected.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4064">Jis taip pat naudojamas mėnesio aktyviems vartotojams / įrenginiams ir debesies patikimumo rodikliams apskaičiuoti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4064">It is also used to calculated monthly active users/devices, and cloud reliability metrics.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4065">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4065">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4066">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** – nurodo, ar įvykyje galima tinkamai užpildyti kitų dokumentų telemetrijos susijusias reikšmes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4066">**Data_AddDocTelemRes** - Reports whether we were able to properly populate other document telemetry related values in the event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4067">Naudojama duomenų kokybės diagnostikai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4067">Used for data quality diagnostics.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4068">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** – baitų (suglaudintų), kurie, kaip manoma, gali atidaryti failą, skaičius, nepaisant, ar mes juos gausime iki tol, kol vartotojas nori pradėti redaguoti arba galbūt įrašyti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4068">**Data_BytesAsynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we believe we can open the file without if we get them before the user wants to start editing or maybe saving</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4069">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** – baitų (suglaudintų), kuriuos naudodami galėtume atidaryti failą, skaičius, tačiau norint, kad tai įvyktų, reikės daug investuoti į kodą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4069">**Data_BytesAsynchronousWithWork** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we might be able to open the file without but would require significant code investments to make it happen</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4070">**Data_BytesSynchronous** – baitų (suglaudintų) skaičius, kuriuos privalome turėti prieš pradėdami atidaryti failą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4070">**Data_BytesSynchronous** - Number of bytes (compressed) that we must have before we can start opening the file</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4071">**Data_BytesUnknown** – baitų skaičius dokumento dalyse, kurių nesitikėjome rasti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4071">**Data_BytesUnknown** - Number of bytes in document parts that we don’t expect to find</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4072">**Data_DetachedDuration** – nurodo, kiek laiko gijoje nebuvo veiklos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4072">**Data_DetachedDuration** - How long was the activity detached from the thread</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4073">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** – nurodo, ar dokumentas yra skirtas tik skaityti, ar redaguojamas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4073">**Data_Doc_AccessMode** - Document is read only/editable</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4074">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** – iš anksto nustatytų dokumento atidarymo pagalbiniu skaitymo režimu priežasčių reikšmių rinkinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4074">**Data_Doc_AssistedReadingReasons** - Predefined set of values of why document was opened in assisted reading mode</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4075">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind** – nurodo, ar debesies dokumento talpykloje esanti versija buvo atidaryta, ir kuri asinchroninio atnaujinimo logika buvo naudojama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4075">**Data_Doc_AsyncOpenKind –** Indicates whether a cached version of the cloud document was opened and which asynchronous refresh logic was used.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4076">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** – elementai, naudojami nuosekliam dokumento atidarymui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4076">**Data_Doc_ChunkingType** - Units used for incremental document open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4077">**Data_Doc_EdpState** – dokumentui taikomas elektroninių duomenų apsaugos parametras</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4077">**Data_Doc_EdpState** - Electronic Data Protection setting for the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4078">**Data_Doc_Ext** – dokumento plėtinys (docx, xlsb, pptx ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4078">**Data_Doc_Ext** - Document extension (docx/xlsb/pptx etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4079">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** – failo formato protokolo versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4079">**Data_Doc_FileFormat** - File format protocol version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4080">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** – „OneDrive“ arba „SharePoint“ interneto domeno vardas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4080">**Data_Doc_Fqdn** - OneDrive or SharePoint Online Domain Name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4081">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** – kliento identifikuojamo domeno vardo vienpusė maiša</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4081">**Data_Doc_FqdnHash** - One-way hash of customer identifiable domain name</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4082">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** – vartotojo tapatybės, naudojamos atidarymui, vienpusė maiša</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4082">**Data_Doc_IdentityTelemetryId** - A one-way hash of the user identity used to perform the open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4083">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** – įrašo, kaip dokumentas buvo atidarytas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4083">**Data_Doc_InitializationScenario** - Records how the document was opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4084">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** – informuoja apie į talpyklą įtrauktas žymes, naudotas nustatyti užklausos parinktis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4084">**Data_Doc_IOFlags** - Reports on the cached flags used to set open request options</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4085">**Data_Doc_IrmRights** – veiksmai, leidžiami elektroninių duomenų apsaugos strategijos, kuri buvo taikyta dokumentui arba vartotojui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4085">**Data_Doc_IrmRights** - Actions permitted by the Electronic Data Protection policy that has been applied to the document/user</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4086">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** – žymė, nurodanti, kad dokumentas buvo palaipsniui atidarytas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4086">**Data_Doc_IsIncrementalOpen** - Flag indicating that the document has been incrementally opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4087">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** – žymė nurodanti, kad dokumentą palaiko bendradarbiavimo tarnyba</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4087">**Data_Doc_IsOcsSupported** - Flag indicating that the document is supported in the collaboration service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4088">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** – žymė, nurodanti, kad atidaryta autonominė dokumento kopija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4088">**Data_Doc_IsOpeningOfflineCopy** - Flag indicating that the offline copy of a document was opened</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4089">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** – žymė, nurodanti, kad automatiškai sinchronizuota dokumento kopija yra kompiuteryje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4089">**Data_Doc_IsSyncBacked** - Flag indicating that an auto synced copy of the document exists on the computer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4090">**Data_Doc_Location** – nurodo tarnybą, pateikusią dokumentą („OneDrive“, „File Server“, „SharePoint“ ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4090">**Data_Doc_Location** - Indicates which service provided the document (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4091">**Data_Doc_LocationDetails** – nurodo įrenginyje saugomo dokumento žinomą aplanką</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4091">**Data_Doc_LocationDetails** - Indicates which Known Folder provided a locally stored document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4092">**Data_Doc_NumberCoAuthors** – skaičiuoja bendro redagavimo seanso metu bendradarbiaujančių vartotojų skaičių</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4092">**Data_Doc_NumberCoAuthors** - Count of the number of fellow users in a collaborative editing session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4093">**Data_Doc_PasswordFlags** – nurodo, ar nustatytas skaitymo arba skaitymo / rašymo slaptažodžio žymių rinkinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4093">**Data_Doc_PasswordFlags** - Indicates read or read/write password flags set</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4094">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** – dokumento atidarymo tik kaip skaitomo priežastys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4094">**Data_Doc_ReadOnlyReasons** - Reasons why the document was opened read only</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4095">**Data.Doc.ResourceIdHash** – anonimiškai pateiktų dokumentų identifikatorius, naudojamas problemoms diagnozuoti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4095">**Data_Doc_ResourceIdHash** - An anonymized document Identifier used to diagnose problems</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4096">**Data_Doc_RtcType** – nurodo, kaip buvo nustatytas realaus laiko kanalas (RTC) dabartiniam failui (išjungtas, nepalaikomas, pagal pageidavimą, visada įjungta, ir t. t.).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4096">**Data_Doc_RtcType** -  Indicates how the real-time channel (RTC) was setup for current file (Disabled, unsupported, on demand, always on, etc.).</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4097">**Data.Doc.ServerDocId** – nekintamų anonimiškai pateiktų dokumentų identifikatorius, naudojamas problemoms diagnozuoti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4097">**Data_Doc_ServerDocId** - An immutable anonymized document Identifier used to diagnose problems</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4098">**Data_Doc_ServerProtocol** – protokolo versija, naudojama norint susisiekti su tarnyba</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4098">**Data_Doc_ServerProtocol** - the protocol version used to communicate with the service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4099">**Data.Doc.ServerType** – tarnybą siūlančio serverio tipas („SharePoint“, „OneDrive“, WOPI ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4099">**Data_Doc_ServerType** - the type of the server offering the service (SharePoint, OneDrive, WOPI, etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4100">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** – serverio versija, siūlanti tarnybą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4100">**Data_Doc_ServerVersion** - the server version offering the service</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4101">**Data_Doc_SessionId** – nustato konkretų dokumentų redagavimo seansą visame seanse</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4101">**Data_Doc_SessionId** - Identifies a specific document edit session within the full session</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4102">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** – „SharePoint Online“ užklausų diagnostinė informacija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4102">**Data_Doc_SharePointServiceContext** - Diagnostic information from SharePoint Online requests</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4103">**Data_Doc_SizeInBytes** – dokumento dydžio indikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4103">**Data_Doc_SizeInBytes** - Indicator of document size</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4104">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** – dokumento URL arba kelio specialiųjų simbolių indikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4104">**Data_Doc_SpecialChars** - Indicator of special chars in the document's URL or Path</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4105">**Data_Doc_StreamAvailability** – indikatorius, nurodantis, ar dokumentų srautas yra pasiekiamas arba išjungtas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4105">**Data_Doc_StreamAvailability** - Indicator if document stream is available/disabled</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4106">**Data_Doc_SyncBackedType** – dokumento tipo indikatorius (vietinis arba pagrįstas tarnyba)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4106">**Data_Doc_SyncBackedType** - Indicator as to the type of document (local or service based)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4107">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** – vienpusė maiša, skirta „naïve“ dokumento identifikatoriui</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4107">**Data_Doc_UrlHash** - One-way hash to create a naïve document identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4108">**Data_EditorDisablingRename** – pirmojo redaktoriaus, dėl kurio buvo išjungtas pervardijimas, identifikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4108">**Data_EditorDisablingRename** - Identifier of the first editor that caused for rename to be disabled</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4109">**Data_EditorsCount** – dokumento redaktorių skaičius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4109">**Data_EditorsCount** - Number of editors in the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4110">**Data_ForceReadWriteReason** – sveikasis skaičius, nurodantis priežastį, kodėl failas buvo priverstinai atidarytas skaitymo / rašymo režimu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4110">**Data_ForceReadWriteReason** - Integer value representing the reason why the file was forced into read/write mode</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4111">**Data_FSucceededAfterRecoverableFailure** – nurodo, kad atidaryti pavyko pašalinus triktį, įvykusią atidarant dokumentą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4111">**Data_FSucceededAfterRecoverableFailure** - Indicates that open succeeded after repairing a failure while opening the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4112">**Data_LastLoggedTag** – unikali kodo iškvietimo žymės vieta, naudojama nustatyti, kada dukart nepavyksta bandymas įrašyti (naudojama duomenų kokybės diagnostikai)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4112">**Data_LastLoggedTag** - Unique tag for code call site used to identify when we fail to try the save twice (used for data quality diagnostics)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4113">**Data_LinkStyles** – nurodo, ar mes susieti su šablono stiliais</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4113">**Data_LinkStyles** - Indicates whether we are linking to the template styles</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4114">**Data_MainPdod** – dokumento identifikatorius vykstant „Office Word“ procesui.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4114">**Data_MainPdod** - The document identifier in Office Word process</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4115">**Data_Measurements** – užkoduota eilutė, kurioje pateiktas skirtingų dalių atidarymo laiko suskirstymas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4115">**Data_Measurements** - Encoded string containing the time breakdown of the different parts of open.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4116">Skirta našumui vertinti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4116">Used to measure performance.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4117">**Data_MoveDisabledReason** – klaida, kuri yra išjungia dokumento perkėlimą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4117">**Data_MoveDisabledReason** - Error that is disabling move for the document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4118">**Data_MoveFlightEnabled** – nurodo, ar įjungta perkėlimo testavimo funkcija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4118">**Data_MoveFlightEnabled** - Whether the flight for the move feature is enabled</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4119">**Data_PartsUnknown** – dokumento dalių, iš kurių nepavyko gauti duomenų, skaičius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4119">**Data_PartsUnknown** - the number of document parts that we couldn’t get data for</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4120">**Data_RecoverableFailureInitiationLocationTag** – unikali kodo iškvietimo vietos žymė, naudojama vietai kode, kurioje stengiamės sutvarkyti failą prieš jį atidarant, identifikuoti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4120">**Data_RecoverableFailureInitiationLocationTag** - Unique tag for code call site used to identify the place in code where we attempt to fix the file before opening it</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4121">**Data_RenameDisabledReason** – klaida, dėl kurios šiam dokumentui išjungiamas pervardijimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4121">**Data_RenameDisabledReason** - Error that is causing for rename to be disabled for this document</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4122">**Data_RenameFlightEnabled** – nurodo, ar įjungta pervardijimo testavimo funkcija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4122">**Data_RenameFlightEnabled** - Whether the flight for the rename feature is enabled</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4123">**Data_SecondaryTag** – unikali kodo iškvietimo vietos žymė, naudojama papildomiems trikties duomenims atidaryti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4123">**Data_SecondaryTag** - Unique tag for code call site used to add additional failure data for open</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4124">**Data_TemplateFormat** – šablono failo, kuriuo pagrįstas dokumentas, formatas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4124">**Data_TemplateFormat** - File format of the template that the document is based on</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4125">**Data_UsesNormal** – nurodo, ar atidarytas dokumentas pagrįstas įprastu šablonu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4125">**Data_UsesNormal** - Indicates whether the open document is based on the normal template</span></span>


#### <a name="renewuserop"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4126">RenewUserOp</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4126">RenewUserOp</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4127">Renkama, kai vartotojas bando atidaryti IRM apsaugotą dokumentą ar taikyti IRM apsaugas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4127">Collected when a user attempts to open an IRM protected doc or apply IRM protections.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4128">Joje yra informacija, reikalinga tinkamai nustatyti ir diagnozuoti problemas, įvykusias atliekant vartotojo sertifikatų atnaujinimo operaciją.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4128">It contains the information needed to be able to properly investigate and diagnose issues that happen when renew user certificates operation is performed.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4129">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4129">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4130">**AppInfo.ClientHierarchy** – kliento hierarchija, kuri nurodo programos paleidimus gamybos aplinkoje arba kūrėjo aplinkoje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4130">**AppInfo.ClientHierarchy** - Client hierarchy which indicates the application runs in production environment or developer environment</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4131">**AppInfo.Name** – programos pavadinimas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4131">**AppInfo.Name** - Application name.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4132">**AppInfo.Version** – programos versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4132">**AppInfo.Version** - Application version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4133">**iKey** – registravimo serverio ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4133">**iKey** - Logger server Id</span></span>

### <a name="office-accessibility-configuration-subtype"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4166">*„Office“ pritaikymo neįgaliesiems konfigūracijos potipis*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4166">*Office accessibility configuration subtype*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4167">„Office“ pritaikymo neįgaliesiems funkcijos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4167">Office accessibility features</span></span>

#### <a name="officeaccessibilityaccessibilitytoolsessionpresencewin32"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4168">Office.Accessibility.AccessibilityToolSessionPresenceWin32</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4168">Office.Accessibility.AccessibilityToolSessionPresenceWin32</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4171">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4171">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4172">**Data\_Data\_Jaws -** Nurodo, ar „Jaws“ veikė seanso metu**Data\_Data\_Magic -** Nurodo, ar „Magic“ veikė seanso metu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4172">**Data\_Data\_Jaws -** indicates if Jaws was running during the session**Data\_Data\_Magic -** indicates if Magic was running during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4173">**Data\_Data\_Magnify -** Nurodo, ar Didinimas veikė seanso metu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4173">**Data\_Data\_Magnify -** indicates if Magnify was running during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4174">**Data\_Data\_Narrator -** Nurodo, ar Diktorius veikė seanso metu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4174">**Data\_Data\_Narrator -** indicates if Narrator was running during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4175">**Data\_Data\_Narrator -** Nurodo, ar Diktorius veikė seanso metu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4175">**Data\_Data\_NVDA -** indicates if NVDA was running during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4176">**Data\_Data\_SA -** Nurodo, ar SA veikė seanso metu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4176">**Data\_Data\_SA -** indicates if SA was running during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4177">**Data\_Data\_Supernova -** Nurodo, ar „Supernova“ veikė seanso metu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4177">**Data\_Data\_Supernova -** indicates if Supernova was running during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4178">**Data\_Data\_SuperNovaessSuite -** Nurodo, ar „SuperNovaAccessSuite“ veikė seanso metu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4178">**Data\_Data\_SuperNovaessSuite -** indicates if SuperNovaAccessSuite was running during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4179">**Data\_Data\_WinEyes -** Nurodo, ar „WinEyes“ veikė seanso metu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4179">**Data\_Data\_WinEyes -** indicates if WinEyes was running during the session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4180">**Data\_Data\_ZoomText -** Nurodo, ar Teksto mastelis veikė seanso metu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4180">**Data\_Data\_ZoomText -** indicates if ZoomText was running during the session</span></span>

#### <a name="office_apple_darkmode"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4181">Office_Apple_DarkMode</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4181">Office_Apple_DarkMode</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4182">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4182">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4183">Įvykis praneša mums, ar vartotojas naudoja sistemą režime „DarkMode“ ir ar vartotojas perrašė programos „Office“ sistemos „DarkMode“ parametrus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4183">The event tells us if user is running a System on DarkMode and whether the user overwrote the DarkMode System setting in Office.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4184">Naudojame šį įvykį, kad užtikrintume pritaikymą neįgaliesiems ir nustatytume prioritetu vartotojų patirties optimizavimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4184">We use this event to help ensure accessibility and prioritize user-experience optimization.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4185">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4185">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4186">**Data_DarkModeIsEnabled** – nurodo, ar sistemoje įgalintas „DarkMode“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4186">**Data_DarkModeIsEnabled** - Whether DarkMode is enabled in the system.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4187">**Data_RequiresAquaSystemAppearanceEnabled** – ar programoje „Office“ perrašytas „DarkMode“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4187">**Data_RequiresAquaSystemAppearanceEnabled** - Whether DarkMode is overwritten in Office.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4193">**Data_CollectionTime** – laiko žyma, rodanti įvykio rinkimo laiką.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4193">**Data_CollectionTime** - A timestamp denoting the event collection time.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4248">**Data_DownloadedContentServiceGroupState –** atsisiųsto turinio vartotojo parametras</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4248">**Data_DownloadedContentServiceGroupState -** User setting for downloaded content</span></span> 
 
  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4249">**Data_ForwardLinkId –** saitas į vartotojo scenarijaus privatumo dokumentaciją</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4249">**Data_ForwardLinkId -** Link to privacy documentation for the user scenario</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4252">**Data_OfficeServiceConnectionState –** prijungtų tarnybų vartotojo parametras</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4252">**Data_OfficeServiceConnectionState -** User setting for connected services</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4253">**Data_RecordRegistry –** įmonės privatumo dialogo lango rodymo įrašas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4253">**Data_RecordRegistry -** Record of showing the enterprise privacy dialog</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4255">**Data_SeenInsidersDialog –** „Insider“ privatumo dialogo lango rodymo įrašas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4255">**Data_SeenInsidersDialog -** Record of showing the Insiders privacy dialog</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4256">**Data_SendTelemetryOption –** telemetrijai skirtas vartotojo parametras</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4256">**Data_SendTelemetryOption -** User setting for telemetry</span></span>

   - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4260">**Data_UserContentServiceGroupState –** vartotojo parametrai, skirti turiniui analizuoti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4260">**Data_UserContentServiceGroupState -** User setting for analyzing content</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4270">Renka bet kokių neapdorojamų išimčių informaciją naudodama duomenų srautinio duomenų siųstuvo programą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4270">Collects information for any unhandled exceptions using the Data Streamer App.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4271">Šie duomenys naudojami programos sveikatai stebėti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4271">This data is used to monitor the health of the application.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4272">Šis įvykis sugeneruojamas iš „Microsoft“ srautinio duomenų siųstuvo, skirto „Excel“ papildiniui.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4272">This event is generated by Microsoft Data Streamer for Excel Add-in.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4273">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4273">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4275">**Event Name** – Įvykio pavadinimas yra įvykio kategorija ir įvykio etiketė.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4275">**Event Name** - Event Name is the Event Category and Event Label.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_apple_identitydomainname"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4276">Office_Apple_IdentityDomainName</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4276">Office_Apple_IdentityDomainName</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4277">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4277">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4278">Šis įvykis naudojamas mūsų sistemos sveikatai stebėti, taip pat tiriant tam tikrų domenų vartotojų trikčių priežastis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4278">The event is used to monitor the health of our system as well as investigating causes of failures by certain domain users.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4279">Renkame domeną, kurį naudoja mūsų vartotojai autentifikavimo metu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4279">We collect the domain used by our users when they authenticate.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4280">Naudojame šiuos duomenis, kad padėtų nustatyti ir išspręsti šias problemas, kurios gali atrodyti pernelyg darančios poveikį platesniame lygmenyje, bet kurios paaiškėja, kad daro poveikį tam tikram vartotojų domenui.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4280">We use this data to help identify and fix those issues that might not seem too impactful at a broader level, but that turn out to be very impactful to a certain domain of users.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4281">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4281">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4282">**Data_Domain** – autentifikavimui naudojamas domenas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4282">**Data_Domain** - the domain used for authentication</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4283">**Data_IdentityProvider** – autentifikavimo tapatybės teikėjo pavadinimas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4283">**Data_IdentityProvider** - The authentication identity provider name.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4284">(t. y. LiveId arba ADAL)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4284">(i.e. LiveId or ADAL)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4285">**Data_IdentityProviderEnum** – autentifikavimo tapatybės teikėjo kodas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4285">**Data_IdentityProviderEnum** - The authentication identity provider code.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4286">(Skaičius)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4286">(A number)</span></span>

#### <a name="office_apple_systemhealthappexitmacandios"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4287">Office_Apple_SystemHealthAppExitMacAndiOS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4287">Office.Apple.SystemHealthAppExitMacAndiOS</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4288">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4288">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4289">Šis įvykis naudojamas „Office“ taikomųjų programų sveikatai stebėti, taip pat tirti trikčių priežastis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4289">The event is used to monitor the health of our Office applications as well as for investigating causes of failures.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4290">Mes renkame duomenis apie kiekvieną išėjimą iš programos, kad nustatyti, ar taikomoji programa išėjo sklandžiai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4290">We collect data on each application exit to determine whether an application exited gracefully.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4291">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4291">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4292">**Data_AffectedProcessSessionID** – seanso, dėl kurio buvo išeita iš programos, identifikatorius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4292">**Data_AffectedProcessSessionID** - The identifier for the session that experience the application exit.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4293">**Data_AffectedSessionBuildNumber** – papildoma taikomosios programos versija, kurioje buvo pastebėtas išėjimas iš programos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4293">**Data_AffectedSessionBuildNumber** - The minor version of the application in which an application exit was observed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4294">**Data_AffectedSessionDuration** – seanso trukmė nuo pradžios iki išėjimo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4294">**Data_AffectedSessionDuration** - The length of the session from start to exit</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4295">**Data_AffectedSessionIDSMatch** – indikatorius, nurodantis telemetrijos sveikatą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4295">**Data_AffectedSessionIDSMatch** - An indicator of telemetry health.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4296">**Data_AffectedSessionMERPSessionID** – telemetrijos sveikatos indikatorius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4296">**Data_AffectedSessionMERPSessionID** - An indicator of telemetry health.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4297">**Data_AffectedSessionOSLocale** – OS lokalė, po kurios buvo stebėtas išėjimas iš programos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4297">**Data_AffectedSessionOSLocale** - The Locale of the OS under which the application exit was observed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4298">**Data_AffectedSessionOSVersion** – OS versija, po kurios buvo stebėtas išėjimas iš programos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4298">**Data_AffectedSessionOSVersion** - The OS version under which the application exit was observed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4299">**Data_AffectedSessionResidentMemoryOnCrash** – nuolatinės atminties kiekis, kuris buvo sunaudotas įvykus išėjimui iš programos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4299">**Data_AffectedSessionResidentMemoryOnCrash** - The amount of resident memory that was consumed when the application exit occurred</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4300">**Data_AffectedSessionStackHash** – identifikatorius, žymintis tam tikras įvykusias klaidas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4300">**Data_AffectedSessionStackHash** - An identifier that will denote the specific error being hit.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4340">„Office“ papildiniai veikia smėlio dėžėje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4340">Office Add-ins run in a sandbox.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4341">Šis įvykis surenka kontrolinių signalų informaciją apie aktyvinimus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4341">This event collects heartbeat information on activations.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4342">Kai papildinys sugenda, šis įvykis surenka informaciją, kodėl jis sugedo, jeigu su susijusi su mūsų smėlio dėžėje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4342">When an add-in crashes, this event collects why it crashed in the case it’s related to our sandbox.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4343">Naudojama tiriant tai atvejais, kai problemas nurodo klientai.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4343">Used to investigate when customers escalate issues.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4346">**AppInfo** – duomenys, susiję su papildinio tipu (užduočių sritis arba be sąsajos, arba turinys ir t. t.) ir teikėjo tipu (domenas, "SharePoint", failų sistema ir t. t.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4346">**AppInfo** - Data regarding the type of add-in (task pane or UILess or in content etc.) and the provider type (omen, SharePoint, filesystem etc.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4347">**AppInstanceId** – taikomosios programos egzemplioriaus ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4347">**AppInstanceId** - ID of the app instance</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4348">**AssetId** – taikomosios programos ištekliaus ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4348">**AssetId** - Asset ID of the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4351">**RemoterType** – nurodo nuotolinio elemento, kuris naudojamas norint suaktyvinti papildinį, tipą (patikimas, nepatikimas, „Win32webView“, patikimas UDF ir t. t.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4351">**RemoterType** - Specifies the type of remoter (Trusted, untrusted, Win32webView, Trusted UDF, etc.) used to activate the add-in</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4352">**StoreType** – taikomosios programos kilmė</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4352">**StoreType** - Origin of the app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4353">**Tag** – nurodo, kur tiksliai kodas nepavyko, naudojant su juo susietą unikalią žymę.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4353">**Tag**- Specifies where exactly the code has failed using the unique tag associated with it.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4354">**UsesSharedRuntime** – nurodo, ar taikomoji programa naudoja „sharedRuntime“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4354">**UsesSharedRuntime** - indicates the app uses sharedRuntime or not.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4358">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4358">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4479">**Interface** – „Office“ sąsaja, kur įvyko išimtis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4479">**Interface** – the Office interface where the exception occurred</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4480">**LoadAttempts** – bandymų įkelti papildinį skaičius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4480">**LoadAttempts** – the number of attempts to load the add-in</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4482">**OfficeApplication** – „Office“ programa, kur įvyko išimtis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4482">**OfficeApplication** – the Office application where the exception occurred</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4483">**OfficeVersion** – „Office“ versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4483">**OfficeVersion** – the versions of Office</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4484">**AddinProgId** – papildinio programos identifikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4484">**ProgID** – the add-in Prog identifier</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4498">**AffectedProcessUnsymbolicatedChecksum** – taikoma su dėklo maiša, siekiant užtikrinti simbolizaciją</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4498">**AffectedProcessUnsymbolicatedChecksum** – Goes with Stack hash for symbolization</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4499">**AffectedProcessVirtualMemoryOnCrash** – sugedusios programos virtualioji atmintis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4499">**AffectedProcessVirtualMemoryOnCrash** – Virtual memory of crashed app</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4502">**CrashedProcessSessionID** – taikomosios programos gedimo proceso seanso ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4502">**CrashedProcessSessionID** – SessionID of the process in app crash</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4503">**DetectionTime** – taikomosios programos gedimo data ir laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4503">**DetectionTime** – DateTime of app crash</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4504">**DeviceModel** – aparatūros modelis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4504">**DeviceModel** – Hardware model</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4505">**MERPSessionID** – MERP seanso ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4505">**MERPSessionID** – Session ID of MERP</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4506">**ReportingOsLocaleTag** – operacinės sistemos lokalė</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4506">**ReportingOsLocaleTag** – OS locale</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4507">**ReportingOSVerStr** – operacinės sistemos versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4507">**ReportingOSVerStr** – OS version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4508">**SessionBuildNumber** – sugedusios taikomosios programos versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4508">**SessionBuildNumber** – Crashed App’s version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4509">**SessionIDSMatch** – Bulio logika, skirta patvirtinti, ar ataskaitos seanso ID yra toks pat, kaip ir paimtas MERP</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4509">**SessionIDSMatch** – Boolean to verify whether reporting session ID is the same as picked up by Merp</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4510">**SessionVersion** – sugedusios taikomosios programos versija – **StackHash** – sugedusios taikomosios programos dėklo -pėdsako maiša</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4510">**SessionVersion** – Crashed App’s version– **StackHash** – Hash of the crashed app’s stack trace</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4511">**UAEType** – išvardijimas, suteikiantis mums informacijos apie įvykusios gedimo tipą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4511">**UAEType** – Enum giving us information on what type of crash it was</span></span>

### <a name="application-feature-performance-subtype"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4519">*Taikomosios programos funkcijų našumo potipis*</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4519">*Application feature performance subtype*</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4520">Prastas scenarijų, pvz., taikomosios programos paleidimas ar failo atidarymas, atsakymo laikas ar veikimas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4520">Poor response time or performance for scenarios such as application start up or opening a file.</span></span>

#### <a name="initial_page_landing"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4521">Initial_page_landing</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4521">Initial_page_landing</span></span> 
 
<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4522">Šis įvykis padeda sekti vartotojo matomą patirties tipą, kai vartotojai bus perkeliami į mūsų taikomosios programos puslapį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4522">This event helps track the type of experience that users see when they land in our application page.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4523">Šie duomenys naudojami norint nustatyti vartotojų srautą, nukreiptą į kiekvieną mūsų taikomosios programos patirtį ir taip pat padeda lengvai konsoliduoti eksperimentų rezultatus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4523">This data is used to determine the traffic of users piped into each experience in our application and also helps us to easily consolidate experimentation results.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4524">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4524">The following fields are collected:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4525">**Page** – ši funkcija naudojama patirties tipą, kurią vartotojai pirmiausia mato, kai pereina į mūsų puslapį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4525">**Page** - This is used to track the type of experience that user first sees when they land on our page.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4526">Galimos reikšmės yra „bandomoji versija“, „praleisti“, "iš karto", „iš anksto sugrupuota“, „prenumerata“ ir t. t.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4526">Possible values are “Trial”, “Skip”, “Prebundled”, “Subscription” etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4527">**storeExperience** – naudojama nustatyti, ar vartotojas turi teisę matyti saugyklos SDK patirtį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4527">**storeExperience** - This is used to determine if user was eligible to see the Store SDK Experience.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4528">**stringVariant** – ši funkcija naudojama norint nustatyti vartotojų matomų eilučių tipą, kai jie pereina į mūsų puslapį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4528">**stringVariant** - This is used to determine the type of strings that user sees when they land on our page.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4529">Atminkite, kad bet kuriame puslapyje, pvz., „bandomoji versija“, vartotojas gali matyti kitas eilutes. Tai priklauso nuo to, ar jie yra įsidiegę senesnę „Office“ versiją, arba jei anksčiau suaktyvino programą „Office“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4529">Note that for any page such as “Trial”, user can be eligible to see different strings based on whether they had Legacy Office installed, or if they had previously activated Office.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4530">Galimi šios ypatybės išvardijimai yra „LegacyUpsell“, „OfficeOpened“, „Default“, „YesIntent“, „NoIntent“ ir t. t.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4530">Possible enumerations of this property are “LegacyUpsell”, “OfficeOpened”, “Default”, “YesIntent”, “NoIntent” etc.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4531">**windowsBuildType** – tai naudojama norint stebėti naudotojo naudojamo „WindowsBuildType“ tipą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4531">**windowsBuildType** - This is used to track the type of WindowsBuildType that user is on.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4532">i.e. „RS4“, „RS5“, „RS19H1“, „Vibranium“ ir t. t. Kadangi mūsų patirtys dažniausiai orientuojasi į skirtingus „WindowsBuildTypes“ tipus, ši ypatybė yra gyvybiškai svarbi norint atskirti išvestis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4532">i.e. “RS4”, “RS5”, “RS19H1”, “Vibranium etc. As our experiences are usually targeted to different WindowsBuildTypes, this property is vital in differentiating between rollouts.</span></span> 

#### <a name="ipcpbootstrapuser"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4533">IpcpBootstrapUser</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4533">IpcpBootstrapUser</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4534">Renkama, kai vartotojas bando atidaryti IRM apsaugotą dokumentą ar taikyti IRM apsaugas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4534">Collected when a user attempts to open an IRM protected doc or apply IRM protections.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4535">Joje yra informacija, reikalinga tinkamai nustatyti ir diagnozuoti problemas, įvykusias IpcpBootstrapUser API iškvietimo metu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4535">It contains the information needed to be able to properly investigate and diagnose issues that happen when the IpcpBootstrapUser API call is made.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4537">**AppInfo.ClientHierarchy** – kliento hierarchija, kuri nurodo programos paleidimus gamybos aplinkoje arba kūrėjo aplinkoje</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4537">**AppInfo.ClientHierarchy** - Client hierarchy which indicates the application runs in production environment or developer environment</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4539">**AppInfo.Version** – programos versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4539">**AppInfo.Version** - Application version</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4540">**iKey** – registravimo tarnybos serverio ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4540">**iKey** - Logging service server Id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4541">**RMS.ApplicationScenarioId** programos pateiktas scenarijaus ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4541">**RMS.ApplicationScenarioId** - Scenario Id provided by the application</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4542">**RMS.AuthCallbackProvided** – nurodo, ar pateikiamas autentifikavimo iškvietimas kaip API iškvietimo įvestis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4542">**RMS.AuthCallbackProvided** - Indicate if provides the authentication callback as input of the API call or not</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4543">**RMS.ConnectionInfo.ExtranetUrl** – ryšio informacijos ekstraneto URL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4543">**RMS.ConnectionInfo.ExtranetUrl** - the extranet URL in connection info</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4544">**RMS.ConnectionInfo.IntranetUrl** – ryšio informacijos intraneto URL</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4544">**RMS.ConnectionInfo.IntranetUrl** - the intranet URL in connection info</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4545">**RMS.ConnectionMode** – ryšio režimas tarp teisių valdymo tarnybos kliento ir serverio: prisijungęs ar neprisijungęs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4545">**RMS.ConnectionMode** - The connection mode between Rights Management Service client and server: online or offline</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4547">**RMS.DurationWithoutExternalOps** – bendrasis laikas atėmus išorinių operacijų laiką, pvz., tinklo delsą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4547">**RMS.DurationWithoutExternalOps** - Total time minus external operations consumed, such as network latency.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4672">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4672">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4673">Šis įvykis naudojamas „Office“ taikomųjų programų sveikatai stebėti, taip pat tirti trikčių priežastis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4673">The event is used to monitor the health of our Office applications as well as for investigating causes of failures.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4674">Renkame informaciją, kiek kartų taikomoji programa neatsakė iki buvo pasirinktas nesklandusis programos išėjimas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4674">We collect the number of times an application appeared to be unresponsive prior to hitting an ungraceful application exit.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4676">**Data_HangsDetected** – kiek kartų taikomoji programa neatsakė iki buvo pastebėtas nesklandusis programos išėjimas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4676">**Data_HangsDetected** - The number of times the application appeared to become unresponsive prior to observing the ungraceful application exit.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4677">**Data_LastSessionId** – seanso, kurio metu buvo stebėtas nesklandusis programos išėjimas, identifikatorius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4677">**Data_LastSessionId** - The identifier for the session in which the ungraceful application exit was observed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4678">**Data_SessionBuildNumber** – papildoma taikomosios programos versija, kurioje buvo pastebėtas nesklandusis išėjimas iš programos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4678">**Data_SessionBuildNumber** - The minor version of the application in which an ungraceful application exit was observed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4679">**Data_SessionVersion** – pagrindinė taikomosios programos versija, kurioje buvo pastebėtas nesklandusis išėjimas iš programos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4679">**Data_SessionVersion** - The major version of the application in which an ungraceful application exit was observed.</span></span>

#### <a name="office_apple_whatsnewerrorandwarning"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4680">Office_Apple_WhatsNewErrorAndWarning</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4680">Office_Apple_WhatsNewErrorAndWarning</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4681">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4681">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4682">Įvykis naudojamas funkcijos Kas nauja sveikatai stebėti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4682">The event is used to monitor the health of the What’s New feature.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4683">Šis įvykis nurodo, kad funkcijos Kas nauja turinio analizavimo įvyko klaida/įspėjimas, nurodanti galimas turinio kūrimo triktis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4683">This event denotes that an error/warning occurred while parsing What's New content, pointing to potential content authoring issues.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4684">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4684">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4685">**Data_ContentKey** – žymiklis, nurodantis turinio dalį, kuri galėjo sukelti klaidą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4685">**Data_ContentKey** - A pointer to the section of the content that is likely to have caused the error.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4686">**Data_ErrorCode** – pastebėtos klaidos kodas (jei yra)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4686">**Data_ErrorCode** - The observed error code (if available)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4687">**Data_ErrorDescription** – klaidos aprašas (jei yra)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4687">**Data_ErrorDescription** - A description of the error (if available)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4688">**Data_EventID** – renkame duomenis eilutės, nurodančios pastebėtos klaidos tipą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4688">**Data_EventID** - We collect a string representing the type of error observed.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4689">**Data_IncludesHTMLTag** – ar turinyje yra raiškiojo html</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4689">**Data_IncludesHTMLTag** - Whether the content contains rich html</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4690">**Data_IncludesItemsTag** – ar turinyje yra elementų hierarchija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4690">**Data_IncludesItemsTag** - Whether the content contains a hierarchy of items</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4691">**Data_LengthOfRawData** – turinio dydis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4691">**Data_LengthOfRawData** - The size of the content</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4692">**Data_RequestURL** – URL, iš kurio atsisiųstas turinys</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4692">**Data_RequestURL** - The URL from which the content was downloaded</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4693">**Data_ServerLanguageTag** – kalba, kuria buvo sukurtas turinys.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4693">**Data_ServerLanguageTag** - The language the content was in.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4694">**Data_StatusCode** – klaidos būsena (jei yra)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4694">**Data_StatusCode** - The status of the error (if available)</span></span>

#### <a name="officeextensibilityrichapimethodinvocation"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4695">Office.Extensibility.RichApiMethodInvocation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4695">Office.Extensibility.RichApiMethodInvocation</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4696">Šis įvykis suaktyvinamas, kai klientas naudoja „Office“ papildinį ir paslaugai teikti iškviečia raiškųjį API.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4696">When customer uses an Office Add-in and calls Rich API for providing service, this event will be triggered.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4697">Naudojamas norint įvertinti paslaugos patikimumą, veikimą ir raiškiojo API metodo naudojimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4697">Used to measure the service reliability, performance and usage for Rich API method invocation.</span></span>
 
<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4698">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4698">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4699">**Api** – visas API pavadinimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4699">**Api** - Full name of the API</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4700">**DispFlag** – bitų žymė, aprašanti metodo iškvietimo tipą (pavyzdžiui, 0 x 1 = METHOD, 0 x 2 = PROPERTYGET, 0 x 4 = PROPERTYPUT, 0 x 8 = PROPERTYPUTREF)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4700">**DispFlag** - A bit flag describing the type of method call (Ex: 0x1 = METHOD, 0x2 = PROPERTYGET, 0x4 = PROPERTYPUT, 0x8 = PROPERTYPUTREF)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4701">**DispId** – iškviečiamo metodo išsiuntimo ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4701">**DispId** - Dispatch ID for the method being called</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4702">**HResult** – metodo iškvietimo „HResult“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4702">**HResult** - HResult for the method call</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4703">**Latency** – iškvietimo gaištis mikrosekundėmis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4703">**Latency** - Latency for the call, in microseconds</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4704">**ReqId** – GUID, skirtas paketo užklausai, kuriai šis metodas priklauso</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4704">**ReqId** - GUID for the batch request that this method belongs to</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4705">**TypeId** – GUID, skirtas sąsajai, kuriai šis metodas iškviečiamas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4705">**TypeId** - GUID for the interface on which this method being called</span></span>


#### <a name="officemanageabilityserviceapplypolicy"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4706">Office.Manageability.Service.ApplyPolicy</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4706">Office.Manageability.Service.ApplyPolicy</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4707">Svarbi telemetrija, skirta gedimams stebėti\\Sėkmingas debesijos strategijos nustatymų registravimas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4707">Critical telemetry to track failure\\Success of applying cloud policy settings to registry.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4708">„LastError“ nurodo, kodėl ir kur nepavyko taikyti registro strategijos.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4708">LastError tells why and where the Application of policy in registry failed.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4709">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4709">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4710">**Data.ApplyLogMsg** – išimties pranešimas, jei strategija buvo taikoma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4710">**Data.ApplyLogMsg** - The exception msg if any while policy was being applied</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4711">**Data.Cid** – dinamiškai sukurtas sąsajos identifikatorius, siunčiamas į tarnybą, kai buvo atliktas tarnybos iškvietimas, kad gautų debesijos strategiją.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4711">**Data.Cid** - dynamically generated correlation identifier sent to the service when the service call was made to fetch the cloud policy.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4712">Naudojamas nustatyti, kuris iškvietimas sukėlė problemą taikant strategiją debesyje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4712">Used to correlate which call caused an issue while applying the policies on the cloud.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4713">**Data.Last Error** – Viena iš penkių eilučių reikšmių (surašytuvai), norint užregistruoti, kuris strategijos taikymo etapas buvo įvykdytas, kai įvyko išimtis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4713">**Data.Last Error** - One of five string values (enumerators) to log which stage of policy application was being executed when the exception occurred</span></span>

#### <a name="officeoutlookdesktopbootperfmetrics"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4714">Office.Outlook.Desktop.BootPerfMetrics</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4714">Office.Outlook.Desktop.BootPerfMetrics</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4720">**CredPromptCount** – skaičių Raginimų pateikti kredencialus skaičius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4720">**CredPromptCount** – Number of credential prompts shown</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4721">**ElapsedTotal** – Bendras įkrovos laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4721">**ElapsedTotal** - Total time spent for boot</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4722">**IsLoggingEnabled** – Ar įgalintas registravimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4722">**IsLoggingEnabled** - Is logging enabled</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4723">**ShowChooseProfileDlg** – Ar buvo rodomas dialogo langas Pasirinkti profilį</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4723">**ShowChooseProfileDlg** – Whether the Choose Profile Dialog was shown</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4724">**ShowFirstRunDlg** – Ar „Outlook“ paleidžiamas pirmą kartą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4724">**ShowFirstRunDlg** - is outlook launched for the first time</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4725">**ShowIMAPSrchfldWarningDlg** – Įspėjimai, jei yra IMAP paskyra su ANSI PST</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4725">**ShowIMAPSrchfldWarningDlg** - Warnings in case we have an IMAP account with an ANSI PST</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4726">**ShowNeedSupportDlg** – Įkrovos trikties sužadintas palaikymo dialogo lango</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4726">**ShowNeedSupportDlg** - Boot failure triggered support dialog</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4727">**ShowSafeModeDlg** – Ar seansas atidarytas saugiuoju režimu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4727">**ShowSafeModeDlg** - is the session opened in safe mode</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4728">**ShowScanPstDlg** – Parduotuvės taisymo patikrinimo metu rodomas klaidos pranešimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4728">**ShowScanPstDlg** - Store repair check displayed error message</span></span>


#### <a name="officeoutlookmacbootperf"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4729">Office.Outlook.Mac.BootPerf</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4729">Office.Outlook.Mac.BootPerf</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4730">Renkamas laikas, kurio reikia paleisti „Outlook“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4730">Collects time taken to boot Outlook.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4731">„Outlook“ paleidimo laikas aktyviai stebimas, kad aptiktų ir diagnozuotų regresiją.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4731">The boot time of Outlook is actively monitored to detect and diagnose regressions.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4732">Jis taip pat naudojamas klientų sudėtingesniems atvejams nustatyti ir laikui bėgant pagerinti įkrovos veikimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4732">It is also used to diagnose customer escalations as well as improve boot performance over time.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4734">**MacOLKBootPerfDuration** – bendras sistemos įkrovos laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4734">**MacOLKBootPerfDuration** - total time spent booting</span></span>

#### <a name="officeoutlookmacperformanceunresponsive"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4736">Office.Outlook.Mac.PerformanceUnresponsive</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4736">Office.Outlook.Mac.PerformanceUnresponsive</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4738">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4738">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4739">**Duration** – prabėgęs pablogėjusio veikimo laikas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4739">**Duration** - time elapsed of degraded performance</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4740">**EventType** – įvykio, per kurį pablogėjo veikimas, tipas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4740">**EventType** - type of event experiencing degraded performance</span></span>


#### <a name="officeperformanceboot"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4741">Office.Performance.Boot</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4741">Office.Performance.Boot</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4742">Surinkta taikomosios programos „Office“ paleidimo metu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4742">Collected when an Office application is booted.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4743">Nurodoma, ar paleidimas buvo pradėtas atidarant failą, ar paleidžiant per meniu Pradžia, ar tai buvo pirmasis taikomosios programos paleidimas, kiek atminties naudoja taikomoji programa, ir ar vartotojui buvo parodyta blokuojama vartotojo sąsaja.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4743">Includes whether the boot was initiated by opening a file or launching via the Start menu, whether this was the first boot of the application, how much memory the application is using, and whether there was any blocking UI shown to the user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4744">Naudojama išmatuoti, kaip greitai veikia taikomosios programos „Office“ paleidimas ir kiek atminties naudojama paleidimo metu, kad užtikrinti priimtiną vartotojo patirtį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4744">Used to measure how fast Office applications boot and how much memory they use when they start, to ensure there is an acceptable user experience.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4745">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4745">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4746">**ActivationKind** – ar taikomoji programa buvo pradėta naudojant Pradžios meniu, atidarant failą arba naudojant OLE automatizavimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4746">**ActivationKind** - Whether the application was started by launching from the Start menu, by opening a file, or through OLE Automation.</span></span>
  
  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4747">**BootToStart** – ar paleidžiant šią taikomąją programą vartotojas pasirinko rodyti pradžios ekraną.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4747">**BootToStart** - Whether the user has chosen to show the start screen when this application starts.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4748">**DocLocation** – atidarant dokumentą nurodo dokumentą pateikusią tarnybą („OneDrive“, „File Server“, „SharePoint“ ir kt.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4748">**DocLocation** -  When opening a document, indicates which service provided the document (OneDrive, File Server, SharePoint, etc.).</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4749">**FirstBoot** – ar tai buvo pirmas taikomosios programos įkrovimas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4749">**FirstBoot** - Whether this was a first boot of the application.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4750">**Initializationduration** – pirmojo „Office“ inicijavimo proceso trukmė mikrosekundėmis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4750">**InitializationDuration** - The duration in microseconds it took to first initialize the Office process.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4751">**InterruptionMessageId** – ar paleidimas buvo pertrauktas dialogo lango, prašančio naudotojo atlikti įvestį, dialogo lango ID.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4751">**InterruptionMessageId** - If the boot was interrupted by a dialog asking for user input, the ID of the dialog.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4752">**Totalworkingsetmb** – proceso darbinio paketo atminties kiekis megabaitais.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4752">**TotalWorkingSetMB** - The amount of memory in megabytes in the process’s working set.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4753">**VirtualSetMB** – proceso paketo atminties kiekis megabaitais.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4753">**VirtualSetMB** - The amount of memory in megabytes in the process’s virtual set.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4754">(tik „MacOS“/ „iOS“)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4754">(MacOS / iOS only)</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4755">**Workingsetpeakmb** – didžiausias atminties kiekis megabaitais, kuris iki šiol yra buvęs proceso darbiniame rinkinyje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4755">**WorkingSetPeakMB** - The largest amount of memory in megabytes that was ever in the process’s working set so far.</span></span>

#### <a name="officeuxofficeinsidercanshowofficeinsiderslab"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4756">Office.UX.OfficeInsider.CanShowOfficeInsiderSlab</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4756">Office.UX.OfficeInsider.CanShowOfficeInsiderSlab</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4760">**Data_Event** – nenaudojamas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4760">**Data_Event** - Unused</span></span>
