  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4762">**Data_Reason** – nenaudojamas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4762">**Data_Reason** - Unused</span></span>
 

#### <a name="officeuxofficeinsiderregistercurrentinsider"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4763">Office.UX.OfficeInsider.RegisterCurrentInsider</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4763">Office.UX.OfficeInsider.RegisterCurrentInsider</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4764">Kritinis signalas, skirtas stebėti sėkmingą arba nesėkmingą vartotojų, kurie anksčiau nebuvo užregistruoti kaip „Office Insider“ programos dalyviai, registravimą naudojant „Office Insider“ komponavimo versijas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4764">Critical signal for tracking success or failure of registering users using Office Insider builds who weren't registered as Office Insiders before.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4765">Jis visų pirma taikomas dabartiniams „Office Insider“ programos dalyviams, kurie prie „Office Insider“ programos prisijungė prieš įtraukiant „Office Insider“ programos dalyvių registraciją.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4765">Main scenario for this is current Office Insiders who joined Office Insider program before registration of Office Insiders was added.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4766">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4766">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4767">**Data_RegisterInsider** – „Office Insider“ registracijos būsena</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4767">**Data_RegisterInsider** - Status of Office Insider registration</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4768">**Data_RegisterInsiderHr** – „Office Insider“ registracijos rezultatų kodas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4768">**Data_RegisterInsiderHr** - Result code for Office Insider registration</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4769">**Data_RegistrationStateCurrent** – dabartinė registracijos būsena</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4769">**Data_RegistrationStateCurrent** - Current registration state</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4770">**Data_RegistrationStateDesired** – prašoma registracijos būsena</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4770">**Data_RegistrationStateDesired** - Requested registration state</span></span>


#### <a name="officeuxofficeinsidershowofficeinsiderdlg"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4771">Office.UX.OfficeInsider.ShowOfficeInsiderDlg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4771">Office.UX.OfficeInsider.ShowOfficeInsiderDlg</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4772">Kritinis signalas, naudojamas vartotojo sąveikai su dialogu „Prisijunkite prie „Office Insider“ stebėti.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4772">Critical signal tracking user interaction with Join Office Insider dialog.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4773">Jis naudojamas nustatyti bet kokioms problemoms, kurios kyla vykdant vartotojo inicijuotus pakeitimus, tokius kaip prisijungimas prie „Office Insider“ programos, pasitraukimas iš jos arba „Office Insider“ programos dalyvio lygio pakeitimas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4773">It is used for identifying any issues in performing user-initiated changes such as joining or leaving Office Insider program and changing Office Insider level.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4774">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4774">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4775">**Data_AcceptedContactMeNew** – nurodo, ar vartotojas sutiko, kad prisijungus prie „Office Insider“ programos, „Microsoft“ su juo susisiektų</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4775">**Data_AcceptedContactMeNew** - Indicates if a user has accepted to be contacted by Microsoft upon joining Office Insider program</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4776">**Data_InsiderLevel** – „Insider“ lygis atidarant dialogo langą „Prisijunkite prie „Office Insider“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4776">**Data_InsiderLevel** - Insider Level on opening of “Join Office Insider” dialog</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4777">**Data_InsiderLevelNew** – „Insider“ lygis uždarant dialogo langą „Prisijunkite prie „Office Insider“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4777">**Data_InsiderLevelNew** - Insider level on closing of “Join Office Insider” dialog</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4778">**Data_IsInternalUser** – nurodo, ar taikomoji programa vykdoma naudojant „Microsoft“ įmonės paskyros kredencialus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4778">**Data_IsInternalUser** - Indicates whether the application runs under the credentials of a Microsoft corporate account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4779">**Data_IsInternalUser** – nurodo, ar kodas gali nustatyti, ar taikomoji programa vykdoma naudojant „Microsoft“ įmonės paskyros kredencialus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4779">**Data_IsInternalUserInit** - Indicates whether the code could determine whether the application runs under the credentials of a Microsoft corporate account.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4780">**Data_OpenNewsletterWebpage** – nurodo, ar „Office Insider“ informacinio biuletenio prenumeratos saitas buvo paspaustas su sąlyga, kad vartotojas prisijungė prie „„Office Insider“ programos, naujienlaiškio prenumeratos funkcija įjungta ir vartotojas neatšaukė „Office Insider“ naujienlaiškio prenumeratos svetainės atidarymo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4780">**Data_OpenNewsletterWebpage** - Indicates whether Office Insider Newsletter Subscription link was triggered under condition that user has joined Office Insider program, Newsletter Subscription feature is enabled, and the user have not cancelled opening of Office Insider Newsletter Subscription webpage.</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4781">**Data_RegisterInsider** – „Office Insider“ registracijos būsena</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4781">**Data_RegisterInsider** - Status of Office Insider registration</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4782">**Data_RegisterInsiderHr** – „Office Insider“ registracijos rezultatų kodas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4782">**Data_RegisterInsiderHr** - Result code for Office Insider registration</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4783">**Data_RegistrationStateCurrent** – dabartinė registracijos būsena</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4783">**Data_RegistrationStateCurrent** - Current registration state</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4784">**Data_RegistrationStateDesired** – prašoma registracijos būsena</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4784">**Data_RegistrationStateDesired** - Requested registration state</span></span>




#### <a name="officevisiosharedvisiofilerender"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4785">Office.Visio.Shared.VisioFileRender</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4785">Office.Visio.Shared.VisioFileRender</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4786">Šis įvykis užfiksuoja failo generavimo laiką.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4786">This event captures file render time.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4787">Šis įvykis padeda išlaikyti failo generavimo veikimo patikrą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4787">This event helps us keep file render performance in check.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4788">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4788">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4789">**Data\_AvgTime: integer** – Vidutinis laikas, per kurį seanse buvo generuotas „Visio“ piešimo vaizdas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4789">**Data\_AvgTime: integer** - Average time it took to render Visio drawing in a session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4790">**Data\_CompositeSurfEnabled: bool** – „ True“, jei įgalintas sudėtinis vaizdo generavimo režimas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4790">**Data\_CompositeSurfEnabled: bool** - true is composite rendering mode is enabled</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4791">**Data\_Count: integer** – Laikas, kada „Visio“ generuoja piešimo seanso vaizdą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4791">**Data\_Count: integer** - Number of time Visio renders the drawing in a session</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4792">**Data\_FirstRenderTime: long** – Trukmė, skirta pirmą kartą generuoti failą, milisekundėmis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4792">**Data\_FirstRenderTime: long** - duration to render file on first launch in millisecond</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4793">**Data\_AvgTime: integer** – Vidutinis laikas, per kurį seanse buvo generuotas „Visio“ piešimo vaizdas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4793">**Data\_MaxTime: integer** - Max time it took to render Visio drawing in a session</span></span>

#### <a name="officeairspacebackendwin32graphicsdriversofthang"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4833">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.GraphicsDriverSoftHang</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4833">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.GraphicsDriverSoftHang</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4834">Padeda „Microsoft“ atskirti ilgą vaizdo plokštės tvarkyklės „pakibimą“ nuo trumpo, o tai savo ruožtu padeda priimti sprendimus apie tai, kurios vaizdo plokštės tvarkyklės gali turėti problemų.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4834">Helps Microsoft separate long video card driver hangs from short ones, which in turn helps make decisions about which video card drivers may be having problems.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4835">Dėl vartotojo vaizdo plokštės tvarkyklės„pakibo“„Office“, bet „pakibimo“ poveikis dar nežinomas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4835">The user's video card driver has caused Office to hang, but the impact of the hang is not known yet</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4836">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4836">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4837">**Data\_InDeviceCall** – Vaizdo plokštės metodas, dėl kurio įvyko „pakibimas“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4837">**Data\_InDeviceCall** - The method called on the video card that produced the hang</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4838">**Data\_Timeout** – kiek laiko truko „pakibimas“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4838">**Data\_Timeout** - How long the hang lasted</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4840">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4840">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4841">Įvykis naudojamas užfiksuoti „Digital River“ aktyvinimo nesėkmes (įvykis registruoja raktą ir produktą, kuris buvo naudojamas aktyvinimui, taip pat gautą klaidos kodą).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4841">The event is used for capturing digital river activation failures (the event logs the key and product that was used to activate, as well as the error code received).</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4842">Šis įvykis naudojamas nustatant ir padedant šalinti aktyvinimo triktis („Digital River“ problemos).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4842">This event is used for detecting and helping troubleshoot activation failures (Digital River issues).</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4843">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4843">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4844">**Data_DigitalRiverID** – „Digital River“ produkto ID, siejantis su šia „Office“ produkto partnerių programa SKY</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4844">**Data_DigitalRiverID** - Digital River product Id that maps to this Office product SKY</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4845">**Data_Error** – eilutė, nurodanti aktyvinimo klaidos kodą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4845">**Data_Error** - A string representing an activation error code.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4846">**Data_ProductKey** – produkto kodas, kurį buvo bandoma suaktyvinti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4846">**Data_ProductKey** - Product key that was attempted to be activated</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4847">**Data_ProductKeyHash** – aktyvintas užkoduotas produkto kodas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4847">**Data_ProductKeyHash** - An encoded product key being activated</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4849">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4849">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4850">Įvykis surenka pateiktą klaidos kodą, bei periodiškai tikrina prenumeratos licencijos galiojimą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4850">The event collects the error code returned while periodically checking the validity of a subscription license.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4851">Klaidos kodas gali reikšti serverio nepasiekiamumą, bet taip pat licencijos galiojimo laiko pasibaigimą, kompiuterių skaičiaus limitą, neteisingą aparatūros ID ir t. t.  Šis įvykis naudojamas stebėti „Office“ licencijavimo tarnybos sveikatą, bei tirti įvykius, susijusius su kompiuterio prenumeratos valdymu.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4851">The error code can signify server unavailability but also license expiration, machine count limit, invalid hardware ID, etc.  This event is used to monitor the health of the Office Licensing Service but also to investigate issues related to subscription machine management.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4852">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4852">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4862">Šis įvykis gaunamas „Office“ programoms, veikiančioms „Apple“ platformose.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4862">This event is collected for Office applications running under Apple platforms.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4863">Įvykis leidžia mums žinoti, kad vartotojas paleido pirmojo sistemos paleidimo programą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4863">The event lets us know a user has entered first run experience.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4864">Šį įvykį naudojame norėdami išsiaiškinti, ar pirmojo sistemos paleidimo programa (FRE) sėkmingai paleista.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4864">We use this event to figure out if the First-Run Experience (FRE) was started successfully.</span></span>

#### <a name="officegraphicsarcexceptions"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4867">Office.Graphics.ARCExceptions</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4867">Office.Graphics.ARCExceptions</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4868">Ši išimties ataskaitų teikimo informacija yra svarbi vertinant bendrą grafikos rietuvės sveikatą, taip pat nustatant kodo dalis, kuriose dažniai pasitaiko gedimų, siekiant nustatyti tyrimo prioritetą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4868">This exception reporting information is important for assessing the overall health of the graphics stack, as well as identifying parts of the code where failures are occurring at high frequency, in order to prioritize investigation.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4869">Ši išimties ataskaitų teikimo informacija yra svarbi vertinant bendrą grafikos rietuvės sveikatą, taip pat nustatant kodo dalis, kuriose dažniai pasitaiko gedimų.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4869">This exception reporting information is important for assessing the overall health of the graphics stack, as well as identifying parts of the code where failures are occurring at high frequency.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4870">Tai padeda inžinieriui nustatyti, kurios generavimo problemos turi įtakos daugeliui vartotojų, leidžia mums nustatyti mūsų prioritetą sprendžiant problemas, kurios aktualios didžiausiam vartotojų skaičiui.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4870">This helps an engineer to determine which rendering failures are impacting the most users, enabling us to prioritize our investigations toward fixing issues that will have the greatest user benefit.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4871">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4871">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4893">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4893">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-4895">**1 -** Bulio logika nurodo, ar vartotojas pasirinko naują failą</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-4895">**1 -** Bool indicating if the user chooses new file or not</span></span>

#### <a name="officeairspaceairspacelocalblocklistdriverupdated"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5047">Office.AirSpace.AirSpaceLocalBlocklistDriverUpdated</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5047">Office.AirSpace.AirSpaceLocalBlocklistDriverUpdated</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5048">Vartotojas atnaujino vaizdo plokštės tvarkyklę, kuri anksčiau sukėlė „Office“ gedimus ir todėl nebenaudojama.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5048">User has updated a video card driver that was previously causing Office crashes and thus no longer being used to render.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5049">Informuoja „Microsoft“, kad vartotojai, kurie vieną kartą buvo netinkamoje vaizdo generavimo būsenoje, vėl yra rekomenduojamoje vaizdo generavimo būsenoje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5049">Informs Microsoft that users who were once in a sub-optimal rendering state are once again in the recommended rendering state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5050">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5050">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5051">**Data\_BlockedDriverVersion** – Tvarkyklės versija, kuri buvo blokuota.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5051">**Data\_BlockedDriverVersion** - Version of the driver that was blocklisted.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5052">**Duomenų\_DeviceId** – Vaizdo plokštės įrenginio, kuris buvo blokuotas, identifikatorius.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5052">**Data\_DeviceId** -identifier of the video card device that was blocklisted.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5053">**Data\_UpdatedDriverVersion** – Atnaujintos tvarkyklės versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5053">**Data\_UpdatedDriverVersion** - Version of the updated driver</span></span>

#### <a name="officeairspaceairspacelocalblocklistinfo"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5054">Office.AirSpace.AirSpaceLocalBlocklistInfo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5054">Office.AirSpace.AirSpaceLocalBlocklistInfo</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5055">Išsami informacija apie vartotojo vaizdo plokštės tvarkyklę, kuri sukėlė kelis pastaruosius „Office“ programų gedimus.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5055">Details on the user's video card driver that has caused multiple recent crashes of Office applications.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5056">„Office“ nepanaudos šios vaizdo plokštės šiame „Office“ seanse (naudojant programinės įrangos vaizdo generavimą) tol, kol bus atnaujinta tvarkyklė.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5056">Office will not use this video card in this Office session (using software rendering instead) until the driver is updated.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5057">Informuoja „Microsoft“ apie vaizdo plokštės tvarkykles, kurios sukelia problemų „Office“, todėl galima nustatyti tendencijas ir analizuoti tokių tvarkyklių poveikį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5057">Informs Microsoft of video card drivers that are causing problems in Office so trends can be identified and the user of impact of such drivers can be analyzed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5058">Pranešti „Microsoft“, kiek vartotojų yra naudojant šią antrinę optimalią būseną.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5058">Tell Microsoft how many users are in this sub-optimal state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5059">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5059">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5060">**Data\_AllAppsBlocked** – Ar visos „Office“ programos blokuotos</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5060">**Data\_AllAppsBlocked** - Whether all Office apps are blocklisted</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5061">**Data\_BlockedDeviceId** – Vaizdo plokštės įrenginio, kuris buvo blokuotas, identifikatorius</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5061">**Data\_BlockedDeviceId** - identifier of the video card device that was blocklisted</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5062">**Data\_BlockedDriverVersion** - Tvarkyklės versija, kuri buvo blokuota.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5062">**Data\_BlockedDriverVersion** - Version of the driver that was blocklisted</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5063">**Duomenų\_CrashHistory** – Struktūra, vaizduojanti vaizdo plokštės tvarkyklės, dėl kurios kilo gedimas, istoriją</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5063">**Data\_CrashHistory** - A string that represents the history of video card driver caused crashes for analysis</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5064">**Data\_SecsBetweenCrashes** - Kaip dažnai pasitaiko tvarkyklės kortelės gedimų</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5064">**Data\_SecsBetweenCrashes** - How frequently driver card crashes are occurring</span></span>

#### <a name="officeairspaceairspacewincompisenabled"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5065">Office.AirSpace.AirSpaceWinCompIsEnabled</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5065">Office.AirSpace.AirSpaceWinCompIsEnabled</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5066">Ar naudojama naujausia „Office“ žemo lygio vaizdo generavimo platforma, pagrįsta „Windows Composition“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5066">Whether the latest Office low-level rendering platform based on Windows Composition is being used.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5067">Kadangi naujausia „Office“ žemo lygio vaizdo generavimo platforma sukurta ir pradedama leisti klientams, tai leidžia „Microsoft“ pamatyti, kiek vartotojų yra kiekvienoje versijoje, kad užtikrintų, jog platformoje neliko klaidų.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5067">As the latest Office low-level rendering platform is developed and begins to be released to customers, this allows Microsoft to see how many users are on each version to ensure the platform remains bug-free.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5068">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5068">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5069">**Data\_WinCompEnabled** - Ar naudojama „Windows Composition“ pagrįsta vidinė versija</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5069">**Data\_WinCompEnabled** -Whether the Windows Composition-based backend is in use</span></span>

#### <a name="officeairspacebackendwin32graphicsdriverhangdetectorblocklistapp"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5070">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.GraphicsDriverHangDetectorBlocklistApp</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5070">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.GraphicsDriverHangDetectorBlocklistApp</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5071">Pastebėta, kad dėl vartotojo vaizdo plokštės kyla ilgų arba nepataisomų „pakibimų“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5071">User’s video card has been detected as causing long or unrecoverable hangs.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5072">„Office“ nepanaudos šios vaizdo plokštės šiame „Office“ seanse (naudojant programinės įrangos vaizdo generavimą) tol, kol bus atnaujinta tvarkyklė.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5072">Office will not use this video card in this Office session (using software rendering instead) until the driver is updated.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5073">Informuoja „Microsoft“ apie vaizdo plokštės tvarkykles, kurios sukelia problemų „Office“, todėl galima nustatyti tendencijas ir analizuoti tokių tvarkyklių poveikį.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5073">Informs Microsoft of video card drivers that are causing problems in Office so trends can be identified and the user of impact of such drivers can be analyzed.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5074">Taip pat informuoja, kiek vartotojų yra naudojant šią antrinę optimalią būseną.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5074">Also helps in informing how many users are in this sub-optimal state.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5075">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5075">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5076">**Data\_AppName** - Dėl kokios programos „pakimba“ vaizdo plokštės tvarkyklė</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5076">**Data\_AppName** - Which app has encountered video card driver hangs</span></span>

#### <a name="officeairspacebackendwin32graphicsdriverhangdetectorregistrywrite"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5077">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.GraphicsDriverHangDetectorRegistryWrite</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5077">Office.AirSpace.Backend.Win32.GraphicsDriverHangDetectorRegistryWrite</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5078">„Office“ nustatė, kad dėl naudotojo vaizdo plokštės „pakibo“ programa, kuri turėtų būti analizuojama kitoje „Office“ programos įkrovoje.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5078">Office has identified that the user's video card driver has caused a hang that should be analyzed at the next Office application boot.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5079">Naudojamos norint nustatyti, ar naudojant kitą vaizdo plokštės tvarkyklę arba adapterį vartotojui būtų suteikta geresnė patirtis.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5079">Used to determine whether using a different video card driver or adapter would offer a better user experience.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5080">Kaip matyti, „Microsoft“ gali atlikti koregavimus, kad „Office“ patirtis būtų kuo sklandesnė.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5080">As patterns occur, Microsoft may make adjustments to keep the Office experience as smooth as possible.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5081">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5081">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5082">**Data\_HangDetected** – Ar aptiktas „pakibimas“</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5082">**Data\_HangDetected** - Whether a hang was detected</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5083">**Data\_InDeviceCall** - Kuris vaizdo plokštės vaizdo generavimo iškvietimas buvo „Office“, kai įvyko „pakibimas“.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5083">**Data\_InDeviceCall** - Which video card rendering call Office was in when the hang occurred</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5084">**Data\_Timeout** – kiek laiko praėjo nuo „pakibimo“, jei programa atkurta</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5084">**Data\_Timeout** - How long the hang lasted, if it recovered</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5085">**Duomenų\_UnrecoverableCommand** - Ar paprastai šios vaizdo plokštės vaizdo generavimo komandos „pakibimas“ yra atkuriamas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5085">**Data\_UnrecoverableCommand** - Whether the hang in this video card rendering command is typically recoverable.</span></span>

#### <a name="officegraphicsspritememcorrupt"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5104">Office.Graphics.SpriteMemCorrupt</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5104">Office.Graphics.SpriteMemCorrupt</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5105">Praneša apie aptiktas „sprite“ atminties apskaitos telemetrijos klaidas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5105">Reports any errors detected in the sprite memory accounting telemetry.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5106">Svarbu vertinant grafinės atminties naudojimo telemetrijos būseną.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5106">Critical for assessing health of the graphics memory usage telemetry.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5107">Ši informacija reikalinga norint patikrinti mūsų „SpriteMem“ telemetrijos tikslumą.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5107">This information is needed to validate the correctness of our SpriteMem telemetry.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5108">Renkami šių laukų duomenys:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5108">The following fields are collected:</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5109">**Duomenų\_CurrentSpriteMem** - Bendras atminties kiekis, aktyviai paskirstytas išlaikyti „sprites“ (vaizdus), dėl kurių atsiranda ekrano turinys.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5109">**Data\_CurrentSpriteMem** - Total amount of memory that is actively allocated to hold sprites (images) that result in screen content.</span></span>

  - <span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5110">**Data\_Function** - Funkcijos, kuri bando paleisti „sprite“ atmintį, pavadinimas.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5110">**Data\_Function** - The name of the function that is attempting to release sprite memory.</span></span>

#### <a name="officepowerpointpptsharednointernetconnectivity"></a><span data-ttu-id="d1a89-5112">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Shared.NoInternetConnectivity</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d1a89-5112">Office.PowerPoint.PPT.Shared.NoInternetConnectivity</span></span>
